NK032(khi)004:1: // snyan brgyud rin po che rdo rje zam pa'i gdams
NK032(khi)004:2: ngag gzhung bshad che ba 'dzeng yab sras kyi slob
NK032(khi)004:3: ma slob dpon kun bzang rdo rjes mdzad pa bzhugs
NK032(khi)004:4: / ma nor ma bcos bsam 'das brjod med ngang la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK032(khi)004:5: gdod nas dag pa'i byang chub sems nyid kyis //
NK032(khi)004:6: nyid kyi ngo bo nyid kyi don bstan pa //
NK032(khi)004:7: zhes bya bas sngon du mchod par brjod cing bshad par dam bca' ba ston pa'o //
NK032(khi)004:8: spyir gdams ngag gi lugs kyis mchod par brjod pa mi 'byung ba yin te /
NK032(khi)004:9: mchod par brjod pa ni rgyud lung dam sgrub thabs las 'byung ngo //
NK032(khi)004:10: gdams ngag la mchod par brjod pa mi 'byung ba'i rgyu mtshan ni /
NK032(khi)004:11: spyir gdams ngag gi lugs kyis rang gi rgyud la nyams su myong ba'i go tshod dam /
NK032(khi)004:13: rgyud lung gi don dang mi 'gal bar nyung la
NK032(khi)004:14: 'dus pa'i don de bla mas brda dang ngag gi
NK032(khi)004:15: ngo sprod nas ston pa las /
NK032(khi)004:16: klad kyi don dang gzhung dang mjug bsdu ba med
NK032(khi)004:17: pas na mchod par brjod pa mi 'byung ba lags
NK032(khi)004:18: skad / rgyud lung ngam sgrub thabs la mchod par brjod pa 'byung ba ni /
NK032(khi)004:20: sgrub thabs kyi gtso bo'i lha la mchod par brjod pa yin pas /
NK032(khi)004:21: de yang 'bras bu gsang sngags kyi lugs kun tu
NK032(khi)004:22: bzang po'am rdo rje 'chang ngam rdo rje sems dpa'
NK032(khi)004:24: rgyu mtshan nyid kyi lugs kyi yum chen mo'am sh+aakya
NK032(khi)004:25: thub pa'am byang chub sems dpa' la mchod par brjod
NK032(khi)004:26: pa'o // yang na bstan bcos rtsom pa po rten gyi gang zag gis yi dam gyi lha'am /
NK032(khi)004:27: yang na bstan pa'i bdag po la mchod par brjod pa'o //
NK032(khi)004:28: gdams ngag la mchod par brjod pa mi 'byung ba yin te /
NK032(khi)004:29: 'byung na'ang rtsa ba'i bla ma la mchod par brjod pa'o //
NK032(khi)004:30: de yang ma dag pa dag par byed pa'am /
NK032(khi)004:31: ma rtogs pa rtogs par bya ba'i phyir gzhan la mchod par brjod pa'o //
NK032(khi)004:32: gdams ngag 'di'i dbang du byas na mchod par brjod pa 'dir 'byung ste /
NK032(khi)004:34: 'di ni gang zag gis go tshod dam /
NK032(khi)004:35: rtogs tshod la brten nas bcos pa lta bu min te /
NK032(khi)004:36: bcom ldan 'das dpal kun tu bzang po'am /
NK032(khi)004:37: rdo rje sems dpa' nas da lta yan chad du
NK032(khi)004:38: bka' brgyud kyi phreng ba ma chad pa'i phyir rgyud
NK032(khi)004:40: dgongs pa don gyi brgyud kyi snying po 'di yin pas /
NK032(khi)004:42: de yang rgyud kyi ston pa la sogs pa rang
NK032(khi)004:43: gi sems nyid la tshur la 'tshal ba ma yin
NK032(khi)004:44: pa'i yul gzhan la phar la mchod par mi brjod
NK032(khi)004:45: de / nyid la nyid kyis mchod par brjod pa yin pas /
NK032(khi)004:46: so so rang rang nyid kyi sems nyid dngos po'i gnas lugs de la phyag 'tshal bar ston pa'o //
NK032(khi)004:47: de yang rdzogs pa chen po gu ru bzhi pa las /
NK032(khi)004:48: sems las sangs rgyas med pas mchod pa gzhan mi bya //
NK032(khi)004:50: de bas na mchod par brjod pa'i yul zhig dang /
NK032(khi)004:51: rjod par byed pa'i rig pa gnyis su med de /
NK032(khi)004:52: gnyis su med pa'i don brjod du med pa'i ngang
NK032(khi)004:53: de nyid rang gi rgyud la yod par rtog pa'i
NK032(khi)004:54: don de nyid gsal 'debs pa'i phyir nyid la nyid
NK032(khi)004:56: de yang rdo rje zam pa'i rtsa ba'i rgyud ye shes gsang ba'i le'u dang po las /
NK032(khi)004:57: yon tan thams cad ma btsal rang las shar //
NK032(khi)004:58: rtogs pa'i rig pa gnyis med ngang du 'dud //
NK032(khi)004:60: de'i phyir gnyis su med pa'i don brjod du med pa'i ngang de la mchod par brjod pa'o //
NK032(khi)004:61: de yang tshul lam thabs ji ltar du mchod par brjod na /
NK032(khi)004:62: ma nor ma bcos bsam 'das brjod med ngang la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK032(khi)004:64: de la dang po ma nor zhes pa ni /
NK032(khi)004:65: chos spyi dang rang gi mtshan nyid kyi don /
NK032(khi)004:66: sems nyid dngos po gshis kyi gnas lugs /
NK032(khi)004:67: rang byung gi ye shes chen po /
NK032(khi)004:71: skye 'gags med pa'i don chos bzhi dang ldan pa 'dus ma byas pa /
NK032(khi)004:73: gsal la rtog pa med pa /
NK032(khi)004:74: blo'i mtha' zab cing phra ba tsam la yang mi
NK032(khi)004:75: gnas pa nam mkha' dag pa'i dkyil lta bu de
NK032(khi)004:76: phyin ci ma log par rtogs pas na ma nor
NK032(khi)004:77: ba'o // chos bzhi dang ldan pa'i don ma nor ba de nyid las /
NK032(khi)004:78: yar sangs rgyas sgam ste mdzad du mi btub /
NK032(khi)004:79: mar sems can sgrin te bsgyur du mi btub ste
NK032(khi)004:80: gang zag gi blo yis bcos su med pas na
NK032(khi)004:81: ma bcos pa'o // ma bcos pa de nyid yid kyi yul lam /
NK032(khi)004:84: bsam pa'i yul la mi gnas te /
NK032(khi)004:85: bsam du ma btub pas na bsam 'das so //
NK032(khi)004:86: bsam pa las 'das pa de nyid blo'i yul lam /
NK032(khi)004:89: tshig gi yul la mi gnas te /
NK032(khi)004:90: smra ru ma btub pas na brjod med do //
NK032(khi)004:91: brjod du med pa'i don de nyid dus gsum du 'du 'bral med /
NK032(khi)004:94: skye 'gags med par chos bzhi dang ldan pa'i don
NK032(khi)004:95: de las mi 'da' bar gnas pas na ngang ngo
NK032(khi)004:96: // la ni tshig dgar bar byed pas na la zhes bya ste /
NK032(khi)004:99: bsam 'das brjod du med pa'i ngang de rang du dgar nas /
NK032(khi)004:100: mthar thug brjod du med pa'i don de rang yin par ngos 'dzin pas na la zhes bya'o //
NK032(khi)004:101: phyag ni brjod du med pa'i ngang de la nyon
NK032(khi)004:102: mongs pa'i skyon nam shes bya'i sgrib pa mi gnas
NK032(khi)004:103: par ngang du dag pas na phyag ces bya'o //
NK032(khi)004:104: 'tshal ni don brjod du med pa'i ngang de las
NK032(khi)004:105: lhag tu med pas gzhan du ltos ma dgos te
NK032(khi)004:106: brjod du med pa'i don des tshim pas na 'tshal
NK032(khi)004:107: zhes bya'o // lo zhes bya ba ni brjod med
NK032(khi)004:108: kyi ngang du kho thag chod pa'i tshig dang der
NK032(khi)004:109: mthar thug gi don de las bstan du med par
NK032(khi)004:110: blo thag chod pas na lo zhes bya'o //
NK032(khi)004:111: des sngon du mchod par brjod pa bstan pa'o //
NK032(khi)004:112: gdod nas dag pa'i byang chub sems nyid kyis //
NK032(khi)004:113: nyid kyi ngo bo nyid kyi don bstan pa //
NK032(khi)004:114: zhes pa de yang rgyud yin na bshad par dam bca' ba 'byung ba yin te /
NK032(khi)004:115: 'di ni rgyud kyi don mi bslu ba'i man ngag yin pas /
NK032(khi)004:116: chos spyi'i yin lugs bshad pa lta bu gcig min te /
NK032(khi)004:117: don rang gi mtshan nyid sems nyid dngos po'i gnas lugs de /
NK032(khi)004:118: bla mas brda dang ngag gis ngo sprad nas ston pa yin pas na bstan par dam bca' ba'o //
NK032(khi)004:119: de yang gdod nas dag pa ni sems nyid dngos
NK032(khi)004:120: po'i gnas lugs de la rtogs pa rang rgyud du
NK032(khi)004:121: grub pa rdul tsam yang med de /
NK032(khi)004:122: ye gdod ma nas sus kyang ma byas ma bcos
NK032(khi)004:123: pa de la skyon nam dri ma gang yang ma
NK032(khi)004:124: grub cing mi gnas pas na gdod nas dag pa'o
NK032(khi)004:125: // byang ni sems nyid dngos po'i gnas lugs de
NK032(khi)004:126: la bag chags bzang ngan gang gis kyang ma bslad
NK032(khi)004:127: // de / glo bur gzung 'dzin gyi rtog pa
NK032(khi)004:128: gang yang mi gnas par zad pas na byang ba'o
NK032(khi)004:129: // de / // chub ni sems nyid kyi gnas
NK032(khi)004:130: lugs de ma rig cing 'khrul na dug lnga dang
NK032(khi)004:131: ldan par khyab pas na chub dang /
NK032(khi)004:132: gnas lugs de rig cing rtogs na ye shes lnga dang ldan par khyab par na chub pa'o //
NK032(khi)004:133: ye shes rnam pa lnga ni sems nyid ye nas
NK032(khi)004:134: dus gsum du 'du 'bral med pa'i dbyings de ngo
NK032(khi)004:135: shes pas na chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes /
NK032(khi)004:136: de rang gi sems nyid du rig /
NK032(khi)004:137: sems nyid du gsal bar shes pas na me long lta bu'i ye shes /
NK032(khi)004:138: de yang 'khor 'das thams cad la bde bar gshegs
NK032(khi)004:139: pa'i snying pos ye nas mnyam par brdal ba'i don
NK032(khi)004:140: de shes pas na mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes
NK032(khi)004:141: / gnas lugs de'ang yod pa sems can kun gyi rgyud la yod /
NK032(khi)004:142: yin pa 'di ltar snang grags kyi chos thams cad wal le khyug ge ba 'di yin la /
NK032(khi)004:143: gzhan nas btsal ma dgos par rang re'i rgyud la
NK032(khi)004:144: so sor ma 'dres par rtogs rung du byung bas
NK032(khi)004:145: na so sor rtog pa'i ye shes /
NK032(khi)004:146: de ltar ye nas yin pa'i don ji bzhin par rtogs tsa na /
NK032(khi)004:147: ji ltar gnas pa'i don thams cad rang gi rgyud
NK032(khi)004:148: la ye nas grub par shes pas nas bya ba
NK032(khi)004:150: de ni ye shes lnga dang ldan pa'o //
NK032(khi)004:151: de yang ye shes gsang ba las /
NK032(khi)004:152: rang gsal ye nas ma bcos pa'i //
NK032(khi)004:153: don de shes pa ye shes yin //
NK032(khi)004:155: des na ye shes lnga dang ldan par chub ba'i don no //
NK032(khi)004:156: de nas sems zhes bya ba ni /
NK032(khi)004:157: sems ma yin pa'i phyir na sems nyid do //
NK032(khi)004:158: de la sems ni dran pa glo bur ba rtog pa rkyen las skyes pa /
NK032(khi)004:160: 'dus byas kun rdzob yin te rtag mi thub cing
NK032(khi)004:161: rkyen gyis bsgyur bas don dam pa ma yin no
NK032(khi)004:162: // sems nyid ni ye gdod ma nas 'dus ma byas pa /
NK032(khi)004:164: dus gsum du 'gyur ba med pa'i don gsal la rtog pa med pa'i gnas lugs de nyid do //
NK032(khi)004:165: de yang pha rol tu phyin pa las /
NK032(khi)004:167: sh+aa ra dwa ti'i bu sems ma yin pa ni
NK032(khi)004:168: 'gyur ba med pa rnam par rtog pa med pa
NK032(khi)004:169: ste / de ni chos thams cad kyi de bzhin nyid do //
NK032(khi)004:171: sems nyid ni sems ma yin pa'i don gsal la
NK032(khi)004:172: 'gyur ba med cing rtog pa med pa de nyid
NK032(khi)004:173: do // kyis zhes bya ba ni snga ma'i tshig
NK032(khi)004:174: gzhung sdud pa'i phyir te gcod par byed pas na
NK032(khi)004:175: do // kyis so // nyid ni gang zag so
NK032(khi)004:176: so rang rang gang la ston pa de nyid do
NK032(khi)004:177: do // kyis so // // kyi zhes bya ba
NK032(khi)004:178: bar ma 'di ni tshig gong 'og ma chad par
NK032(khi)004:180: ngo bo nyid ni rang gi rgyud la yod pa'i sems nyid dngos po'i gnas lugs de nyid do //
NK032(khi)004:181: de yang rtsa ba'i rgyud ye shes gsang ba las /
NK032(khi)004:182: ngo bo nyid ni gnas lugs te //
NK032(khi)004:184: kyi zhes bya ba tha ma 'di yang tshig gong
NK032(khi)004:185: 'og mi 'bral bar bsdebs par byed pas na kyi'o
NK032(khi)004:186: // kyi ni 'brel bar byed pa'i tshig /
NK032(khi)004:188: don bstan pa ni don de nyid gzhan zhig nas
NK032(khi)004:189: btsal lam bkrus sam phyis nas kha dog gam dbyibs
NK032(khi)004:190: su grub pa 'di yin no zhes mig gis mthong
NK032(khi)004:191: rgyu'am / lag tu gtad rgyu zhig med de /
NK032(khi)004:192: gang zag so so rang rang gi rgyud la yod
NK032(khi)004:193: pa don sems nyid dngos po'i gnas lugs de bla
NK032(khi)004:194: ma'i brda dang ngag gis ngo sprod nas ston pa'o
NK032(khi)004:195: // de yang tshul lam thabs ji ltar du ston na /
NK032(khi)004:196: chos spyi'i 'dod lugs dang don rang gi mtshan nyid du gtan la phab nas /
NK032(khi)004:197: bla ma'i brda dang ngag gis gnad gcig gi steng
NK032(khi)004:198: du rgyud la sbyar nas nyams su myong ba'i don
NK032(khi)004:199: de yid ches the tshom mi za bar bya ba'i
NK032(khi)004:200: don du sangs rgyas kyis gsungs pa'i rgyud lung man
NK032(khi)004:201: ngag dang mi 'gal bar ston pa'o //
NK032(khi)004:202: de yang dang po chos spyi'i 'dod lugs ni /
NK032(khi)004:203: ston pa rnam pa gsum gyis bstan pa'i chos yin te /
NK032(khi)004:204: chos kyi sku'i ston pa dpal kun tu bzang pos /
NK032(khi)004:205: bstan pa byin gyis brlabs nas bstan /
NK032(khi)004:206: bstan pa'i chos mdo sde rgyud sde klong sde gsum yin /
NK032(khi)004:207: de yang don sems la dgongs nas bstan /
NK032(khi)004:208: sems ma rig pa'i log rtog 'khrul par 'dug pa
NK032(khi)004:209: de ma 'khrul par 'chos par bya ba'i phyir mdo
NK032(khi)004:210: sde bstan / sems de yang dran rig rgyun chad med par 'dus pas /
NK032(khi)004:211: chos nyid kyang gsal stong rgyun mi chad par shes par bya ba'i phyir rgyud sde bstan /
NK032(khi)004:212: sems nyid de yang 'dus ma byas pa mi 'dzad pa'i klong du 'dug pas /
NK032(khi)004:213: chos nyid kyang mi 'dzad par gnas pa'i phyir klong sde bstan /
NK032(khi)004:214: de yang yo ga rnam pa gsum yin te /
NK032(khi)004:215: nang pa sde gsum dbang po rab kyi gsum la bstan pa yin te /
NK032(khi)004:216: bsdu na bslab pa gsum du 'dus so //
NK032(khi)004:217: longs spyod rdzogs pa sku'i ston pa dpal rnam par snang mdzad kyis /
NK032(khi)004:219: bstan pa'i chos kri ya yo ga u pa ya gsum bstan /
NK032(khi)004:220: de yang sems can thams cad kyi rgyud la nyon
NK032(khi)004:221: mongs pa rags su song bas lus ngag yid gsum
NK032(khi)004:222: 'byung bas / lus 'dul ba'i phyir kri ya bstan /
NK032(khi)004:223: ngag 'dul ba'i phyir yo ga bstan /
NK032(khi)004:224: yid 'dul ba'i phyir u pa bstan /
NK032(khi)004:225: de yang kri yog rnam gsum yin te /
NK032(khi)004:226: phyi pa sde gsum dbang po 'bring gi gsum la bstan pa yin te /
NK032(khi)004:227: bsdu na bslab pa rnam pa gsum du 'dus so //
NK032(khi)004:228: sprul pa sku'i ston pa sh+aakya thub pas /
NK032(khi)004:230: bstan pa'i chos mngon pa 'dul ba mdo sde gsum bstan /
NK032(khi)004:231: de yang sems can thams cad kyi rgyud la nyon
NK032(khi)004:232: mongs pa phra rags su yod pas lus ngag yid
NK032(khi)004:233: gsum gyi steng du dug gsum byung bas /
NK032(khi)004:234: gti mug 'dul phyir mngon pa bstan /
NK032(khi)004:236: zhe sdang 'dul phyir mdo sde bstan /
NK032(khi)004:237: de yang mngon pa 'dul ba mdo sde gsum yin pas /
NK032(khi)004:238: mtshan nyid sde gsum dbang po tha ma'i gsum la bstan pa yin te /
NK032(khi)004:239: de bsdu na bslab pa rnam pa gsum du 'dus so //
NK032(khi)004:240: de tsho ni dbang po'i rim pa la dgongs te bka' stsal to //
NK032(khi)004:241: de yang nges brjod bla ma'i lung las /
NK032(khi)004:242: nyan thos rang rgyal byang chub sems dpa' gsum //
NK032(khi)004:243: bskal pa gsum gyi sangs rgyas sa la sleb //
NK032(khi)004:244: kri ya yo ga u pa ya dang gsum //
NK032(khi)004:245: mi tshe gsum gyi sangs rgyas sa la sbyor //
NK032(khi)004:246: bskyed dang rdzogs dang rdzogs pa chen po gsum //
NK032(khi)004:247: mi tshe gcig gi sangs rgyas lag tu len //
NK032(khi)004:249: sems can 'khrul pa nyon mongs pa dug gsum je rags su song bas /
NK032(khi)004:250: gti mug las gyur pa nyon mongs pa nyi khri dang chig stong du 'phros /
NK032(khi)004:251: 'dod chags las gyur pa nyon mongs pa nyi khri dang chig stong du 'phros /
NK032(khi)004:252: zhe sdang las gyur pa nyon mongs pa nyi khri dang chis stong du 'phros /
NK032(khi)004:253: der nyon mongs drug khri dang sum stong du byung /
NK032(khi)004:254: de'i steng du dug gsum cha mnyam spyi mthun las
NK032(khi)004:255: gyur pa nyon mongs pa nyi khri dang chig stong
NK032(khi)004:256: du 'phros pas / der nyon mongs pa'i sgo mo brgyad khri dang bzhi stong du byung ngo //
NK032(khi)004:257: de yang gti mug gi gnyen por mngon pa nyi khri dang chig stong gcig gsungs /
NK032(khi)004:258: 'dod chags kyi gnyen por 'dul ba nyi khri dang chig stong gcig gsungs /
NK032(khi)004:259: zhe sdang gi gnyen por mdo sde nyi khri dang chig stong gcig gsungs /
NK032(khi)004:260: der chos kyi sgo mo drug khri dang sum stong du byung /
NK032(khi)004:261: de'i steng du sde snod gsum cha mnyam pa spyi
NK032(khi)004:262: mthun las gyur pa chos kyi sgo mo nyi khri
NK032(khi)004:263: dang chig stong gcig gsungs pas /
NK032(khi)004:264: der nyon mongs pa'i sgo mo brgyad khri dang bzhi
NK032(khi)004:265: stong gi gnyen por chos kyi sgo mo brgyad khri
NK032(khi)004:266: dang bzhi stong gcig gsungs pa ni /
NK032(khi)004:267: gnyen po'i don spros pa la dgongs te rgyas par bka' stsal pa'o //
NK032(khi)004:268: de nas nyon mongs pa'i sgo mo de rnams la bye brag tu phye na /
NK032(khi)004:269: de yang gti mug nyi khri chig stong gi gnyen
NK032(khi)004:270: por mngon pa nyi khri chig stong gsungs pa yin
NK032(khi)004:271: / 'dod chags nyi khri chig stong gi gnyen por
NK032(khi)004:272: 'dul ba nyi khri chig stong gcig gsungs pa yin
NK032(khi)004:273: / / zhe sdang nyi khri chig stong gi gnyen
NK032(khi)004:274: por mdo sde nyi khri chig stong gcig gsungs pa
NK032(khi)004:275: / / yin / dug gsum cha mnyam nyi khri
NK032(khi)004:276: chig stong gi gnyen por sde snod gsum cha mnyam
NK032(khi)004:277: pa nyi khri chig stong gsungs pa yin zhes bshad
NK032(khi)004:278: / / yin / do // de yang nyon mongs
NK032(khi)004:279: pa de rnams bye brag tu phye bas rten 'brel
NK032(khi)004:280: yan lag bcu gcig su byung ba'o //
NK032(khi)004:293: rga shi dang bcu gnyis su bshad pa'o //
NK032(khi)004:294: de yang chos kyi sgo mo la bye brag tu
NK032(khi)004:295: phye bas gsung rab yan lag bcu gnyis su byung
NK032(khi)004:297: lung du bstan pa'i sde dang /
NK032(khi)004:298: tshigs su bcad pa'i sde dang /
NK032(khi)004:299: ched du brjod pa'i sde dang /
NK032(khi)004:301: rtogs pa brjod pa'i sde dang /
NK032(khi)004:303: skyes pa rabs kyi sde dang /
NK032(khi)004:304: shin tu rgyas pa'i sde dang /
NK032(khi)004:305: rmad du byung ba'i sde dang /
NK032(khi)004:306: gtan la dbab pa'i sde dang /
NK032(khi)004:307: dbyangs kyis bsnyad pa'i sde dang bcu gnyis su bshad pa'o //
NK032(khi)004:308: de ni bye brag tu dbye ba'i don la dgongs te rgyas bsdus 'bring po ru bka' stsal pa'o //
NK032(khi)004:309: de yang nyon mongs pa'i sgo mo bsdu na ngo bo rang bzhin mtshan nyid gsum du 'dus te /
NK032(khi)004:310: de yang ngo bo ma rig par byung /
NK032(khi)004:312: mtshan nyid sdug bsngal du nyams su myong ba'o //
NK032(khi)004:313: de yang chos kyi sgo mo bsdu na bslab pa rnam pa gsum du 'dus te /
NK032(khi)004:314: lhag pa shes rab kyi bslab pa /
NK032(khi)004:315: lhag pa tshul khrims kyi bslab pa /
NK032(khi)004:316: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi bslab pa dang gsum mo //
NK032(khi)004:317: nyon mongs pa dug lnga'am dug gsum ni ngo bo
NK032(khi)004:318: rang bzhin mtshan nyid gsum du 'dus pa yin la
NK032(khi)004:319: / chos kyi sgo mo gsang sngags rgyud sde bzhi'am /
NK032(khi)004:320: mtshan nyid sde snod gsum ni bslab pa rnam pa gsum du 'dus pa yin pas /
NK032(khi)004:321: de ni gsum gsum du bsdu ba'i don la dgongs te nyung la 'dus par bka' stsal pa'o //
NK032(khi)004:322: de yang shes rab sdud pa las /
NK032(khi)004:323: ma rig 'khrul 'khor 'di la zad med 'phel ba med //
NK032(khi)004:325: de yan chad ni chos spyi'i mtshan nyid dam 'dod lugs yin te /
NK032(khi)004:326: dper na 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal po dmus long
NK032(khi)004:327: du song ba spyan ma dbye ba dang 'dra ste
NK032(khi)004:328: / rin po che sna bdun yod pa'i sgra'am go
NK032(khi)004:329: yul tsam las rin po che'i dngos po ma mthong
NK032(khi)004:330: ba bzhin du don spyi'i go yul tsam du lus
NK032(khi)004:331: / pa'o // de yang don rang gi mtshan nyid du nye bar bsdu na /
NK032(khi)004:332: dang po nyon mongs pa'i rtsa ba ngo bo rang
NK032(khi)004:333: bzhin mtshan nyid gsum rang gi rgyud la ngos bzung
NK032(khi)004:334: ba ni / de yang rang gi rgyud la ye
NK032(khi)004:335: nas yod pa'i sems nyid kyi ngo bo de kho
NK032(khi)004:336: na ma rtogs pa la ngo bo ma rig pa
NK032(khi)004:337: zer ba ste gti mug yin /
NK032(khi)004:338: sems nyid kyi ngo bo chos bzhi dang ldan pa'i gnas lugs de ma rig pas /
NK032(khi)004:339: de ma yin pa la der 'dzin gyi shes pa
NK032(khi)004:340: bag chags kyi rtog pa gcig byung ba de ni
NK032(khi)004:341: rang bzhin 'khrul pa yin te 'dod chags yin /
NK032(khi)004:342: ma rig pas der 'dzin gyi rtog pa la brten
NK032(khi)004:343: nas chags sdang gi mtshan nyid nyon mongs par byung
NK032(khi)004:344: ba de ni mtshan nyid sdug bsngal yin te zhe
NK032(khi)004:345: sdang yin no // de yang dper na rang gi
NK032(khi)004:346: grib ma rang du ngo ma shes pa de dgrar
NK032(khi)004:347: mthong nas bred pa de rang gi grib ma yin
NK032(khi)004:348: par ngo ma shes kyi bar du bros pas mi
NK032(khi)004:350: rang gi sems nyid kyi gnas lugs ma rig cing
NK032(khi)004:351: ma rtogs pas 'khrul pa'i dbang gis sdug bsngal du
NK032(khi)004:353: da bla ma'i gdams ngag gis snga ma'i nyon mongs
NK032(khi)004:354: pa de thams cad rang gi ma rig pas 'khrul
NK032(khi)004:355: par shes nas / da sems nyid dngos po'i gnas
NK032(khi)004:356: lugs ma rig pa med cing 'khrul pa chod nas
NK032(khi)004:357: sdug bsngal dang bral ba gcig tu ma rtogs na
NK032(khi)004:358: par shes nas / / ma rig cing 'khrul pa
NK032(khi)004:359: spangs pas mi 'dzad de 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal 'ba'
NK032(khi)004:361: de yang rtsa ba'i rgyud ye shes gsang ba las /
NK032(khi)004:362: rang gsal dgongs pa'i thugs ma rig /
NK032(khi)004:363: 'dzin pa'i cha la gang gnas kyang //
NK032(khi)004:366: gnyis pa chos kyi sgo mo'i bslab pa gsum gyi don rang gi rgyud la ngos bzung ba ni /
NK032(khi)004:367: sems nyid dngos po'i gnas lugs de la gzung 'dzin
NK032(khi)004:368: gyi blo yi mtha' zab cing phra ba tsam yang
NK032(khi)004:369: mi gnas par spros pa dang bral ba gcig tu
NK032(khi)004:370: rig cing rtogs pa de ni shes rab /
NK032(khi)004:371: gnas lugs spros pa dang bral ba de la 'du byed blo yi bye brag gang yang med de /
NK032(khi)004:372: chos nyid kyi ngang ngam tshul de las mi 'da' ba de ni tshul khrims /
NK032(khi)004:373: chos nyid kyi ngang de la nyon mongs pa'am /
NK032(khi)004:374: chos nyid tsam gyi blo'i mtha' zab cing phra ba tsam yang mi gnas te /
NK032(khi)004:375: nyon mongs pa'am chos nyid de la gnas pa dang bral ba yang med de /
NK032(khi)004:376: de bzhin du 'du 'bral med pa'i ngang las mi 'gyur ba de ni bsam gtan yin no //
NK032(khi)004:377: de yang theg pa chen po rgyud bla ma las /
NK032(khi)004:378: spros med rtogs pa shes rab yin //
NK032(khi)004:379: 'du byed med pa tshul khrims yin //
NK032(khi)004:380: gnas med mi 'bral bsam gtan yin //
NK032(khi)004:382: de ni don rang gi mtshan nyid du nye bar
NK032(khi)004:383: bsdu ba'i don la dgongs te bka' stsal pa yin
NK032(khi)004:384: no // de yang chos spyi'i rnam dag bstan pa ni /
NK032(khi)004:385: dper na rdo rje gdan bltar 'dod pa'i mi rgyus med gcig la /
NK032(khi)004:386: rdo rje gdan 'di lta bu zhig yod pa yin zhes lo rgyus bshad pa dang 'dra ste /
NK032(khi)004:387: don spyi dang rang gi mtshan nyid kyi yin lugs thos pas /
NK032(khi)004:388: de 'dra ba gcig yod tshod 'dug snyam pa'i go
NK032(khi)004:389: yul tsam las don nyams su ma myong bas yid
NK032(khi)004:391: de yang chos kyi rnam pa tsam du lus pa'o //
NK032(khi)004:392: de yang shin tu nye ba'i don la dgongs te
NK032(khi)004:393: don rang gi mtshan nyid snying po'i don lhan cig
NK032(khi)004:394: skyes pa la sbyor ba ni /
NK032(khi)004:395: de yang chos spyi dang rang gi mtshan nyid kyi
NK032(khi)004:396: don sems nyid dngos po'i gshis kyi gnas lugs rang
NK032(khi)004:397: byung gi ye shes chen po de gnad gcig gi
NK032(khi)004:398: steng du bla ma'i brda dang ngag gis rgyud la
NK032(khi)004:399: sbyar bas / nyon mongs pa'i rtsa ba ngo bo rang bzhin mtshan nyid gsum gnas 'gyur nas /
NK032(khi)004:400: chos kyi sgo mo'i rtsa ba bslab pa gsum rgyud
NK032(khi)004:401: la shar nas nyams su myong ba'i don de lung
NK032(khi)004:402: dang man ngag dang mi 'gal bar ston pa'o //
NK032(khi)004:403: de yang gzhan zhig na re /
NK032(khi)004:404: de tsug tu bstan du cang btub bam /
NK032(khi)004:405: btub na dang khyed thabs re che ste /
NK032(khi)004:406: brdzun nam 'ud du mi 'agro'am zer na /
NK032(khi)004:407: ded thabs che ba dang mkhas pa rang yin byas la khas blangs /
NK032(khi)004:408: khas blangs pa ni dam bcas pa yin /
NK032(khi)004:409: dam bcas pas mi 'gal bar ston pa de ni gdams ngag che ba rang yin gsungs /
NK032(khi)004:410: de yang rdzogs pa chen po kun byed rgyal po las /
NK032(khi)004:411: che ba'i ye shes rnyed dka' bas //
NK032(khi)004:412: shes rab thabs la brten pas 'grub //
NK032(khi)004:413: ming tsam gzhan la brten 'dra yang //
NK032(khi)004:414: mngon sum bde ba rang la 'byung //
NK032(khi)004:416: rtsa ba'i rgyud ye shes gsang ba las /
NK032(khi)004:417: che ba'i ye shes gsang ba 'di //
NK032(khi)004:418: shes rab thabs la brten pas 'grub //
NK032(khi)004:420: de yang shes rab dmigs su med pa dang thabs
NK032(khi)004:421: yengs pa med pa la brten nas 'grub pa yin
NK032(khi)004:422: te / de yang ji ltar du ston na chos spyi'i rnam par shigs kyis bshig /
NK032(khi)004:423: don rang gi tshan nyid du 'ub kyis bsdus nas /
NK032(khi)004:424: gnad kyi brda bzhis rgyud la sbyar nas ston pa ni /
NK032(khi)004:426: mi rtog pa gnad kyi brda /
NK032(khi)004:428: dbyer mi phyed pa gnad kyi brda dang bzhi'o //
NK032(khi)004:429: de yang dbang po'i sgo ma bkag pa /
NK032(khi)004:432: lce'i rtse mo gang la'ang mi brten par 'jog pa dang bzhi'o //
NK032(khi)004:433: de'i dus su don gsal ba /
NK032(khi)004:436: ngo bo dbyer mi phyed par rgyud la 'char ba'o //
NK032(khi)004:437: de yang gsal ba de dbang po'i sgo ma bkag pa las byung /
NK032(khi)004:438: mi rtog pa de dbang po'i sgo ma g.yos pa las byung ma /
NK032(khi)004:439: bde ba de 'og rlung yid tsam zin pa las byung /
NK032(khi)004:440: dbyer mi phyed pa de lce'i rtse mo gang la yang ma brten pa las byung ba'o //
NK032(khi)004:441: de yang dbang po'i sgo ma bkag par /
NK032(khi)004:442: sems nyid de rang du rig cing rang gsal bas
NK032(khi)004:443: nyon mongs pa'i rtsa ba ngo bo ma rig pa
NK032(khi)004:444: ma spangs par gnas 'gyur nas spros pa med par
NK032(khi)004:445: dag pa de chos kyi sgo mo'i rtsa ba shes
NK032(khi)004:447: de ni mtshan nyid sde snod gsum gyi dbang du
NK032(khi)004:448: byas na don rig cing gsal ba de mngon pa'i
NK032(khi)004:449: don no // gsang sngags rgyud sde bzhi'i dbang du
NK032(khi)004:450: byas na don rig cing rtogs par bya bas nas
NK032(khi)004:452: dbang po'i sgo ma g.yos pas nyon mongs pa'i rtsa
NK032(khi)004:453: ba rang bzhin 'khrul pa ma spangs par gnas 'gyur
NK032(khi)004:454: nas mi rtog pa de chos kyi sgo mo'i rtsa
NK032(khi)004:455: ba tshul khrims kyi bslab pa'o //
NK032(khi)004:456: de yang sde snod gsum gyi dbang du byas na
NK032(khi)004:457: rtog pa la mi gnas pas nyon mongs pa zhi
NK032(khi)004:459: rgyud sde bzhi'i dbang du byas na mi rtog pa
NK032(khi)004:460: chos nyid kyi don la spyod pas na spyod pa'i
NK032(khi)004:461: rgyud do // 'og rlung yid tsam zin pas nyon
NK032(khi)004:462: mongs pa'i rtsa ba mtshan nyid sdug bsngal ma spangs
NK032(khi)004:464: lus sems yod du mi tshor bar bde ba de
NK032(khi)004:465: chos kyi sgo mo'i rtsa ba ting nge 'dzin gyi
NK032(khi)004:466: bslab pa / de ni sde snod gsum gyi yod
NK032(khi)004:467: med gnyis su ma grub pa'i don gnyis med gcig
NK032(khi)004:468: tu mdor bsdus shing zug rdu med par bde bas
NK032(khi)004:469: bslab pa / mdo sde'i don / rgyud sde bzhi
NK032(khi)004:470: las gnyis su med pas bde ba'i don rnal ma
NK032(khi)004:471: la 'byor bas na rnal 'byor gyi rgyud do //
NK032(khi)004:472: lce'i rtse mo gang la yang ma brten pas gsal ba /
NK032(khi)004:474: bde ba gsum tshig la tha dad kyang don la ngo bo dbyer mi phyed de /
NK032(khi)004:475: nang na bsam pa'i blo med /
NK032(khi)004:476: phyin brjod pa'i tshig med de /
NK032(khi)004:477: dbyer mi phyed pa'i dus na dbyer phyed bya ba'am /
NK032(khi)004:478: mi phyed bya ba'i blo'i mtha' 'am tshig gi mtha'
NK032(khi)004:479: zab cing phra ba tsam yang mi gnas te 'du
NK032(khi)004:480: shes zad pa'o // de ni sde snod gsum gyi dgongs pa mthar phyin pa yin te /
NK032(khi)004:482: ji srid 'du shes yod kyi bar //
NK032(khi)004:483: theg pa'i mtha' la thug pa med //
NK032(khi)004:484: 'du shes med cing gnas med na //
NK032(khi)004:487: rgyud sde bzhi'i don kyang mthar phyin pa yin te /
NK032(khi)004:488: blo'i mtha' zab cing phra ba tsam yang mi gnas
NK032(khi)004:489: pa'i don rnal ma blo'i spyod yul du ma gyur
NK032(khi)004:490: pa la 'byor cing mngon du gyur te /
NK032(khi)004:491: de las lhag pa'i don gzhan na med pas rgyud mthar thug pa yang de rang yin no //
NK032(khi)004:492: de bas na mtshan nyid sde snod gsum dang gsang
NK032(khi)004:493: sngags rgyud sde bzhi yang gcig gi khong na gcig
NK032(khi)004:494: yod pa yin pas na bslab pa gsum du don
NK032(khi)004:495: gcig par 'dus / bslab pa gsum rang gi rgyud
NK032(khi)004:496: la sbyar bas don gsal ba mi rtog pa bde
NK032(khi)004:498: de gsum yang ngo bo dbyer mi phyed pas chos kyi dbyings gcig tu 'dus /
NK032(khi)004:499: dbyer med phyed pa'i dus na dbyer phyed ces bya
NK032(khi)004:500: ba'am dbyer mi phyed bya ba'i blo'i mtha' zab cing
NK032(khi)004:501: phra ba tsam yang mi gnas te /
NK032(khi)004:502: de nyid la yang ma zhen pas na chos kyi dbyings rnam par dag pa'o //
NK032(khi)004:503: chos kyi dbyings rnam par dag pa de don chos nyid kyi rdo rje'o //
NK032(khi)004:504: sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa don chos nyid rdo rje
NK032(khi)004:505: zam ma chad pas na rdo rje'i zam pa zhes
NK032(khi)004:506: bya'o // de yang 'og ma rnams su rna ba nas rna bar brgyud /
NK032(khi)004:507: gong ma rnams su barda'am thabs tshegs med pa 'phrul lta bu gcig bstan pas /
NK032(khi)004:508: don mig phye ba lta bur lhag ger mthong ba'i
NK032(khi)004:509: dgongs pa gcig nas gcig tu brgyud pas rdo rje
NK032(khi)004:511: de yang zam pa chen po dbang gi man ngag las /
NK032(khi)004:512: rna brgyud 'phrul mig brgyud pa'i rdo rje zam pa yin //
NK032(khi)004:514: de yang dang po bla ma'i brda dang ngag gis ngo sprod nas /
NK032(khi)004:515: rang gi rgyud la bstan nas byung bas /
NK032(khi)004:516: chos kyi chos nyid blo'i spros pa dang bral ba rang gi rgyud la nyams myong du byung bas /
NK032(khi)004:517: sems kyi sems nyid rnam par rtogs pa med pa /
NK032(khi)004:518: de gnyis gnyis su med pa'i bde ba dbyer med
NK032(khi)004:519: mi phyed pa nam mkha'i mtshan nyid blo'i mtha' zab
NK032(khi)004:520: cing phra ba tsam la yang mi gnas pa'o //
NK032(khi)004:521: de tsa na mtshan nyid gsum gcig tu 'dres pas
NK032(khi)004:522: 'di bzhag phyis mi len gyi dgongs pa rang rig
NK032(khi)004:523: dang po'i sar tshud pa zhes bya ba ste /
NK032(khi)004:524: de tsa na skye ba 'di bzhag nas gzhan don
NK032(khi)004:525: du sems bskyed kyi sprul pa go ma 'gags tsam
NK032(khi)004:526: las 'khor ba rang rgyud pa'i lus mi len pa'o
NK032(khi)004:527: // rang rig dngos po'i gnas lugs rtogs nas gzhi
NK032(khi)004:528: dang po ma 'khrul pa'i steng du rang sa zin
NK032(khi)004:530: des na rang gi grib ma rang gis ngo shes pa dang 'dra ste /
NK032(khi)004:532: rgyal po dmus long spyan phye ba dang 'dra ste /
NK032(khi)004:533: yon tan gzhan nas btsal mi dgos par da rang la tshang /
NK032(khi)004:534: rdo rje gdan du brtol nas mthong ba dang 'dra ste /
NK032(khi)004:535: bshad du blta mi dgos par rang gi sems nyid de nyid sangs rgyas su rtogs pa'o //
NK032(khi)004:536: de yang bstan pa tsam gyis mi rtogs te blta dgos /
NK032(khi)004:537: bltas pa tsam gyis mi chog ste mthong dgos /
NK032(khi)004:538: don mthong ba tsam gyis mi chog ste goms shing 'dris dgos /
NK032(khi)004:539: 'dris pa tsam gyis mi chog ste don mngon du gyur dgos /
NK032(khi)004:540: don de la blta na sangs rgyas gyi dgongs pa la blta /
NK032(khi)004:541: don de ngo shes na sangs rgyas ngo shes /
NK032(khi)004:542: don de dang 'dris nas sangs rgyas dang 'dris /
NK032(khi)004:543: mngon du gyur na sangs rgyas pa rang yin gsungs so //
NK032(khi)004:544: rang gi sems nyid rtogs pa mngon du gyur pa
NK032(khi)004:545: de ni snying po'i don rang gi sems nyid sangs
NK032(khi)004:546: rgyas kyi dgongs pa dang lhan cig tu skyes /
NK032(khi)004:547: don la dgongs te bka' stsal pa'o //
NK032(khi)004:549: bde gshegs snying po 'gro kun yongs la khyab //
NK032(khi)004:550: ces pa dang yang mthun la mi 'gal lo //
NK032(khi)004:551: de yang sems nyid rtogs pa mngon du gyur pa de sangs rgyas yin par cis shes na /
NK032(khi)004:552: sangs rgyas kyis gsungs pa'i lung dang man ngag gis
NK032(khi)004:553: mi 'gal bar yid ches the tshom mi za bar
NK032(khi)004:555: man ngag rdo rje zam pa 'di ru gtan la 'bebs pa'o //
NK032(khi)004:556: de yang gsang sngags don gyi tshad ma las /
NK032(khi)004:557: lung dang man ngag stobs kyis rang rig nges par 'char //
NK032(khi)004:559: lung dgyes pa'i rdo rje brtag pa gnyis pa las /
NK032(khi)004:560: sems can thams cad sangs rgyas nyid //
NK032(khi)004:561: 'on kyang glo bur dri mas bsgrib //
NK032(khi)004:562: dri ma dag na sangs rgyas nyid //
NK032(khi)004:564: de yang glo bur gyi dri ma ngo bor ma rig pa dang /
NK032(khi)004:566: mtshan nyid sdug bsngal gsum gyis sgrib pa de /
NK032(khi)004:567: ngo bo ma rig pa gsal bar dag /
NK032(khi)004:568: rang bzhin 'khrul pa mi rtog par dag /
NK032(khi)004:569: mtshan nyid sdug bsngal bde bar dag /
NK032(khi)004:570: gsal ba mi rtog pa bde ba gsum dbyer mi
NK032(khi)004:571: phyed pa de blo'i mtha' zab cing phra ba tsam
NK032(khi)004:572: la yang mi gnas par dag pas na sangs rgyas
NK032(khi)004:573: nyid de / 'phags pa 'da' ka ye shes las /
NK032(khi)004:574: sems ni ye shes 'byung ba'i rgyu //
NK032(khi)004:575: sangs rgyas gzhan nas ma 'tshol zhig /
NK032(khi)004:577: sems nyid dngos po'i gnas lugs ye nas yin pa'i don de shes tsa na /
NK032(khi)004:578: sangs rgyas de rang yin pas gzhan nas btsal mi dgos pa'o //
NK032(khi)004:579: rtsa ba'i rgyud ye shes gsang ba'i le'u brgyad pa las /
NK032(khi)004:580: ye nas chos skur gnas pa la //
NK032(khi)004:581: sangs rgyas gzhan nas btsal du med //
NK032(khi)004:583: rdzogs pa chen po rmad du byung las /
NK032(khi)004:584: ji ltar byung zhing srid pa dang //
NK032(khi)004:585: snang zhing grags pa thams cad kun //
NK032(khi)004:586: thams cad rang rig kun tu bzang //
NK032(khi)004:587: sangs rgyas gzhan nas btsal du med //
NK032(khi)004:589: sgrub sde bcu gsum gyi don bsdus pa rna brgyud lung gi phreng ba las /
NK032(khi)004:590: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten thams cad na //
NK032(khi)004:591: sangs rgyas btsal bas mi rnyed de //
NK032(khi)004:592: rang sems rtogs na sangs rgyas yin //
NK032(khi)004:593: de las gzhan du ma 'tshol zhig /
NK032(khi)004:595: rang sems rtogs na sangs rgyas yin par rgyud lung
NK032(khi)004:596: man ngag thams cad nas 'cham par bshad 'dug pas
NK032(khi)004:597: na / rang sems rtogs pas sangs rgyas yin par yid ches the tshom mi za bar bstan pa'o //
NK032(khi)004:598: mdo sde nges par 'jog pa las /
NK032(khi)004:599: dge sbyong chen pos 'di skad gsungs //
NK032(khi)004:600: sdig pa ci yang mi bya zhing //
NK032(khi)004:601: dge ba phun sum tshogs par spyad //
NK032(khi)004:602: rang gi sems ni yongs su 'dul //
NK032(khi)004:603: 'di ni sangs rgyas bstan pa yin //
NK032(khi)004:605: de yang gong du chos spyi dang rang gi mtshan
NK032(khi)004:606: nyid de bla ma'i brda dang ngag gis gnad gcig
NK032(khi)004:607: gi steng du rang gi rgyud la sbyar bas nyon
NK032(khi)004:608: mongs pa'i rtsa ba ngo bo ma rig pa dag
NK032(khi)004:610: mtshan nyid sdug bsngal dang bral bas na /
NK032(khi)004:611: sdig pa ci yang ma byas pa'o //
NK032(khi)004:612: chos kyi sgo mo'i rtsa ba bslab pa gsum gsal ba /
NK032(khi)004:614: bde ba gsum du rang gi rgyud la shar bas na /
NK032(khi)004:615: dge ba phun sum tshogs par spyad pa'o //
NK032(khi)004:616: de gsum yang ngo bo dbyer mi phyed /
NK032(khi)004:617: dbyer mi phyed pa'i dus na dbyer phyed bya ba'am /
NK032(khi)004:618: mi phyed bya ba'i blo'i mtha' zab cing phra ba
NK032(khi)004:619: tsam la yang mi gnas pas na rang gi sems
NK032(khi)004:621: blo'i mtha' zab cing phra ba tsam yang mi gnas
NK032(khi)004:622: pa de don dam pa blo'i spyod yul du ma
NK032(khi)004:623: gyur pas na don chos kyi rdo rje /
NK032(khi)004:624: 'bras bu gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa'i dgongs pa zam ma chad pas na rdo rje'i zam pa /
NK032(khi)004:625: sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa de yang dang po bla ma'i brda dang ngag gis ngo sprad nas /
NK032(khi)004:626: rig cing rtogs pa'i don de sangs rgyas kyi dgongs
NK032(khi)004:627: pa yin par yid ches the tshom mi za bar
NK032(khi)004:629: sangs rgyas kyis gsungs pa'i lung dang man ngag dang mi 'gal bar ngo sprad nas bstan pas na /
NK032(khi)004:630: 'di ni sangs rgyas bstan pa yin //
NK032(khi)004:633: nyams su myong ba'i don de man ngag lung dang mi 'gal bar bstan pa thal lo //
NK032(khi)004:634: de'i gong ma des chos spyi dang rang gi mtshan
NK032(khi)004:635: nyid kyi don bla ma'i gdams ngag gis rang gi
NK032(khi)004:636: rgyud la sbyar nas nyams su myong ba'i don thal
NK032(khi)004:637: lo // de'i gong ma des chos spyi dang rang
NK032(khi)004:638: gi mtshan nyid snying po'i don lhan cig skyes pa
NK032(khi)004:640: de'i gong ma des nye bar bsdu ba'i don la dgongs pa thal lo //
NK032(khi)004:641: der nye bar bsdu ba'i don la dgongs pa dang gcig /
NK032(khi)004:642: snying po'i don lhan cig skyes pa la dgongs pa dang gnyis /
NK032(khi)004:643: de bla ma'i gdams ngag gis rang gi rgyud la sbyar nas nyams su myong ba'i don dang gsum /
NK032(khi)004:644: don de man ngag lung dang mi 'gal bar bstan
NK032(khi)004:645: pa dang bzhis don rang gi mtshan nyid la yid
NK032(khi)004:647: de'i gong ma des nyung ngur bsdu ba'i don la
NK032(khi)004:648: dgongs te nyon mongs pa dang chos kyi sgo mo
NK032(khi)004:649: gsum gsum drug tu bsdu ba thal lo //
NK032(khi)004:650: de'i gong ma des rgyas bsdus 'bring po bye brag
NK032(khi)004:651: tu phye ba'i don la dgongs te chos dang nyon
NK032(khi)004:652: mongs pa bcu gnyis mtshan nyid nyi shu rtsa bzhir
NK032(khi)004:654: de'i gong ma des spros pa'i don la dgongs te
NK032(khi)004:655: nyon mongs pa dang chos kyi sgo mo brgyad khri
NK032(khi)004:656: bzhi stong tshan pa gnyis su spros te khri tsho
NK032(khi)004:657: bcu drug dang stong tsho brgyad du rgyas par bka'
NK032(khi)004:658: stsal pa thal ba lags so //
NK032(khi)004:659: de'i gong ma des ston pa rnam par gsum gyis dbang po'i rim pa la dgongs te /
NK032(khi)004:660: rab 'bring tha ma gsum la dgur phyes nas bstan pa'o //
NK032(khi)004:661: der dbang po'i rim pa la dgongs nas bstan pa dang gcig /
NK032(khi)004:662: spros pa'i don la dgongs nas bstan pa dang gnyis /
NK032(khi)004:663: dbye ba'i don la dgongs nas bstan pa dang gsum /
NK032(khi)004:664: bsdu ba'i don la dgongs nas bstan pa dang bzhis chos spyi'i mtshan nyid dam 'dod lugs bstan pa'o //
NK032(khi)004:665: de'i gong ma des don bstan pa thal /
NK032(khi)004:666: de'i gong ma des nyid kyi ngo bo nyid thal /
NK032(khi)004:667: de'i gong ma des byang chub sems nyid thal /
NK032(khi)004:668: de'i gong ma des gdod nas dag pa thal /
NK032(khi)004:669: gdod nas dag pa dang gcig /
NK032(khi)004:670: byang chub sems nyid dang gnyis /
NK032(khi)004:671: nyid kyi ngo bo nyid dang gsum /
NK032(khi)004:672: don bstan pa dang bzhis bstan par dam bca' ba'i rtsa ba bstan pa'o //
NK032(khi)004:673: de'i gong ma des phyag 'tshal ba thal lo //
NK032(khi)004:674: de'i gong ma des ngang la thal mo //
NK032(khi)004:675: de'i gong ma des bsam 'das brjod med thal lo //
NK032(khi)004:676: de'i gong ma des ma nor ma bcos thal lo //
NK032(khi)004:677: der ma nor ma bcos dang gcig /
NK032(khi)004:680: phyag 'tshal lo dang bzhis mchod par brjod pa bstan pa'o //
NK032(khi)004:681: der gang thal na sngon du mchod par brjod cing
NK032(khi)004:682: bstan par dam bca' ba des chos spyi'i rnam pa
NK032(khi)004:683: de don rang gi mtshan nyid du bla ma'i brda
NK032(khi)004:684: dang ngag gis rgyud la sbyar nas nyams su myong
NK032(khi)004:685: ba'i don de yid ches the tshom mi za bar
NK032(khi)004:686: bya ba'i phyir / sangs rgyas kyis gsungs pa'i man ngag lung dang ni 'gal bar ston pa'o //
NK032(khi)004:687: des ni phyi nang gyi bar gcod kyi dmigs thad
NK032(khi)004:688: ka ru sel ba shan 'byed kyi gdams ngag bya
NK032(khi)004:689: ba tshig don gsal ba lags so //
NK032(khi)004:690: hril gyis dril bas de yan chad kyis spyi don
NK032(khi)004:691: dang po klad kyi don mchod par brjod cing bshad
NK032(khi)004:692: par dam bca' ba'i skabs thal ba lags so //
NK032(khi)004:693: gang zag dbang po rab gcig la don go zhing rtogs par 'dod pa la /
NK032(khi)004:694: rdo rje zam pa zhes pa'i mtshan thos pa'am /
NK032(khi)004:695: mchod par brjod cing bstan par dam bca' ba gnyis
NK032(khi)004:696: kyis ngo bor nyid kyi don bstan pa de tsam
NK032(khi)004:697: zhig gis chog / gang zag dbang po 'bring la /
NK032(khi)004:698: dang po don gtan la 'bebs pa'i dus /
NK032(khi)004:699: rna brgyud lung gi gter chen dgrol ba dang gcig /
NK032(khi)004:700: sgom med don gyi gzer chen gdab pa dang gnyis /
NK032(khi)004:701: re dogs med par dbyings su gtad pa dang gsum mo //
NK032(khi)004:702: bar du gtan la phebs pa'i dus su /
NK032(khi)004:703: dbang dang gis rdzogs pas sgom sgrub dge ba'i chos
NK032(khi)004:704: la mi ltos par gtan la phebs pa dang gcig
NK032(khi)004:705: / sku rang chas su gyur pas gnyis 'dzin las grol bar gtan la phebs pa dang gnyis /
NK032(khi)004:706: don gcig tu rtogs bas rtog dpyod las 'das par gtan la phebs pa dang gsum /
NK032(khi)004:707: tha ma nyams su shar ba'i dus su /
NK032(khi)004:708: 'di ni rdo rje'i lam mchog dang gcig /
NK032(khi)004:709: skal ldan 'bad pa med par grol ba dang gnyis /
NK032(khi)004:710: grol ba rang grol gzhan las min pa dang gsum /
NK032(khi)004:713: nyams su shar ba'i gzhung dus dang gsum gyis bshad pas grol /
NK032(khi)004:714: tha ma zhib tshags 'bru bsnon dpe don man ngag
NK032(khi)004:715: lung dang mi 'gal bar bshad pa ni yid ches
NK032(khi)004:716: the tshom mi za ba ru ston pa'o //
NK032(khi)004:717: spyi don gnyis pa de ltar bstan pa'i don la gsum de /
NK032(khi)004:718: don dang po gtan la 'bebs pa'i dus dang gcig /
NK032(khi)004:719: bar du gtan la phebs pa'i dus dang gnyis /
NK032(khi)004:720: tha ma nyams su shar ba'i dus dang gsum mo //
NK032(khi)004:721: don dang po gtan la 'bebs pa'i dus la gsum ste /
NK032(khi)004:722: rna brgyud lung gi gter chen dgrol ba dang gcig /
NK032(khi)004:723: sgom med don gyi gzer chen gdab pa dang gnyis /
NK032(khi)004:724: re dogs med par dbyings su gtad pa dang gsum mo //
NK032(khi)004:725: dang po rna brgyud lung gi gter chen dgrol ba la go ba dang /
NK032(khi)004:727: go ba ni mdor bstan pa'o //
NK032(khi)004:728: tshig don ni rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK032(khi)004:730: dang po rna brgyud ces pa'i go ba ni gang zag grub thob rnams so //
NK032(khi)004:731: snyan nas snyan du brgyud pa yin pas na rna brgyud ces pa'o //
NK032(khi)004:732: lung gi zhes pa ni rig 'dzin rnams so //
NK032(khi)004:733: barda'am lung bstan pa tsam gyis grol bas na lung gi zhes pa'o //
NK032(khi)004:734: rna brgyud ces pa sngon la 'ong ba ni /
NK032(khi)004:735: tshig sdeb sbyor legs par bya ba'am /
NK032(khi)004:736: da lta snyan nas snyan du brgyud pa yin pas sngon la 'ong ba'o //
NK032(khi)004:737: lung gi zhes pa phyi la 'ong ba ni gong
NK032(khi)004:738: ma rnams kyi lo rgyus sam gtam rgyud dam barda'am
NK032(khi)004:739: lung bstan pa tsam du 'dug pas na phyi la
NK032(khi)004:740: 'ong ba'o // gter chen dgrol ba'i go ba ni /
NK032(khi)004:741: dbul mos gter rnyed pa'i dpes mtshon pa yin la /
NK032(khi)004:742: de yang rgya gar gyi yul sing+ga la bya ba na /
NK032(khi)004:743: yab tshong dpon phyi'i rgya mtsho la nor bu len pa'i rigs gcig gis /
NK032(khi)004:744: phyi rabs la phan pa srid snyam nas /
NK032(khi)004:745: sgyed po ma sgyed mi sgul ba de'i 'og tu gser phye bum pa gang sbas nas bzhag pas /
NK032(khi)004:746: dus lan gcig tshong dpon de shi nas bza' mi de min tsho zad pa'i shul du /
NK032(khi)004:747: bu mo ltog ma gcig lus yod tsa na /
NK032(khi)004:748: yul gcig na gter sa'i dpyad shes pa'i mi sa
NK032(khi)004:749: 'og sa steng sa bla gsum na gter ram nor
NK032(khi)004:750: ci yod pa mthong zhing shes pa gcig yod pa
NK032(khi)004:751: des / dus lan gcig sing+ga la'i yul der brtol
NK032(khi)004:752: nas bltas pas dbul mo bza' ba dang gyon pa
NK032(khi)004:753: des / med de / nor du ras gos hrul po gcig las med pa /
NK032(khi)004:754: de yang nyin mo smad du dkris nas 'tsho ba bya 'tshol byed pa nang lto nang 'tshol /
NK032(khi)004:756: nub mo ras gos de gnyis lteb byas nas shul
NK032(khi)004:757: du bkab nas nyal ba las gzhan ci yang med
NK032(khi)004:758: pa'i dbul mo de'i sgyed po'i 'og na phas gter
NK032(khi)004:759: du sbas pa'i gser phye bum pa gang 'dug pa
NK032(khi)004:760: de mthong nas / gter sa'i dpyad shes pa'i mi des dbul mo de'i drung du phyin nas /
NK032(khi)004:761: dbul mo khyod la bza' ba dang gyon pa med dam zhes dris pas /
NK032(khi)004:764: nga la ni ci yang med do zer bas /
NK032(khi)004:765: gter sa'i dpyad shes pa des nga la ci yang 'dod pa min cing /
NK032(khi)004:766: khyod rang gi sgyed po ma sgyed kyi 'og na
NK032(khi)004:767: yab kyis sbas pa'i gser phye bum pa gang 'dug
NK032(khi)004:768: gi / de khyod rang gis thon la bde bar longs spyod cig /
NK032(khi)004:769: gzhan la rag mi lus par skyid po 'ong gis byas pas /
NK032(khi)004:771: de cang bden nam bden na dga' ste /
NK032(khi)004:772: nga bya ba bsod nams chung bas yod dam /
NK032(khi)004:773: yod shes kyang ngas mi rnyed byas pas /
NK032(khi)004:774: rnyed 'ong zhing de thon la bde bar longs spyod cig byas pas /
NK032(khi)004:775: gal te bden nam snyam bltas pas /
NK032(khi)004:776: sgyed po ma sgyed kyi 'og nas gser phye bum
NK032(khi)004:777: pa gang rnyed nas de la mos cha gsum du
NK032(khi)004:778: bgos nas / cha gcig bla ma dang dkon mchog la mchod pa'i phud bcad /
NK032(khi)004:779: cha gcig long sprang dang yul de'i rgyal po la khral dang sbyin par bcad /
NK032(khi)004:780: dus de tsam na rgyal po blas 'tsho ba bya
NK032(khi)004:781: ba so nam bya mi dgos par khral phud kyis
NK032(khi)004:783: mnga' bdag dpal 'khor btsan bzhugs pa'i dus su /
NK032(khi)004:784: rgyal bu gcig gis yar klung rog pa rtsa ru byon pas /
NK032(khi)004:785: rgan mo gcig gis nas phung gcig la bzang ngan gsum du phye nas 'dug pas /
NK032(khi)004:786: rgyal bu des nas gsum 'byed pa ci tshug yin byas pas /
NK032(khi)004:788: nas kyi snying po bla ma dkon mchog gnyan pas mchod pa'i phud du bcad pa yin /
NK032(khi)004:789: 'bring po de nged rang gis so nam byas pa yin pas 'tsho ba'i rgyags byed pa yin /
NK032(khi)004:790: ngan shos 'di rgyal po dang long sprang la khral dang sbyin par gtong ba yin zer bas /
NK032(khi)004:791: de nas rgyal bu de pho brang du byon nas /
NK032(khi)004:792: nged rang so nam byed dgos par 'dug /
NK032(khi)004:793: nged rgyal po dang long sprang mnyam por byas nas
NK032(khi)004:794: rgyal po'i dpya dang long sprang gi yon la ngan
NK032(khi)004:795: shos ster ba yin 'dug zer nas bod kyi rgyal
NK032(khi)004:796: po dus de nas so nam la tshud pa lags
NK032(khi)004:797: skad / rgya gar na da dung du yang yod pa yin skad do //
NK032(khi)004:798: de yang dbul mo'i gter des yar la bla ma dkon mchog mchod pa /
NK032(khi)004:799: mar rgyal po dang long sprang la sbyin par btang ba /
NK032(khi)004:800: bar mo rang gi bza' gyon la sogs pa phun sum tshogs pa la longs spyad do //
NK032(khi)004:801: gzhan la rag ma lus pa'i dpe de bzhin du /
NK032(khi)004:802: brgyud pa'i bla ma rnams kyis ye nas bde bar
NK032(khi)004:803: gshegs pa'i snying po rang gi rgyud la yod pa'i
NK032(khi)004:804: sems nyid kyi gter chen de bla ma'i brda dang
NK032(khi)004:805: ngag la brten nas gter gyi sgo bsdams pa bkral
NK032(khi)004:807: dbul mos yar la mchod rgyu byung ba bzhin du sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa lon /
NK032(khi)004:808: mar la sbyin rgyu byung ba dang 'dra bar sems can rnams thugs rjes skyob /
NK032(khi)004:809: rang nyid phun sum tshogs pa la longs spyod du byung ba bzhin du /
NK032(khi)004:810: don rang gis sems nyid rtogs pas /
NK032(khi)004:811: gzung 'dzin gyi rnam par rtog pa dang bral nas 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal las grol te /
NK032(khi)004:812: chos nyid la longs spyod du byung ngo //
NK032(khi)004:813: de tsa na thar pa gzhan la rag ma lus te sangs rgyas kho na rang nyid do //
NK032(khi)004:814: de ni gter chen dgrol ba'i go ba dbul mos gter rnyed pa'i dpes mtshon pa'o //
NK032(khi)004:815: gter chen dgrol ba'i tshig la gnyis te /
NK032(khi)004:816: rig 'dzin brdas grol ba'i brgyud pa dang /
NK032(khi)004:817: gang zag gdams ngag gis grol ba'i brgyud pa'o //
NK032(khi)004:818: dang po rig 'dzin brdas grol ba'i brgyud pa la go ba dang /
NK032(khi)004:820: rig 'dzin brdas grol pa'i go ba ni /
NK032(khi)004:821: rig 'dzin zhes pa 'bras bu gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa'i rigs brgyud 'dzin pa yin la /
NK032(khi)004:822: brdas grol ba ni tshigs mang po bshad ma dgos te /
NK032(khi)004:823: bla mas brda bstan pa tsam gyis grol ba'o //
NK032(khi)004:824: brgyud pa ni rdo rje sems dpa' nas bee ro
NK032(khi)004:825: tsa na yan chad du gcig nas gcig tu phreng
NK032(khi)004:827: de yang tshul lam thabs ji ltar du brgyud na /
NK032(khi)004:829: dang po chos 'di 'byung ba'i khungs ni rgya gar gyi yul yin pas /
NK032(khi)004:830: rgya gar gyi yul de na gling chen po dgu yod de /
NK032(khi)004:831: de yang shar phyogs na b+hang+ga la'i gling /
NK032(khi)004:832: lho phyogs na b+he ta la'i gling /
NK032(khi)004:833: nub phyogs na o rgyan gyi gling /
NK032(khi)004:834: byang phyogs na kha che'i gling /
NK032(khi)004:835: shar lho mtshams na khang khams yang snang /
NK032(khi)004:838: lho nub mtshams na zangs gling /
NK032(khi)004:839: nub byang mtshams na za hor gling /
NK032(khi)004:840: byang shar mtshams na ka ma ru pa'i gling /
NK032(khi)004:841: dbus na rdo rje gdan dang dgu yod pa las /
NK032(khi)004:842: gling de rnams las chos 'di 'byung ba'i gnas ni nub phyogs o rgyan gyi yul yin no //
NK032(khi)004:843: spyir rgya gar gyi yul na chos skyong ba'i rgyal po'i rigs d+harma r+aa dza bya ba dang /
NK032(khi)004:844: srid skyong ba'i rgyal po'i rigs u pa r+aa dza bya ba ste gnyis su yod pa las /
NK032(khi)004:845: chos skyong ba'i rgyal po'i rigs de gcig skyes gnyis skyes d+har+m+aa r+aa dza bya bar 'ong ste /
NK032(khi)004:846: las dge ba'i las min pa sdig pa'i las yid la'ang mi 'gyu /
NK032(khi)004:848: byed 'dod kyang bya ba'i dbang med /
NK032(khi)004:849: byas na chos skyong ba'i rgyal srid mi zin no //
NK032(khi)004:850: srid skyong ba'i rgyal po'i rigs de gcig skyes gnyis
NK032(khi)004:851: skyes thams cad u pa r+aa dza bya bar 'ong
NK032(khi)004:852: skad / de la dmag dang sdig pa'i las min pa dge ba'i las yid la'ang mi 'gyu /
NK032(khi)004:855: byas na srid skyong ba'i rgyal srid mi zin skad /
NK032(khi)004:856: de yang rgya gar gyi skad du d+harma ni /
NK032(khi)004:858: rgya gar skad du r+aa dza ni /
NK032(khi)004:859: bod skad du rgyal po bya ba yin pas /
NK032(khi)004:860: de yang chos skyong ba'i rgyal po sh+aakya'i rigs mtshan
NK032(khi)004:861: dri med gtsug phud sh+aaka bzang bya ba'i btsun mo
NK032(khi)004:863: sras mo mtshar sdug 'od du 'bar ba /
NK032(khi)004:864: 'gro bas blta ba'i 'os su gyur pa /
NK032(khi)004:865: bltas pas chog mi shes pa gcig sku 'khrungs te /
NK032(khi)004:866: de'i mtshan rgya gar skad du sa ra ni /
NK032(khi)004:867: bod skad du mdzes ma dang ldan pa bya ba yin te /
NK032(khi)004:868: yab kyi zhal nas nga'i sras mo 'di 'gro ba
NK032(khi)004:869: gzhan la bstan par yang phangs zer nas pho brang
NK032(khi)004:870: dgu thog gi rtse la 'tsho ba'i ma ma dang
NK032(khi)004:871: bcas pa bzhugs su bcug go //
NK032(khi)004:872: de'i tshe de'i dus chos skyong ba'i rgyal po de la rgyal bu med pas gdung brgyud chad de /
NK032(khi)004:873: de'i dus su chos kyi sku'i chos kyi sku dpal bde ba chen po /
NK032(khi)004:874: chos kyi sku'i longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku dpal kun tu bzang po /
NK032(khi)004:875: chos kyi sku'i sprul pa'i sku dpal rdo rje sems dpa' /
NK032(khi)004:878: sku sprul pa'i sku yin te /
NK032(khi)004:879: rdo rje sems dpa' sku gsung thugs gsum rnam par
NK032(khi)004:880: dag pa'i ngang nas thugs rjes 'gro ba'i don du
NK032(khi)004:881: gsang sngags ston par sprul par bkye ba sems dag
NK032(khi)004:882: pa lha'i bu zhes bya ba de /
NK032(khi)004:883: 'og min lha'i gnas na bzhugs pa'i tshe lha'i dbang po brgya byin gyis mkhyen nas /
NK032(khi)004:884: lha'i bu khyod ni rdo rje sems dpas 'gro ba
NK032(khi)004:885: mi'i yul du chos ston par sprul pa yin zhes
NK032(khi)004:886: bskul bas / der sems dag lha'i bus rdo rje
NK032(khi)004:887: sems dpa'i sprul pa yin par rang ngo rang gis
NK032(khi)004:888: shes nas lho 'dzam bu'i gling du chos skyong ba'i
NK032(khi)004:889: rgyal po dri med gtsug phud sh+aaka bzang gi gdung
NK032(khi)004:891: sras mo mdzes ma dang ldan pa'i lhums su zhugs pa yin te /
NK032(khi)004:892: de yang zam pa chen po dbang gi man ngag las /
NK032(khi)004:893: yang sprul dga' rab rdo rje de //
NK032(khi)004:894: 'dzam bu'i gling du rgyal thebs byon //
NK032(khi)004:896: de yang ji ltar du byon na /
NK032(khi)004:898: zla ba dpyid zla ra ba /
NK032(khi)004:900: zla ba'i nya'i gdugs nyi ma rtse shar la sras
NK032(khi)004:901: mo mdzes ma dang ldan pa'i drung du bya g.yu
NK032(khi)004:902: bya khu byug gcig tu sprul nas /
NK032(khi)004:903: ku khug ku khug pa lan gsum du skad bton nas song ste /
NK032(khi)004:904: nga do nub 'ong ngo bya ba'i brdar 'dug ste /
NK032(khi)004:905: de yang do nub srod la khye'u chung mtshar sdug
NK032(khi)004:906: 'od du 'bar ba mtshan dang dpe byad kyis brgyan
NK032(khi)004:907: pa / 'gro bas blta ba'i 'os su gyur pa /
NK032(khi)004:908: bltas pas chog mi shes pa gcig byung nas sbyor
NK032(khi)004:909: ba mdzad nas nangs par tho rangs nam mkha' la
NK032(khi)004:911: de nas sang phod de'i dus tshod sras mo de
NK032(khi)004:912: la sras po mtshan dang dpe byad kyis brgyan pa
NK032(khi)004:914: yab la ngo tsha nas lo bdun gyi bar du gsang ngo //
NK032(khi)004:915: sras mo des yab rgyal po de la /
NK032(khi)004:916: nga la sras po 'di lta bu gcig mnga' byas nas bstan pas /
NK032(khi)004:917: der yab rgyal pos mtshan bltas nas de'i 'phro la ling gis brgyal nas 'dug go //
NK032(khi)004:918: sras mo des yab rgyal po brgyal sangs tsa na yab rgyal po ma mnyes sam byas pas /
NK032(khi)004:919: yab rgyal po de'i zhal nas nga mi dga' ba ci mchis /
NK032(khi)004:920: 'di rigs byed lha'i sprul pa gcig 'dug la /
NK032(khi)004:921: rigs ni theg pa chen po'i rigs byed pa /
NK032(khi)004:922: mdzes shing yab mi mnga' bas na lha'i sprul pa /
NK032(khi)004:923: 'di'i rigs la theg pa chen po'i chos skad cig
NK032(khi)004:924: ma'i don rtogs nas tshe gcig la 'tshang rgya ba'i
NK032(khi)004:925: chos gcig dar 'ong bar 'dug pa la /
NK032(khi)004:926: nga rgas pa gsungs nas spyan chab shar gyis byung skad /
NK032(khi)004:927: spyan chab byung yang yab bu de la dga' ba
NK032(khi)004:928: yin pas sras mo mi gnong par rab tu song
NK032(khi)004:929: ste bu 'di rdo rje sems dpa'i yang sprul yin
NK032(khi)004:930: pas / de bas na dga' rab rdo rje zhes bya bar mtshan btags so //
NK032(khi)004:931: de nas dga' rab rdo rjes lo brgyad lon tsa na yum 'di ru bde bar bzhugs shig /
NK032(khi)004:932: nga 'di nas nub phyogs o rgyan gyi yul d+ha na ko sha'i gling /
NK032(khi)004:935: me tog u dum wa ra 'byung ba'i gling /
NK032(khi)004:936: dur khrod chen po gser gling he chen brdal bya
NK032(khi)004:937: ba na sgrub pa'i gnas gser gyi brag phug yu
NK032(khi)004:938: ba can bya ba yod pas der sgrub pa la
NK032(khi)004:939: 'agro'o // da res dam pa'i chos gcig ma 'grub
NK032(khi)004:940: na 'jig rten 'di'i rgyal srid btsan yang nub gcig
NK032(khi)004:941: gi rmi lam tsam yang med do gsungs nas /
NK032(khi)004:942: yum la phyag 'tshal zhu ba byas nas gser gyi
NK032(khi)004:943: brag phug yu ba can du sgrub pa la gshegs
NK032(khi)004:944: so // de nas yang glang gi lo /
NK032(khi)004:945: zla ba dpyid zla ra ba /
NK032(khi)004:947: zla ba'i nya'i gdugs par nyi ma'i zer la /
NK032(khi)004:948: bcom ldan 'das rdo rje sems dpa'i sku gsung thugs
NK032(khi)004:949: gsum rnam par dag pa'i sprul pa sems dag lha'i
NK032(khi)004:950: bu zhes bya ba snang ba'i gzugs su grub la
NK032(khi)004:951: / reg pa'i gzugs su ma grub pa 'od kyi lus can mtshan dang dpe byad kyis brgyan pa /
NK032(khi)004:952: phyag g.yas na gser gyi rdo rje bsnams pa /
NK032(khi)004:953: g.yon na shel gyi dril bu dku la brten pa /
NK032(khi)004:954: de lta bu gcig gis phyag g.yas pa'i rdo rje dga' rab rdo rje'i spyi bor bzhag nas /
NK032(khi)004:956: a ha ho'i zhes byin gyis brlabs pas /
NK032(khi)004:961: dbyer mi phyed pa'i dus na dbyer phyed bya ba'am mi phyed bya ba'i blo'i mtha' 'am /
NK032(khi)004:962: tshig gi mtha' zab cing phra ba tsam yang mi
NK032(khi)004:963: gnas pa'i chos nyid kyi rang sgra'i ngang du zhag
NK032(khi)004:964: bdun gyi bar du ting nge 'dzin thun gcig tu
NK032(khi)004:966: de las sad tsa na rjes kyi shes pa la
NK032(khi)004:967: sems nyid dngos po gshis kyi gnas lugs de mun
NK032(khi)004:968: khung du sgron me btegs pa zhin du byas pa
NK032(khi)004:969: dang bcos pa med par rang gsal du lhag gis
NK032(khi)004:970: rgyud la shar zhing rtogs pa'o //
NK032(khi)004:971: don de mi brjed mi yal bar brtan par bya
NK032(khi)004:972: ba'i brjed rdo ru sems dag lha'i bus a wa
NK032(khi)004:973: na d+ha ra zhes brda bstan pas /
NK032(khi)004:974: bod skad du khyod rang nam mkha' dag pa la
NK032(khi)004:975: 'ja' gsal ba 'di la ltos dang bya ba'i brdar
NK032(khi)004:976: byung nas / nam mkha'i dag pa'i dkyil na 'ja'
NK032(khi)004:977: gsal ba gcig shar nas 'dug pa de la dga'
NK032(khi)004:979: nam mkha' dag pa de dmigs su med pa chos kyi dbyings kyi brda' /
NK032(khi)004:980: 'ja' de dmigs med kyi don de ma 'gags par
NK032(khi)004:981: byon pa de rig cing gsal ba ye shes kyi
NK032(khi)004:982: brda / de gnyis tha dad du ma song ste /
NK032(khi)004:983: dbyer mi phyed pa de dbyings na ye shes gnyis su med pa /
NK032(khi)004:984: sems dag lha'i bu snang ba'i gzugs su ma 'gags
NK032(khi)004:985: par byon pa de mtshon par byed pa thabs kyi
NK032(khi)004:986: brda / reg pa'i gzugs su ma grub pa de dmigs su med pa shes rab kyi brda /
NK032(khi)004:987: de gnyis tha dad du ma song ste ngo bo
NK032(khi)004:988: gcig tu 'dug pa de thabs shes gnyis su med
NK032(khi)004:989: pa / dbyings ye shes gnyis su med pa /
NK032(khi)004:990: don sems nyid dngos po'i gnas lugs chos bzhi dang
NK032(khi)004:991: ldan pa nam mkha' dag pa la 'ja' gsal ba
NK032(khi)004:992: lta bu gcig tu rtogs so //
NK032(khi)004:993: der zhing las skyes pa'i mkha' 'gro ma'i gtso mo 'bar ma'i gdong can dang /
NK032(khi)004:994: las las skyes pa'i mkha' 'gro ma'i gtso mo mkha' la gshegs ma dang /
NK032(khi)004:995: sngags las skyes pa'i mkha' 'gro ma'i gtso mo mkha'
NK032(khi)004:996: la spyod ma dang gsum yang mdun du shar gyis
NK032(khi)004:997: byung nas / bdag cag gis dga' rab rdo rje
NK032(khi)004:998: la chos zab mo 'di lta bu'i bka' skyong ba'i
NK032(khi)004:999: chos skyong nged kyis byed pa yin no //
NK032(khi)004:1000: 'di bsgrub cing dam tshig bsrung ba la dngos grub ster /
NK032(khi)004:1001: nyams su mi len cing dam tshig mi bsrung ba
NK032(khi)004:1002: la bka' chad gcod pa yin no gsungs nas dga'
NK032(khi)004:1003: rab rdo rje la byin gyis kyang brlabs /
NK032(khi)004:1004: srog snying yang phul te gzhan gyis ma bcos nyid
NK032(khi)004:1005: kyis zhal bzhes ma bya ba yin te rang dam
NK032(khi)004:1006: rang gis bcas pa'i bka' skyong gi mkha' 'gro ma
NK032(khi)004:1007: sde gsum bya ba yin te /
NK032(khi)004:1008: shin tu byin rlabs dang nus mthu che ba'i chos
NK032(khi)004:1009: shin tu gnyan pa yin pas dam tshig shin tu
NK032(khi)004:1010: gtsang ba gal che ba yin gsungs /
NK032(khi)004:1011: sems dag pa lha'i bus slob dpon dga' rab rdo rje la bstan pa tsam gyis rtogs /
NK032(khi)004:1012: rtogs pa tsam gyis don mngon du gyur te sgrib
NK032(khi)004:1013: pa la sbyangs dka' ba nyon mongs pa dang shes
NK032(khi)004:1014: bya'i sgrib pa de nyid du dag /
NK032(khi)004:1015: thob pa la dka' ba thun mong gi dngos grub
NK032(khi)004:1016: dang mchog gi dngos grub de nyid du thob ste
NK032(khi)004:1017: / dper na 'bras 'khor ma lo legs na phub sog zhor la byung ba'am /
NK032(khi)004:1018: yang na nor bu rin po che sngon la rnyed
NK032(khi)004:1019: pa de la mchod pa byas pas dgos 'dod 'phral
NK032(khi)004:1021: de nas slob dpon dga' rab rdo rjes 'gro ba'i don du byin gyis brlabs pas /
NK032(khi)004:1022: slob dpon 'jam dpal bshes gnyen gyi thugs la dad pa rang bzhin gyis shar te /
NK032(khi)004:1023: dper nyi ma la nye ring med kyang snod bcud gtsang ma'i nang du 'char ba bzhin du /
NK032(khi)004:1024: nam tho rangs gcig tsa na ga re bskal pa nas bskal par tshogs bsags /
NK032(khi)004:1025: bskal pa nas bskal par sgrib pa sbyangs kyang bskal
NK032(khi)004:1026: pa grangs med pa gcig gam gnyis na 'khor ba'i
NK032(khi)004:1027: sdug bsngal las grol lam zer ba las /
NK032(khi)004:1028: de'i gong du grol ba'i thabs mi 'dug pas /
NK032(khi)004:1029: skad cig ma'i don rtogs nas tshe gcig gis sangs
NK032(khi)004:1030: rgya ba'i chos gcig yod du gsha' bar 'dug pa
NK032(khi)004:1031: la / de yang gzhan na dri ba'i kha na med de /
NK032(khi)004:1032: grong khyer ser skya'i sgo kha dpal sh+r+ai na len+d+ra'i
NK032(khi)004:1033: gtsug lag khang na rgyu mtshan nyid kyi pan+di ta
NK032(khi)004:1034: lnga brgya / 'bras bu gsang sngags kyi pan+di ta
NK032(khi)004:1035: lnga brgya bzhugs pas de lta bu'i chos zhig yod
NK032(khi)004:1036: na der khungs chod 'ong sems nas /
NK032(khi)004:1037: rgyu mtshan nyid kyi pan+di ta la spyan g.yas pas gzigs /
NK032(khi)004:1038: 'bras bu gsang sngags kyi pan+di ta la spyan g.yon pas gzigs nas /
NK032(khi)004:1040: bskal pa nas bskal par tshogs bsags /
NK032(khi)004:1041: bskal pa nas bskal par sgrib pa sbyangs kyang /
NK032(khi)004:1042: bskal pa grangs med pa gcig gam gnyis na 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal las grol lam zer ba las /
NK032(khi)004:1043: de'i gong du grol ba'i thabs mi 'dug pas /
NK032(khi)004:1044: skad cig mas don rtogs nas tshe da res gcig
NK032(khi)004:1045: pos 'tshang rgya ba'i chos zhig 'ong du gsha' bar
NK032(khi)004:1046: 'dug pa la / de lta bu zhig med na
NK032(khi)004:1047: de ring sang dus btab pa'i mi yang stabs ka
NK032(khi)004:1049: lan gcig ci ltar 'gro cha med byas nas dris pas /
NK032(khi)004:1050: rgyu mtshan nyid kyi pan+di ta rnams ci yang mi gsungs /
NK032(khi)004:1051: 'bras bu gsang sngags kyi pan+di ta rnams spyan zur gyis brdas bskul nas /
NK032(khi)004:1053: de lta bu shes pa 'o skol 'di na med de /
NK032(khi)004:1054: 'di nas nub phyogs su phyin pa na dpal o rgyan gyi yul d+ha na ko sha'i gling /
NK032(khi)004:1056: me tog u dum wa ra 'byung ba'i gling /
NK032(khi)004:1058: dur khrod chen po gser gling he chen brdal bya ba na /
NK032(khi)004:1059: sgrub pa'i gnas gser gyi brag phug yu ba can bya ba yod pas /
NK032(khi)004:1060: de na rigs byed lha'i sprul pa slob dpon chen
NK032(khi)004:1061: po dga' rab rdo rje zhes bya ba bzhugs te
NK032(khi)004:1062: / de la bcom ldan 'das rdo rje sems dpa'i
NK032(khi)004:1063: sprul pa sems dag lha'i bu zhes bya bas byin
NK032(khi)004:1064: / gyis brlabs nas / skad cig ma'i don rtogs
NK032(khi)004:1065: nas tshe gcig gis 'tshang rgya ba'i chos khong la
NK032(khi)004:1068: gzhan gang na yang 'gro ba'i sa med de /
NK032(khi)004:1069: de lta bu'i chos shes zer ba med pas der cis kyang song gsungs skad /
NK032(khi)004:1070: de yang nub phyogs zhes bya ba ni rgya gar rdo rje gdan gyi nub phyogs yin te /
NK032(khi)004:1071: yang na nyon mongs pa mi skye bar nub 'gro bas na nub phyogs so //
NK032(khi)004:1072: dpal o rgyan gyi yul ni rtogs pa bdag gi dpal dang thugs rje gzhan gyi dpal /
NK032(khi)004:1073: de yang pho skyes dpa' bor 'byung la /
NK032(khi)004:1074: mo skyes dpa' mor 'byung ba me tog u dum wa ras brgyan pa'i yul yin no //
NK032(khi)004:1075: d+ha na ko sha'i gling ni d+ha na sems ngal gso ba /
NK032(khi)004:1076: ko sha ni yid skyob par byed pa /
NK032(khi)004:1077: phyi'i rgya mtsho ni ba tsh+wa can btung du mi btub pa /
NK032(khi)004:1078: 'gram ni rgya mtsho de'i chu 'gram la yar la /
NK032(khi)004:1079: ro mchog bde ba'i tshal ni bza' shing gi nags dang tshal yod de /
NK032(khi)004:1080: de gang zos pa'i ro mchog gis rgyud la bde ba skyed nus pa'o //
NK032(khi)004:1081: de'i phyi rim na yar la me tog u dum
NK032(khi)004:1082: wa ra mthing kha sha stag 'byung ba'i gling chags
NK032(khi)004:1083: pa'o // dur khrod ni chos can gyi rnam par
NK032(khi)004:1084: rtog pa thams cad chos nyid kyi ngang du thim
NK032(khi)004:1085: pa'o // pa'i dur / khrod ni rig pa'i ye shes skye 'gags med par gnas pa'i khrod /
NK032(khi)004:1086: gser gling ni gser gyi gling na sa rdo gzhan mi 'byung ba bzhin du /
NK032(khi)004:1087: dur khrod chen po gser gling der tha mal gyi rtog pa rang rgyud la mi skye ba'o //
NK032(khi)004:1088: he chen brdal ni chos nyid gnyis su med pa'i
NK032(khi)004:1089: don la dgyes pa chen po phyogs ris med par
NK032(khi)004:1090: brdal ba'o // sgrub pa'i gnas ni mchog dang thun
NK032(khi)004:1091: mong gis dngos grub ma lus pa thob par byed
NK032(khi)004:1092: brdal ba'o // pa'i gnas so // gser gyi brag ni chos nyid 'gyur ba med pa'o //
NK032(khi)004:1093: phug ni zab mo'i don no //
NK032(khi)004:1094: yu ba can gyi chos nyid zab mo'i don 'gyur
NK032(khi)004:1095: ba med pa rdo rje zam pa 'di la grub
NK032(khi)004:1096: thob brgyud pa'i yu ba gcig nas gcig tu rgyun
NK032(khi)004:1097: mi chad pa la zer ro //
NK032(khi)004:1098: 'o na de lta bu'i gnas mtshan nyid dang ldan
NK032(khi)004:1099: pa de ru 'gro ba la dka' sla dang nye
NK032(khi)004:1102: dka' sla ni shin tu dka' ste mi med pa'i lung stong la gcan gzan ma rungs pa dang /
NK032(khi)004:1105: lha ma yin la sogs pa yod /
NK032(khi)004:1106: gcan gzan gdug pa can dang 'phrad na khrum gyis zos nas 'gro /
NK032(khi)004:1107: sbrul gdug pa can dang 'phrad na dug sbrul gyi
NK032(khi)004:1108: lce yug byas pas snag ma tsho kha ru sibs
NK032(khi)004:1109: la rus pa tshong thang la dkar spung gos 'gro
NK032(khi)004:1110: / mi ma yin dang 'phrad na khyur gyis mid nas 'gro /
NK032(khi)004:1111: lha ma yin dang 'phrad na skad lhangs kyis brjod
NK032(khi)004:1112: pa tsam gyis mig khrag rul gyis 'chi ba yod
NK032(khi)004:1113: / nye ring ni mi grong med pa'i lung stong
NK032(khi)004:1114: de lta bu la zla ba ril po bcu gsum
NK032(khi)004:1115: / du 'gro dgos / dka' sla dang nye ring
NK032(khi)004:1116: de lta bu med na dang nged kyang 'gro ste
NK032(khi)004:1117: / du 'gro dgos / gsung skad do // der
NK032(khi)004:1118: slob dpon 'jam dpal bshes gnyen gyi thugs la nga'i
NK032(khi)004:1119: lus 'di snga ma 'khor ba nyon mongs pa sha
NK032(khi)004:1120: / du 'gro dgos / gsung skad do // stag
NK032(khi)004:1121: la shi / da res chos phyogs su shi ba
NK032(khi)004:1122: / du 'gro dgos / gsung skad do // stag
NK032(khi)004:1123: la shi / gcig byed dgos / lus rkyen de
NK032(khi)004:1124: lta bu gcig gis shi yang /
NK032(khi)004:1125: sems 'di slob dpon dga' rab rdo rje'i gan du ci brtol byed dgos /
NK032(khi)004:1126: slob dpon gyi thugs kyis mkhyen nas /
NK032(khi)004:1127: slob dpon gyis nga'i sems la byin gyis rlob ste 'ong bas /
NK032(khi)004:1128: sems 'khor bar gtan du ma 'khyams na /
NK032(khi)004:1129: lus da res gcig pu la shi ma shi med kyi snyam nas the tshom med par gshegs pas /
NK032(khi)004:1130: zla ba ril po bcu gsum na ri brag gcig tu brtol te /
NK032(khi)004:1131: btsun pa hral po gcig gis phyag na mda' lnga
NK032(khi)004:1132: dang gzhu gcig bsnams pa sham thabs thod du bcing
NK032(khi)004:1134: ga re gzhan 'di ru su yang 'ong ba'i don med de /
NK032(khi)004:1135: slob dpon dga' rab rdo rje yin pa las 'os med kyi sems nas /
NK032(khi)004:1136: slob dpon la gser gyi man+dala 'bul ba'i chag chag 'debs pa'i chu ma rnyed pa la /
NK032(khi)004:1137: slob dpon gyi zhal nas khyod rang la lus 'dug pa gsungs nas /
NK032(khi)004:1138: ga re nga la lus yod /
NK032(khi)004:1140: rtsa la khrag yod sems nas gtar kha byar btub
NK032(khi)004:1141: pa'i rtsa rnams spu gri ka ma las gshags nas
NK032(khi)004:1142: / man+dala bshams nas khrag gis chag chag btab /
NK032(khi)004:1143: gser gyi tshom bu bkod nas lha phyag dgu phrugs su btsal /
NK032(khi)004:1144: bskor ba lan gsum du byas nas /
NK032(khi)004:1146: khyed kyi rtogs pa bdag la bskyed par zhu 'tshal zhes gsol ba btab pas /
NK032(khi)004:1147: ci yang mi gsung bar dur khrod chen po der gshegs nas song ngo //
NK032(khi)004:1148: de'i phyir 'brang nas bskor ba nyin lan gsum mtshan lan gsum du byas /
NK032(khi)004:1149: lha phyag nyin lan gsum mtshan lan gsum du btsal /
NK032(khi)004:1150: zla ba ngo re la zhu ba'i don re phul kyang ci yang mi gsung nas /
NK032(khi)004:1151: 'o skol la gdams ngag mi gnang bar 'dug pas /
NK032(khi)004:1152: yul du phyin na ni lus la bar chad 'ong
NK032(khi)004:1153: ste sems kyang gtan du 'khor bar 'khyams 'gro nyen
NK032(khi)004:1154: yod pas / nga rang 'dir lcebs nas shi la bsdad dgos /
NK032(khi)004:1155: nga'i lus 'di shi yang sems la slob dpon gyi
NK032(khi)004:1156: byin gyis brlabs nas 'khor bar gtan du mi 'khyam
NK032(khi)004:1157: ste 'ong sems nas ka pa li nas spu gri
NK032(khi)004:1158: ka ma li bton nas ske la brdeg dgos bsam
NK032(khi)004:1159: nas dengs kyis byas tsa na /
NK032(khi)004:1160: slob dpon dga' rab rdo rjes gzigs nas khong gi zhal nas 'jam dpal bshes gnyen gsungs nas /
NK032(khi)004:1162: khyod ci 'dod pa yin gsungs pa la /
NK032(khi)004:1163: nga chos nyid kyi don skad cig gis rtogs nas
NK032(khi)004:1164: tshe gcig gis 'tshang rgya ba gcig 'dod pa yin
NK032(khi)004:1165: te byas pas / khyod kyis da dung ma go'am gsungs pas /
NK032(khi)004:1166: bdag gis ni ma rig ma rtogs so byas pas /
NK032(khi)004:1167: phyag g.yas pa spyi bor gzhag nas /
NK032(khi)004:1168: a ha ho 'is byin gyis brlabs pas /
NK032(khi)004:1172: 'i gnyis su med pa'i don dbyer mi phyed pa /
NK032(khi)004:1173: dbyer mi phyed pas dus na dbyer phyed bya ba'am /
NK032(khi)004:1174: mi phyed bya ba'i blo'i mtha' 'am tshig gi mtha'
NK032(khi)004:1175: zab cing phra ba tsam yang mi gnas pa'i chos
NK032(khi)004:1176: nyid kyi rang sgra'i ngang du zhag bdun gyi bar
NK032(khi)004:1177: ting nge 'dzin thun gcig gis ngang du phril gyis
NK032(khi)004:1178: song ngo // de las sad tsa na rjes kyi
NK032(khi)004:1179: shes pa la sems nyid dngos po gshis kyi gnas
NK032(khi)004:1180: lugs rang byung gi ye shes chen po de mun
NK032(khi)004:1181: khung du sgron me btegs pa bzhin du byas pa
NK032(khi)004:1182: dang bcos pa med par rang gsal du rgyud la
NK032(khi)004:1184: don de mi brjed mi yal bar bya ba'i brjed
NK032(khi)004:1185: rdo ru dga' rab rdo rjes s+aur+y+aa d+ha ra zhes
NK032(khi)004:1186: brda bstan pas / khyod rang nyi ma'i snying po
NK032(khi)004:1187: ya gi la ltos shig bya ba'i brdar go nas
NK032(khi)004:1188: bltas pas nyi ma'i snying po de dus gsum du
NK032(khi)004:1193: chos bzhi dang ldan pa gcig tu rtogs so //
NK032(khi)004:1194: dpe de bzhin du rang gi sems nyid kyang chos bzhi dang ldan pa /
NK032(khi)004:1195: gsal la rtogs pa med pa nyi ma'i snying po lta bu gcig tu rtogs so //
NK032(khi)004:1196: de yang bstan pa tsam gyis rtogs /
NK032(khi)004:1197: rtogs pa tsam gyis don mngon du gyur te /
NK032(khi)004:1198: sgrib pa la sbyangs dka' ba nyon mongs pa dang shes bya'i sgrib pa de nyid dag /
NK032(khi)004:1199: thob pa la dka' ba mchog gi dngos grub de nyid du thob /
NK032(khi)004:1200: thun mong gi dngos grub zhor la byung ste /
NK032(khi)004:1201: dper na 'bras 'khor ma lo legs na phub sog zhor la 'byung ba bzhin du gyur te /
NK032(khi)004:1202: slob dpon dga' rab rdo rje'i phyag na mda' lnga
NK032(khi)004:1203: bsnams pa de yang ye shes lnga'i brda ru go
NK032(khi)004:1204: // gzhu dang sprad du 'dug pa de yang thabs
NK032(khi)004:1205: dang shes rab ya ma bral bar zung du 'jug
NK032(khi)004:1206: // par go // sham thabs thod du bcings pa
NK032(khi)004:1207: de yang theg pa 'og ma ma spangs gong ma
NK032(khi)004:1208: dbyings su dag par go zhing rtogs nas /
NK032(khi)004:1209: bka' skyong gi mkha' 'gro ma gsum gyis kyang khas blangs dam bcas byin gyis brlabs nas /
NK032(khi)004:1210: de nas slob dpon 'jam dpal bshes gnyen de'ang bya
NK032(khi)004:1211: 'phur pa'am rdzi bskyod pa bzhin du dur khrod gser
NK032(khi)004:1212: gling nas dpal yon tan 'byung ba'i grong khyer du
NK032(khi)004:1213: zla ba ril po bcu gsum gyi lam yod pa
NK032(khi)004:1214: la gro khar phril gyis brtol lo //
NK032(khi)004:1215: de nas slob dpon 'jam dpal bshes gnyen gyis rang bzhin gyis byin gyis brlabs pas /
NK032(khi)004:1216: slob dpon sh+r+ai sing ha'i thugs la shar ba ni
NK032(khi)004:1217: dper na nyi zla la nye ring med kyang snod
NK032(khi)004:1218: dag pa dang chu gtsang ma'i nang du 'char ba
NK032(khi)004:1219: bzhin du / 'gro ba la nye ring med kyang
NK032(khi)004:1220: slob dpon sh+r+ai seng ha'i thugs la yang dag pa'i
NK032(khi)004:1221: don gcig rang bzhin gyis shar te /
NK032(khi)004:1222: de yang nam tho rangs gcig tsa na /
NK032(khi)004:1223: ga re bskal pa nas bskal par tshogs bsags /
NK032(khi)004:1224: bskal pa nas bskal par sgrib pa sbyangs kyang bskal
NK032(khi)004:1225: pa grangs med pa gcig gam gnyis na 'khor ba
NK032(khi)004:1226: nas thar ram zer ba las /
NK032(khi)004:1227: de'i gong du thar pa'i thabs mi 'dug pas /
NK032(khi)004:1228: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas ni thams cad mkhyen pa yin /
NK032(khi)004:1229: de'i chos byed pa po ni rdo rje gdan gyi
NK032(khi)004:1230: byang phyogs grong khyer ser skya'i sgo kha dpal sh+r+ai
NK032(khi)004:1231: na len+d+ra'i gtsug lag khang na rgyu mtshan nyid kyi
NK032(khi)004:1233: 'bras bu gsang sngags kyi pan+di ta lnga brgya rgyal po'i mchod gnas su yod pas /
NK032(khi)004:1234: skad cig mas don rtogs nas tshe gcig gis sangs
NK032(khi)004:1235: rgya ba'i chos yod dam med de rnams la 'dri
NK032(khi)004:1236: dgos / yod na der zhu dgos /
NK032(khi)004:1237: med na yang der kho thag chod sems nas /
NK032(khi)004:1238: sh+r+ai sing ha sa dpal na len+d+ra'i gtsug lag khang du byon te /
NK032(khi)004:1239: rgyu mtshan nyid kyi pan+di ta la spyan g.yas pas gzigs /
NK032(khi)004:1240: 'bras bu gsang sngags kyi pan+di ta la spyan g.yon pas gzigs nas /
NK032(khi)004:1242: bskal pa nas bskal par tshogs bsags /
NK032(khi)004:1243: bskal pa nas bskal par sgrib pa sbyangs kyang bskal
NK032(khi)004:1244: pa grangs med pa gcig gam gnyis na 'khor ba'i
NK032(khi)004:1245: sdug bsngal las grol lam zer ba las /
NK032(khi)004:1246: de'i gong du grol ba'i thabs mi 'dug pa /
NK032(khi)004:1247: skad cig mas don rtogs nas tshe gcig gis sangs rgya ba'i chos 'dra ba med dam /
NK032(khi)004:1248: de lta bu gcig med na ni de ring sang
NK032(khi)004:1249: la dus btab pa'i gnyen nam grogs sgos mdza' la
NK032(khi)004:1250: sogs pa yang stabs ka snga phyi en pa re
NK032(khi)004:1252: gtan du mi 'phrad par 'gro ba yong gi 'dug pa la /
NK032(khi)004:1253: bskal pa grangs med pa gcig gam gnyis na glo
NK032(khi)004:1254: bur nyon mongs pa'i rkyen gyis ci tsug 'gro rang
NK032(khi)004:1256: rgyu mtshan nyid kyi pan+di ta rnams la rgyus med pas ci yang mi gsung /
NK032(khi)004:1257: 'bras bu gsang sngags kyi pan+di ta rnams gcig nas gcig la spyan zur gyis brdas bskul te /
NK032(khi)004:1258: 'og ma dag des bzhengs nas lan btab pa /
NK032(khi)004:1259: 'o skol 'di na de lta bu mi bdog ste /
NK032(khi)004:1260: 'di nas nub phyogs su phyin pa na dur khrod chen po he chen brdal ba bya ba na /
NK032(khi)004:1261: sgrub pa'i brag phug gser gyi yu ba can bya
NK032(khi)004:1262: ba yod pas de na rigs byed lha'i sprul pa
NK032(khi)004:1263: slob dpon chen po dga' rab rdo rje bya ba
NK032(khi)004:1264: la / bcom ldan 'das rdo rje sems dpa'i sprul
NK032(khi)004:1265: pa sems dag lha'i bu bya ba snang ba'i gzugs
NK032(khi)004:1266: la / su grub la / reg pa'i gzugs su
NK032(khi)004:1267: ma grub pa nam mkha'i 'ja' lta bu gcig gis
NK032(khi)004:1269: skad cig mas don rtogs nas tshe gcig gis 'tshang
NK032(khi)004:1270: rgya ba'i dgongs pa de khong la yod pa yin
NK032(khi)004:1271: pas / de gong du'am 'jam dpal bshes gnyen bya ba gcig 'di ru 'drir byung ba la /
NK032(khi)004:1272: pan+di ta gong ma rnams kyis dga' rab rdo rje'i gan du lung bstan pa yin /
NK032(khi)004:1273: dga' rab rdo rje mkha' 'gro ma rnams kyis nub
NK032(khi)004:1274: phyogs o rgyan gyi yul gyi sprin nag po 'dus
NK032(khi)004:1275: pa'i khrod du gdan drangs nas da lta 'jig rten
NK032(khi)004:1277: khong gis byin gyis brlabs pa'i slob dpon 'jam dpal
NK032(khi)004:1278: bshes gnyen bya ba des skad cig mas don rtogs
NK032(khi)004:1279: nas tshe gcig gis 'tshang rgya ba'i gdams ngag de
NK032(khi)004:1280: lon nas / lho phyogs gyad kyi yul b+he ta la'i gling /
NK032(khi)004:1281: shing dra ba gtsug dgu bkod pa'i tshal /
NK032(khi)004:1283: dpal yon tan thams cad 'byung ba'i grong khyer zhes bya 'phur ba'am rdzi bskyod pa'am /
NK032(khi)004:1284: gom pa gcig gis 'gongs pa'am bya rmyang gcig gis brtol ba bzhin du /
NK032(khi)004:1285: zla ba ril po bcu gsum gyi lam yod pa la /
NK032(khi)004:1286: dur khrod gser gling gi tsha ba thon nas byon
NK032(khi)004:1287: pas dpal yon tan 'byung ba'i grong khyer du gro
NK032(khi)004:1288: khar phril gyis brtol byung ste /
NK032(khi)004:1289: de yang slob dpon 'jam dpal bshes gnyen bya ba de na bzhugs nas yod pas /
NK032(khi)004:1290: skad cig mas don rtogs nas tshe gcig gis sangs rgya ba'i chos de khong la zhus na yod /
NK032(khi)004:1291: de yang lho phyogs ni rgya gar rdo rje gdan gyi lho phyogs /
NK032(khi)004:1292: gyad kyi yul ni gyad stobs po che 'byung ba'i gnas /
NK032(khi)004:1293: b+he ta la'i gling ni lho phyogs na b+he ta la'i gling bya ba yod pas de yin /
NK032(khi)004:1294: shing dra ba gtsug dgu bkod pa'i tshal ni shing
NK032(khi)004:1295: rigs mi gcig pa dgu'i nags dang tshal gyis rim
NK032(khi)004:1297: gnod sbyin 'brog gnas kyi sa ni der 'gro ba'i
NK032(khi)004:1298: lam ri bar gyi 'brog thar la bsngo ba la
NK032(khi)004:1299: sogs pas gnod sbyin mi ma yin chen pos mi
NK032(khi)004:1300: phyugs tshad thams cad las kyi za bar bsngosa pa
NK032(khi)004:1302: de brgal ba na dpal yon tan 'byung ba'i grong
NK032(khi)004:1303: khyer bya ba rig pa'i gnas lnga la sogs pa
NK032(khi)004:1304: yon tan ci yang 'byung ba'i grong khyer chen po
NK032(khi)004:1305: gcig yod pa'o // sh+r+ai sing has grong khyer der
NK032(khi)004:1306: 'gro ba la nye ring dang dka' sla ci tsam
NK032(khi)004:1308: der 'gro ba la nye ring ni mi yi yul
NK032(khi)004:1309: med pa'i lung stong na phar la 'gro ba la
NK032(khi)004:1310: bzla ba ril po bcu gsum gyi lam yod /
NK032(khi)004:1311: dka' sla ni lam na gcan gzan gdug pa can dang /
NK032(khi)004:1313: lha ma yin la sogs pa yod /
NK032(khi)004:1314: gcan gzan gdug pa can dang 'phrad na khrum gyis zos nas 'gro /
NK032(khi)004:1315: sbrul gdug pa can dang 'phrad na lce leb kyis
NK032(khi)004:1316: byas pas snag ma rnams kha ru sib la rus
NK032(khi)004:1317: pa rnams thang la dkar spung gis 'ong ba yin
NK032(khi)004:1318: / lha ma yin dang 'phrad na skad bton pa tsam gyis mig khrag khrul gyis 'chi ba yin /
NK032(khi)004:1319: de lta bu med na dang nged kyang 'gro ste gsungs so //
NK032(khi)004:1320: der sh+r+ai sing has som nyi en gcig zos te de bas nyen chung ba'am /
NK032(khi)004:1321: 'jigs pa chung ba'i lam 'dra ba med dam byas pas /
NK032(khi)004:1322: de bas nye zhing 'jigs ba chung ba'i lam ri'i
NK032(khi)004:1323: khong seng sa'i phug pa gcig nas phar la phyin
NK032(khi)004:1324: na / zla ba ril po drug na brtol 'ong ba'i lam gcig yod de /
NK032(khi)004:1325: de yang lam na phar la sbrul gdug pa can dang /
NK032(khi)004:1326: ri rab kyi khong seng na mi ma yin gyi grong khyer yod pas /
NK032(khi)004:1327: sbrul gdug pa can gyis nye mi nus pa la
NK032(khi)004:1328: rtsi ma gi ta zhes bya ba gla rtsi lus
NK032(khi)004:1329: la 'dogs dgos / mi ma yin gyi grong khyer
NK032(khi)004:1330: du 'khyams na ri rab kyi khong seng du 'khyams
NK032(khi)004:1332: mi ma yin gyi grong khyer gyi sgo sgrib pa
NK032(khi)004:1333: la zhun chen gyi mar me khyer na zla ba
NK032(khi)004:1334: ril po drug na brtol yong ba'i lam gcig yod
NK032(khi)004:1335: zer bas / der cis kyang 'gro dgos sems pa gcig byung nas /
NK032(khi)004:1336: sh+r+ai sing has der 'tsho ba'i yo byad dang /
NK032(khi)004:1337: dgos pa'i rdzas rtsi ma gi ta lus la byugs /
NK032(khi)004:1338: zhun chen gyi mar me khyer nas phyin pas zla
NK032(khi)004:1339: ba ril po drug na dpal yon tan 'byung ba'i
NK032(khi)004:1341: der slob dpon 'jam dpal bshes gnyen bya ba de ga na bzhugs dris pas /
NK032(khi)004:1342: slob dpon 'jam dpal bshes gnyen bya ba de nged
NK032(khi)004:1343: kyi yul du byon nas lo phyugs rtag tu legs
NK032(khi)004:1344: pa / char chu dus su phebs pa /
NK032(khi)004:1345: mi nad dang phyugs nad rgyun chad pa la sogs
NK032(khi)004:1346: pa bkra shis dang yon tan shin du 'phel bar
NK032(khi)004:1348: khong rang nged kyi zhal mjal ba dang ngo shes pa med zer ro //
NK032(khi)004:1349: gcig la dris gnyis la dris 'phrad tshad la dris
