NK032(khi)004:1350: kyang de skad zer ba las ngas ngo shes zer
NK032(khi)004:1352: de nas btsal bas kyang ma rnyed sdod pa yang ma tshugs nas /
NK032(khi)004:1353: cam mer phyin pas chu kha gcig tu brtol tsa na /
NK032(khi)004:1354: bud med chu len pa gcig 'dug nas gtam gcig
NK032(khi)004:1355: 'dri dgos sems nas de ru 'dug dang byas pas
NK032(khi)004:1356: / lan med par chu'i bum pa rgyab tu khyug
NK032(khi)004:1357: gis khur nas mi sdod par 'gro bar 'dug pas
NK032(khi)004:1358: / / de ma 'thad par tshor nas sh+r+ai sing
NK032(khi)004:1359: has kyang gong du rdzu 'phrul gyi dngos grub brnyes
NK032(khi)004:1360: / / pa yin pas / phyag g.yon pa kha
NK032(khi)004:1361: sbub kyis dengs byas te sa ni b+he sa byas
NK032(khi)004:1362: / / pa yin pas / pas / mo'i bum
NK032(khi)004:1363: pa rgyab nas khog gis gog nas sa la khrig
NK032(khi)004:1365: ro // der mos kyang rdzu 'phrul can du ngo
NK032(khi)004:1366: shes nas kha phyir log gi byas nas so gseb
NK032(khi)004:1367: nas shel dkar gyi gri cig car gyis bton nas
NK032(khi)004:1368: tsit+ta a b+hi shiny+tsa pra sa la zer nas brang
NK032(khi)004:1369: kha shags kyis phyes nas snying gi dkyil nas yang
NK032(khi)004:1370: dag grub pa'i lha mo brgyad dpal dang dgu 'dug
NK032(khi)004:1372: sh+r+ai sing has kyang bud med de rdzu 'phrul can gcig 'dug par shes nas /
NK032(khi)004:1373: sa ni sa ma ya dzahbyasa nas phyag rgya yar la dengs byas pas /
NK032(khi)004:1374: bum pa de sa nas khog gis gog gnas mo rang gi rgyab tu khyug gis song ngo //
NK032(khi)004:1376: tsit+ta a b+hi shiny+tsa mam zer nas brang kha cag gis zum mo //
NK032(khi)004:1378: a b+hi shiny+tsa ni dbang bskur ba /
NK032(khi)004:1379: mam ni zhal gsum pa yin te /
NK032(khi)004:1380: de yang sh+r+ai sing ha la yang dag thugs kyi lha mo brgyad dpal dang dgu'i zhal bstan /
NK032(khi)004:1381: dbang bskur nas zhal zlum pa'o //
NK032(khi)004:1383: khyod ci 'dod pa yin zer bas nga gzhan ci yang mi 'dod de /
NK032(khi)004:1384: slob dpon 'jam dpal bshes gnyen bya ba /
NK032(khi)004:1385: dpal yon tan 'byung ba'i grong khyer bya ba 'di
NK032(khi)004:1386: na bzhugs zer nas 'tshol du 'ong ba la ma
NK032(khi)004:1387: rnyed / khyod kyis ngo shes sam byas nas dris pas /
NK032(khi)004:1389: ngas ngo shes pa las gzhan sus kyang ngo mi shes te /
NK032(khi)004:1390: nga rang dam rang gis bcas pa'i sring mo bka'
NK032(khi)004:1391: skyong gi mkha' 'gro ma sde gsum bya ba las
NK032(khi)004:1392: / nga'i ming 'bar ma'i gdong can bya ba yin
NK032(khi)004:1393: te ltos dang zer nas ljags nar gyis brkyang pas
NK032(khi)004:1394: spyi bo ru lhag gis brtol nas gdong pa la
NK032(khi)004:1395: me 'bar ba bzhin du dmar ring gis byung ngo
NK032(khi)004:1398: ngas slob dpon 'jam dpal bshes gnyes khyod la bstan
NK032(khi)004:1399: gyis gsungs nas grong khyer der chu'i bum pa gnas
NK032(khi)004:1400: su skyel ba'i tshul du byas nas phyir byung ste
NK032(khi)004:1401: / slob dpon 'jam dpal bshes gnyen de ma gi yin no gsungs nas bltas pas /
NK032(khi)004:1402: btsun pa hral po gcig gis rmos thong zung gcig mdun du btsug /
NK032(khi)004:1403: gnya' thong zung gcig phrag la gzar nas /
NK032(khi)004:1404: sham thabs thod du bcings pa gcig gis glang la
NK032(khi)004:1405: lcag gis brab kyin zhing rmod du 'gro ba gcig
NK032(khi)004:1406: byung nas de'i drung du phyin nas dang po chos
NK032(khi)004:1409: btsun pa 'o skol la bza' bca' gcig zhu dang byas pas /
NK032(khi)004:1410: btsun pa de na re bza' bca' 'di ru ga na 'ong /
NK032(khi)004:1411: grong ya gi na nga'i jo mo yod cing de ru slong dang zer bas /
NK032(khi)004:1412: 'di la chos yod pa'i gzhung mi 'dug ste /
NK032(khi)004:1413: 'di khyim btsun nam khram btsun nam zog btsun gcig yin tshod 'dug ste /
NK032(khi)004:1414: gal te yin srid pas da dung rdzi rtog dgos sems nas /
NK032(khi)004:1415: jo mo de'i drung du phyin nas jo mo bza' ba gcig zhu dang byas pas /
NK032(khi)004:1416: khyod rang 'dir 'dug gcig nga la spags med pas btsal la 'ong zhes zer nas song bas /
NK032(khi)004:1417: tshong 'dus su 'gro ba la nyin lam bdun yod pa gcig mos yud cig la 'khor nas /
NK032(khi)004:1418: byi'u mchil pa bdun gson po nyos nas thu bar blug nas khyer byung ste /
NK032(khi)004:1419: mdun du brtol ba dang byi'u bdun po ltag pa phud nas bsad de /
NK032(khi)004:1420: spu btogs rgyu long phyungs nas 'bras chan gyi nang
NK032(khi)004:1421: du btsos nas 'bras chan dang gnyis mkhar gzhong gi
NK032(khi)004:1423: spags med 'di gsol bar zhu zer te /
NK032(khi)004:1424: sh+r+ai sing has spyir nga btsun pa'i cha byad du yod pas sha'i rnam la mi zhu /
NK032(khi)004:1425: de'i nang nas kyang dge slong gi cha byad du yod pas mi zhu /
NK032(khi)004:1426: de'i nang nas kyang nga la bsngosa nas bsad pa'i
NK032(khi)004:1427: sha 'di lta bu mi zhu bas phar la bzhes
NK032(khi)004:1429: rjes su yi rang chos pa rang du 'dug zer nas /
NK032(khi)004:1430: byi'u mchil sprad bdun po de lag tu blangs nas
NK032(khi)004:1431: se gol gtogs pa gcig byas pas sbrul chil byas
NK032(khi)004:1432: nas nam mkha' la tsi di ri ri 'phur nas
NK032(khi)004:1433: song ngo // der a ma jo mo 'di yang
NK032(khi)004:1434: bsad gso la sogs pa nus pa'i rdzu 'phrul can
NK032(khi)004:1435: song ngo // zhig 'dug pas / de tsug tu
NK032(khi)004:1436: song na da ci'i btsun pa de slob dpon 'jam
NK032(khi)004:1437: dpal bshes gnyen rang min pa'i gzhung mi 'dug pas
NK032(khi)004:1438: song ngo // zhig 'dug pas / / da rung du rdzi rtog dgos par 'dug sems nas /
NK032(khi)004:1439: jo mo do nub gnas g.yar po zhu dgos byas pas /
NK032(khi)004:1440: khyod rang der 'dug pas chog gsungs nas de ru bsdad tsa na /
NK032(khi)004:1441: de ring gi btsun pa hral po de der byung nas rtsa na yar nyal 'dug skad /
NK032(khi)004:1442: nangs par snga ba nas sh+r+ai seng has langs nas
NK032(khi)004:1443: rdo rje sems dpa'i mdo sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba zhes
NK032(khi)004:1444: bya ba zhal thon du bton pas /
NK032(khi)004:1445: khong gis ce regs na nas mdo de thon pa dang don la lta ci smos te /
NK032(khi)004:1446: tshig la'ang rmongs pa gsungs te tshig de rnams kyang mkhas par 'dug ste /
NK032(khi)004:1447: don ma go bar 'dug pas bya bar go byung bas /
NK032(khi)004:1448: der slob dpon 'jam dpal bshes gnyen yin nam gzhan de skad gsung ba mi yong sems skad /
NK032(khi)004:1449: de nas btsun pa de na re jo mo la spags tshol shog /
NK032(khi)004:1450: de nang btsun pa 'di la tsha ba 'dren dgos
NK032(khi)004:1451: zer nas yang jo mo des tshong 'dus nas bud
NK032(khi)004:1452: med kyi lag pa g.yon pa gru mo man chad
NK032(khi)004:1453: la gdub bu lnga dang ldan pa nyos nas byung
NK032(khi)004:1454: ste / 'bras chan dang gnyis mkhar gzhong gi nang
NK032(khi)004:1455: du drangs te spags med 'di gsol bar zhu zer
NK032(khi)004:1456: ste / skad / sngar bzhin du dge slong gi
NK032(khi)004:1457: cha byad du yod pas sha'i rnam pa mi zhu
NK032(khi)004:1458: ste / skad / / de'i nang nas kyang mi'i sha mi zhu /
NK032(khi)004:1459: de'i nang nas kyang bud med kyi sha mi zhu bas /
NK032(khi)004:1460: phar la bzhes par zhu byas pas /
NK032(khi)004:1461: rjes su yi rang chos pa rang du 'dug gsungs nas /
NK032(khi)004:1462: bud med kyi lag pa de nam mkha' la rgyang
NK032(khi)004:1463: gis bor nas se gol gtogs pa gcig mdzad pas
NK032(khi)004:1464: 'od kha dog lnga dang ldan pa 'ja' lta bu
NK032(khi)004:1465: zhig tu byas nas nam mkha' la yal nas song
NK032(khi)004:1466: skad / der the tshom ma zos te btsun pa
NK032(khi)004:1467: 'di slob dpon 'jam dpal bshes gnyen yin nges 'dug
NK032(khi)004:1468: skad / / jo mo 'di la rdzu 'phrul 'di lta bu 'dug bsam nas /
NK032(khi)004:1470: lha phyag dang bskor ba lan mang po byas nas /
NK032(khi)004:1472: khyed kyi rtogs pa bdag la bskyed par zhu 'tshal
NK032(khi)004:1473: byas nas gsol ba btab pas ci yang mi gsung
NK032(khi)004:1474: skad / de nas lha phyag nyin lan gsum mtshan lan gsum du btsal /
NK032(khi)004:1475: bskor ba nyin lan gsum mtshan lan gsum du byas
NK032(khi)004:1476: nas zla ba re re la zhu ba'i don re
NK032(khi)004:1477: phul kyang ci yang mi gsung nas /
NK032(khi)004:1478: da nam yang chos mi gnang bar 'dug pas /
NK032(khi)004:1479: nga rang gi yul du log nas 'gro dgos sems
NK032(khi)004:1480: nas khur tsa dang ka ba li khres po tsho
NK032(khi)004:1481: btegs nas gdams ngag ma gnang yang phyi phyag gcig
NK032(khi)004:1482: bya dgos sems nas mchod khang du phyin pa dang
NK032(khi)004:1483: / sh+r+ai sing ha gsungs nas dbu btegs gis byung nas /
NK032(khi)004:1484: a byas pa dang lan ci yang mi gsung bar gos kyis dbu hril gyis bstum nas song ngo //
NK032(khi)004:1485: gzhan gdams ngag ni mi ster 'bod don med /
NK032(khi)004:1486: mchod khang gi sbur ma dang 'bag 'bog mi gtsang
NK032(khi)004:1487: ba 'di tsho phyogs bya ba yin par byung sems
NK032(khi)004:1488: nas phyags pas ser bu'am tshang rlangs gcig gis phyags
NK032(khi)004:1489: kyang snga ma'i shul du btab nas byung ngo //
NK032(khi)004:1490: der lan bco brgyad du skad kyis phyags dgos byung ste /
NK032(khi)004:1491: thang chad nas slob dpon gyi mdun na krong nger langs nas yod tsa na /
NK032(khi)004:1492: slob dpon gyi dbu sngas na shing thog rdog po
NK032(khi)004:1493: che ba kha dog legs pa dri zhim pa gcig
NK032(khi)004:1494: 'dug nas da cing la 'bod pa de 'di zo
NK032(khi)004:1495: dang bya ba rang yin nam sems nas shing thog
NK032(khi)004:1496: de zos pas ro mchog brgyad dang ldan pa zhig
NK032(khi)004:1497: byung ste / de zos zin pa dang dug tu
NK032(khi)004:1498: gyur te skyug cing 'gyel nas shi 'phras byed cing
NK032(khi)004:1499: 'chi ba la thug nas yod tsa na /
NK032(khi)004:1500: thugs mug nas sh+r+ai sing ha'i thugs la shi na rung snang ba bdun shar te /
NK032(khi)004:1501: ga re slob dpon gyis gnya' thong zung gcig phrag la bkal /
NK032(khi)004:1502: rmos thong zung gcig mdun du btsug nas byung ba'i
NK032(khi)004:1503: dus na chos nyid kyi brda gcig yin te 'ong
NK032(khi)004:1504: ba la / ngas ma go ba shi na rung sems pa gcig byung /
NK032(khi)004:1505: byi'u mchil sprad bdun gyi sha drangs pa'i dus na chos nyid kyi brda gcig yin 'dug pa la /
NK032(khi)004:1506: ngas ma go ba shi na rung sems pa dang gnyis /
NK032(khi)004:1507: mdo sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba bton pa'i dus na chos nyid kyi brda gcig yin 'dug pa la /
NK032(khi)004:1508: ngas ma go ba shi na rung sems pa dang gsum /
NK032(khi)004:1509: bud med kyi lag pa g.yon pa drangs pa'i dus
NK032(khi)004:1510: na yang chos nyid kyi brda gcig yin 'dug pa
NK032(khi)004:1511: la / ngas ma go ba shi na rung sems pa dang bzhi /
NK032(khi)004:1512: slob dpon la gser gyi man+dala phul /
NK032(khi)004:1513: phyag dang skor ba byas nas gdams ngag zhus pa'i
NK032(khi)004:1514: dus na ci yang mi gsung ba chos nyid kyi
NK032(khi)004:1516: ngas ma go ba shi na rung sems pa dang lnga /
NK032(khi)004:1517: da nga 'gro dgos sems nas mchod khang du phyin pa dang /
NK032(khi)004:1518: sh+r+ai sing ha gsungs nas 'di phyogs bya ba yin
NK032(khi)004:1519: sems nas phyag pas sbar sbur lan bco brgyad du
NK032(khi)004:1520: phyags dgos byung ba de chos nyid kyi brda gcig
NK032(khi)004:1522: ngas ma go ba shi na rung sems pa dang drug /
NK032(khi)004:1523: de nas slob dpon gyi dbu sngas na shing thog
NK032(khi)004:1524: kha dog legs pa dri zhim pa gcig 'dug nas
NK032(khi)004:1525: 'di zo bya ba yin 'dug sems 'dug sems nas
NK032(khi)004:1526: / zos pas dug du gyur te skyug cing 'gyel
NK032(khi)004:1527: nas 'chi ba la thug pa'i dus na chos nyid
NK032(khi)004:1528: kyi brda' gcig yin 'dug pa la ngas ma go
NK032(khi)004:1529: / ba la / go ba med khyod rang shi na rung snyam pa dang bdun shar tsa na /
NK032(khi)004:1531: skyug pa'i 'phro yang chad nas slob dpon gyi mdun du krong der bsdad tsa na /
NK032(khi)004:1532: sh+r+ai sing ha khyod ci 'dod pa yin gsungs /
NK032(khi)004:1533: nga ni chos nyid kyi don skad cig ma gcig
NK032(khi)004:1534: gis rtogs nas tshe gcig gis sangs rgya ba gcig
NK032(khi)004:1536: 'o na khyod kyis da rung ma go'am gsungs /
NK032(khi)004:1537: bdag gis ni ma rig ma rtogs so zhus pas /
NK032(khi)004:1538: slob dpon 'jam dpal bshes gnyen gyis phyag g.yas pa slob dpon sh+r+ai sid+ha'i spyi bor brkyang nas /
NK032(khi)004:1539: a ha ho'i zhes byin gyis brlabs pas /
NK032(khi)004:1540: a ni skye ba med pa /
NK032(khi)004:1542: ho ni gnyis su med pa /
NK032(khi)004:1543: 'i ni gnyis su med pa'i don dbyer mi phyed pa /
NK032(khi)004:1544: dbyer mi phyed pa'i dus na dbyer phyed bya ba'am
NK032(khi)004:1545: mi phyed bya ba'i blo'i mtha' 'am tshig gi mtha'
NK032(khi)004:1546: zab cing phra ba tsam yang mi gnas pa'i chos
NK032(khi)004:1547: nyid kyi rang sgra'i ngang du sil gyis zhag bdun
NK032(khi)004:1549: ting nge 'dzin de las sad tsa na rjes kyi
NK032(khi)004:1550: shes pa la sems nyid dngos po gshis kyi gnas
NK032(khi)004:1551: lugs rang byung gi ye shes chen po de byas
NK032(khi)004:1552: pa dang bcos pa med par rang gsal du rgyud
NK032(khi)004:1554: de'i don de brjed kyis dogs pa'am mi brjed mi
NK032(khi)004:1555: yal bar brtan par bya ba'i phyir brjed rdo bstan
NK032(khi)004:1556: pa ni / a wan d+ha ra zhes brdas bstan no //
NK032(khi)004:1557: de la sh+r+ai sing ha khyod rang nam mkha'i dkyil 'di la ltos dang /
NK032(khi)004:1558: khyod rang gi rgyud la skyes pa de dper na
NK032(khi)004:1559: nam mkha'i dkyil dang 'dra ba yin gyi bya ba'i
NK032(khi)004:1560: brdar byung nas / sprin dang khu rlangs ni ma langs /
NK032(khi)004:1562: mdun gyi nam mkha' dag pa'i dkyil du bltas pas /
NK032(khi)004:1563: nam mkha' de dang po rgyu las ma byung /
NK032(khi)004:1564: bar du rdzas su ma grub /
NK032(khi)004:1565: tha ma rkyen gyis mi 'jig ste gsal la ngos gzung med pa gcig rtogs so //
NK032(khi)004:1566: dpe de bzhin du rang gi sems nyid blo'i mtha'
NK032(khi)004:1567: zab cing phra ba tsam yang mi gnas pa de
NK032(khi)004:1568: / dang po rgyu 'di las byung bya ba mi 'dug /
NK032(khi)004:1569: bar du dngos po'i rdzas gang du yang ma grub /
NK032(khi)004:1570: tha ma rkyen bzang ngan gang gis kyang mi 'jig pa /
NK032(khi)004:1571: gsal la rtog pa med pa nam mkha'i dkyil lta bu gcig tu rtogs so //
NK032(khi)004:1572: der slob dpon 'jam dpal bshes gnyen gyi zhal nas /
NK032(khi)004:1573: ngas gnya' thong zung gcig phrag la gzar /
NK032(khi)004:1574: rmos thong zung gcig mdun du btsug pa'i dus su
NK032(khi)004:1575: thabs shes rab kyi sgo nas bstan pa yin te
NK032(khi)004:1577: byi'u mchil pa bdun gyi sha drangs pa de /
NK032(khi)004:1578: rnam par shes pa tshogs drug ngo bo gcig tu
NK032(khi)004:1579: 'dus par bstan pa yin te khyod kyis ma go
NK032(khi)004:1580: // mdo sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba bton pa'i dus na
NK032(khi)004:1581: chos thams cad bsam brjod dang bral bar bstan pa
NK032(khi)004:1582: yin te khyod kyis ma go //
NK032(khi)004:1583: bud med kyi lag pa g.yon pa gdub bu lnga dang bcas pa gcig drangs pa'i dus su /
NK032(khi)004:1584: bud med shes rab kyi rang bzhin la gdub bu
NK032(khi)004:1585: lnga ye shes lngar 'char bar bstan pa yin te
NK032(khi)004:1587: man+dala phul nas chos zhu ba'i dus su ngas ci
NK032(khi)004:1588: yang ma smras pa de don smra brjod dang bral
NK032(khi)004:1589: bar bstan pa yin te khyod kyis ma go //
NK032(khi)004:1590: sbar sbur lan bco brgyad du 'phyag tu bcug pa
NK032(khi)004:1591: de khyod la khams bco brgyad kyi sgrib pa zab
NK032(khi)004:1592: cing phra ba gcig 'dug pa de sbyong ba'i ched
NK032(khi)004:1593: du bla ma'i mchod khang phyags pa'i las byed du
NK032(khi)004:1594: bcug pa yin te khyod kyis ma go //
NK032(khi)004:1595: shing thog kha dog legs pa rdog po che ba
NK032(khi)004:1596: dri zhim pa de khyod phyi gzung ba'i yul la
NK032(khi)004:1597: chags pa yin / ro mchog brgyad dang ldan par
NK032(khi)004:1598: tshor ba de nang 'dzin pa'i sems la chags pa
NK032(khi)004:1599: chags pa yin / yin / gzung 'dzin gnyis po dug tu gyur nas na bas /
NK032(khi)004:1600: shi la khad pa'i dus su /
NK032(khi)004:1601: shi na rung bdun shar bas bshags par song nas sgrib pa dag nas sos pa yin /
NK032(khi)004:1602: ngas kyang de gong nas bstan pa yin te khyod
NK032(khi)004:1603: rang las sgrib che bas ma go ba yin gsungs
NK032(khi)004:1604: skad / der bstan pa tsam gyis rtogs /
NK032(khi)004:1605: rtogs pa tsam gyis mngon du gyur te /
NK032(khi)004:1606: der sgrib pa sbyangs dka' ba nyon mongs pa dang shes bya'i sgrib pa de nyid du dag /
NK032(khi)004:1607: thob par dka' ba mchog gi dngos grub de nyid du thob /
NK032(khi)004:1608: thun mong gi dngos grub zhar la byung ste /
NK032(khi)004:1609: dper na 'bras 'khor ma lo legs na phub sog zhar las 'byung ba bzhin nam /
NK032(khi)004:1610: yang na nor bu rin po che sngon la rnyed nas mchod pa bya gin gsol ba btab na /
NK032(khi)004:1611: rtog pa med kyang dgos 'dod 'phral la 'byung ba
NK032(khi)004:1612: bzhin du mchog gi dngos grub thob nas gzhan don
NK032(khi)004:1613: du sems bskyed kyin gsol ba btab na /
NK032(khi)004:1615: de nas sh+r+ai sing ha de bya 'phur ba'am rdzi bskyod pa'am gom pa gcig gis 'gong pa'am /
NK032(khi)004:1616: bya rmyang gcig gi sa brtol ba bzhin du gyur te /
NK032(khi)004:1617: dpal yon tan 'byung ba'i grong khyer nas tsha ba thon nas byon pas /
NK032(khi)004:1618: dpal sh+r+ai na len+d+ra'i gtsug lag khang du zla ba
NK032(khi)004:1619: ril po bcu gsum gyi lam yod pa la gro
NK032(khi)004:1620: khar brtol ba'o // de nas rdo rje gdan gyi
NK032(khi)004:1621: byang sgo nas tshur la phyi pa mu stegs pa'i
NK032(khi)004:1622: rtsod pa dar bas nang pa sangs rgyas pa'i bstan
NK032(khi)004:1623: pa nub la khad pa la /
NK032(khi)004:1624: slob dpon sh+r+ai sing has phyi pa mu stegs pa tshar bcad nas /
NK032(khi)004:1625: nang pa sangs rgyas pa'i bstan pa dar zhing rgyas par mdzad do //
NK032(khi)004:1626: chos gra'i slob dpon sh+r+ai sing ha bya bar grags te /
NK032(khi)004:1627: dgra bcom pa lnga brgya'i dpon po mdzad do //
NK032(khi)004:1628: de nas bka' sems phyogs kyi don bod du ji ltar bsgyur ba ni /
NK032(khi)004:1629: kun gzhi'i gsang ba dag pa'i dbyings nas rang shes rig gi rgyal po /
NK032(khi)004:1630: yid byed pa po kun tu bzang po'i zhal nas bka' stsal pa ni /
NK032(khi)004:1631: bka' sa man+ta nam mkha' dang mnyam pa klong dgu
NK032(khi)004:1632: bam po nyi khri le'u khri drug stong la sogs
NK032(khi)004:1633: pa sh+aakya thub pa la bshad do //
NK032(khi)004:1634: sh+aakya thub pas yul so ma pu ri /
NK032(khi)004:1636: lang+ka pu ri gsum du nyid las mi gzhan pa'i 'khor kun tu bzang po /
NK032(khi)004:1637: kun tu bzang po'i sprul pa rdo rje sems dpa' /
NK032(khi)004:1638: de'i sprul pa sems dag lha'i bu gsum la bshad do //
NK032(khi)004:1639: sems dag lha'i bu des dga' rab rdo rje la bshad do //
NK032(khi)004:1640: dga' rab rdo rjes 'jam dpal bshes gnyen la bshad do //
NK032(khi)004:1641: des sh+r+ai sing ha la bshad /
NK032(khi)004:1642: sh+r+ai sing ha la lung dang man ngag gi chos thams cad 'dzoms par yod pa la /
NK032(khi)004:1643: slob dpon sh+r+ai sing ha bzhugs pa'i dus tsa na /
NK032(khi)004:1644: bod kyi rgyal po khri srong lde'u btsan dad pa skyes pa'i sku drin la /
NK032(khi)004:1645: o rgyan gyi mkhan po pad+ma sam+b+ha wa dang bod+hi
NK032(khi)004:1646: sa t+wa la sogs spyan drangs nas dbus kyi bsam
NK032(khi)004:1647: yas dang ru bzhi'i mtha' 'dul la sogs pa'i gtsug
NK032(khi)004:1648: lag khang brgya rtsa brgyad la sogs pa ni bzhengs
NK032(khi)004:1649: su gsol nas / mkhas pa mang po gdan drangs nas chos grwa btsugs nas /
NK032(khi)004:1650: dam pa'i chos gsang sngags mtshan nyid rgyu 'bras kyi chos dar bar byas pa la /
NK032(khi)004:1651: chos de dag gis rgyal po'i thugs thag ma chod nas /
NK032(khi)004:1652: bod du sku 'khrungs pa'i mnga' bdag byang chub sems
NK032(khi)004:1653: dpa' khri srong lde'u btsan gyis bod kyi dge slong
NK032(khi)004:1655: rgya mi mi bdun la bka' stsal pa ni /
NK032(khi)004:1656: rgyal po de'ang dang po rgya gar nas tshe 'phos pa yin pas /
NK032(khi)004:1657: rgya gar gyi yul na man ngag gi chos yod pa cha'ang yod /
NK032(khi)004:1658: rgya gar na man ngag gi chos yod bya ba snyan du yang gsan nas /
NK032(khi)004:1659: rgyal po'i zhal nas rgya gar gyi yul ni ston pa'i zhabs kyis bcags shing /
NK032(khi)004:1660: ston pa ni thams cad mkhyen pa yin pas /
NK032(khi)004:1661: theg pa mtha' dag las bogs byung ba /
NK032(khi)004:1662: rgyu 'bras gnyis las la zlo ba'i chos skad cig
NK032(khi)004:1663: mas don rtogs nas tshe gcig gis 'tshang rgya ba
NK032(khi)004:1664: gcig mi bzhugs mi srid pas /
NK032(khi)004:1665: de len du gtong dgos pas na /
NK032(khi)004:1666: lon na bod yul dbus su sus 'gyur ba'i bsod
NK032(khi)004:1667: nams kyi tshad ni gang dang yang mi mnyam pa
NK032(khi)004:1668: gang gis 'ong ba gcig gtong dgos so byas pas
NK032(khi)004:1669: / li rtag po che'am li khra mi la sogs
NK032(khi)004:1670: pa shin tu shes rab che la thabs mkhas pa
NK032(khi)004:1671: / rnams na re / chos zhu ba la mi btang ba sus mi 'ong ste /
NK032(khi)004:1672: 'phrang dgu dang gcan dgu la sogs pa shin tu dka' ba yod zer bas /
NK032(khi)004:1674: nor yang shor ba'i nyen yod pas /
NK032(khi)004:1677: pra phabs nas des na kha 'cham par 'dis lon
NK032(khi)004:1678: 'ong zer ba phyis mi 'gyod pa'i mi zhig gtong
NK032(khi)004:1679: dgos zer nas / der rgya nag po'i dpyad mkhan la mkhas pa b+he shog pra dang /
NK032(khi)004:1680: rgya gar gyi pra mkhan la mkhas pa pra sen dang /
NK032(khi)004:1681: li'i yul gyi mo ma la mkhas pa dpe ni gu dang de gsum la dpyad byas /
NK032(khi)004:1683: mo btab pas rgya gar gyi yul na chos nyid
NK032(khi)004:1684: kyi don skad cig mas rtogs nas tshe gcig gis
NK032(khi)004:1685: 'tshang rgya ba'i chos 'di zhu ba la gzhan sus
NK032(khi)004:1687: gtsang gi snye mo bye mkhar bya ba na /
NK032(khi)004:1689: yum bran kha bza' sgron skyid kyi bu /
NK032(khi)004:1690: pa gor gan 'jag thang rta bya ba byis pa lo brgyad lon pa gcig yod de /
NK032(khi)004:1691: de btang na chos nyid kyi don skad cig ma
NK032(khi)004:1692: gcig gis rtogs nas tshe gcig gis 'tshang rgya ba
NK032(khi)004:1693: de lon 'ong zer nas gsum kha 'cham par byung
NK032(khi)004:1694: ngo // de nas rgyal po blon 'khor dang bcas pa nyi shu rtsa lnga /
NK032(khi)004:1695: gtsang gi snye mo bye mkhar bya ba der byon
NK032(khi)004:1696: nas de'i dus su rgyal po mi che ba'i zhud
NK032(khi)004:1697: kyis phyag dang zhe sa dka' bas mi gzhan gyis
NK032(khi)004:1698: mjal bar ma nus nas sgo phyir mi'i rgyu 'grul
NK032(khi)004:1699: chad de nyin pa phyed ka gcig tshun chad lus
NK032(khi)004:1700: / de nas byis pa gcig sngon du byung nas
NK032(khi)004:1701: byis pa de la rgyal pos zhal kyal du byas
NK032(khi)004:1702: te byis pa khyod kyi pha gar song byas pas
NK032(khi)004:1704: nga'i pha gtam 'tshol du song zer /
NK032(khi)004:1705: khyod kyi ma gar song byas pas /
NK032(khi)004:1706: nga'i ma mig 'tshol du song zer /
NK032(khi)004:1707: khyod rang gar phyin pa yin byas pas /
NK032(khi)004:1708: nga rang 'gro ba'i don phyin pa yin zer ro //
NK032(khi)004:1709: de la rgyal po mnyes te nged 'dod pa'i bu de 'di rang yin te 'ong /
NK032(khi)004:1710: kha brda dang la nye bzang gsungs skad /
NK032(khi)004:1711: de nas bu de na re /
NK032(khi)004:1712: pha gtam 'tshol du song zer ba de /
NK032(khi)004:1713: phas chang btsal nas byung ste gtam 'byung ba'i rkyen chang lags skad /
NK032(khi)004:1714: ma mig 'tshol du song zer ba de /
NK032(khi)004:1715: mas me khyer nas byung ste mun pa sel ba dang bag dro ba me lags skad /
NK032(khi)004:1716: nga rang 'gro ba'i don la phyin pa yin zer tsa na ri'u lug btsas nas byung skad /
NK032(khi)004:1717: de bzhin du rgya gar gyi chos gtam bod du
NK032(khi)004:1718: byung nas bod ma rig pa'i mun pa sel ba
NK032(khi)004:1719: dang / zab mo'i chos lon nas 'gro ba'i don
NK032(khi)004:1720: du phan thogs 'ong ba'i barda'am la nye ru byung
NK032(khi)004:1721: dang / ba lags skad / der pa gor he
NK032(khi)004:1722: 'dod kyis rgyal po blon 'khor dang bcas pa rnams
NK032(khi)004:1725: drung mar dang bsang bu drangs nas /
NK032(khi)004:1726: mnga' bdag 'di na yar byon pa zhabs don ci mnga' dris pas /
NK032(khi)004:1728: gzhan don ci yang mi bdog ste /
NK032(khi)004:1729: rgya gar gyi yul na rgyu 'bras kyi chos mtha'
NK032(khi)004:1730: dag las bogs phyung ba chos nyid kyi don skad
NK032(khi)004:1731: cig mas rtogs nas tshe gcig gis 'tshang rgya ba'i
NK032(khi)004:1733: gang bas kyang chos 'di gal che bar 'dug pas /
NK032(khi)004:1734: de zhur gtong ba la gzhan gang gis kyang mi
NK032(khi)004:1735: 'ong bar khyod kyi bu 'dis lon 'ong bar kha
NK032(khi)004:1736: 'cham byung bas 'di slong du 'ong ba yin gsungs
NK032(khi)004:1738: nged kyi bu 'di lo brgyad las ma lon pas
NK032(khi)004:1739: rgya gar du 'gro ba la 'phrad dgu dang gcan
NK032(khi)004:1740: dgu la sogs pa dka' ba'i 'phrang mang po yod
NK032(khi)004:1741: zer bas / rgya gar du yang mi brtol chos zhu ba yang da dung mi 'ong /
NK032(khi)004:1742: rgan rgon gnyis la bu yang 'di las med pas de skad mi gsung bar zhu byas pas /
NK032(khi)004:1743: der rgyal po'i zhal nas lo gzhon yang da lta nas gtong ba min cing /
NK032(khi)004:1744: lan gcig 'gro ba 'ong tsa na gtong ba yin cing /
NK032(khi)004:1745: gzhan gyis 'ong bar mi 'dug pas bu 'di nga la mi sbyin pa'i thabs med ces gsungs pas /
NK032(khi)004:1746: der ma sbyin na rgyal po'i bka' chad 'ong bas byin skad /
NK032(khi)004:1747: de nas mnga' bdag rgyal po'i zhal nas /
NK032(khi)004:1748: pha ma gnyis kyi gnyer kyang nga rang gis byed 'ong gsungs nas /
NK032(khi)004:1749: bza' mi gsum ka mar la spyan drangs nas /
NK032(khi)004:1750: pha ma gnyis dar gcig rog pa rtsar bzhugs su bcug /
NK032(khi)004:1751: bee ro tsa na brag dmar bsam yas su bzhugs
NK032(khi)004:1752: su bcug nas lo brgyad kyi bar du zas dkar
NK032(khi)004:1753: gsum dang mngar gsum gsol ba yin /
NK032(khi)004:1754: shes rab bskyed pa dang blo 'phel ba'i gzungs bsgrub tu bcug nas /
NK032(khi)004:1755: de nas lo brgyad ga nyis bcu drug lon tsa na rgya gar du 'gro ba la /
NK032(khi)004:1756: rgya gar gyi mis bod kyi lus la gser sbas pa rnyed na mi bsad gser phrog 'gro bas /
NK032(khi)004:1757: gser mi rnyed par bya ba'i thabs la bee ro
NK032(khi)004:1758: tsa na'i dbu skra bzhar nas gser gyi pa tra
NK032(khi)004:1759: bdun thod pa'i dbyibs su brdungs nas bu ga gser
NK032(khi)004:1760: du tshor tsam pa mang po phug nas dbu la
NK032(khi)004:1761: bkab ste dbu skra phyir nag thibs kyis phyungs nas
NK032(khi)004:1762: / lho brag gi gtsang the len pa dang /
NK032(khi)004:1763: na len+t+ra bya ba'i bu gtsang sngon po legs grub
NK032(khi)004:1764: bya ba lo nyi shu rtsa lnga lon pa go
NK032(khi)004:1765: mtho la shes rab che ba gcig dang /
NK032(khi)004:1766: bee ro tsa na gnyis 'grogs nas chos len du btang ba la /
NK032(khi)004:1767: khong gnyis bsam yas +aar+ya pa lo'i gling du /
NK032(khi)004:1768: nged spun gnyis kyis rgya gar nas chos lon nam mi lon /
NK032(khi)004:1769: 'gro ba gzhan la phan thogs sam mi thogs 'phags pas ston cig ces dmod bor nas gzims pas /
NK032(khi)004:1770: slob dpon bee ro tsa nas srod la rmi lam rmis pa /
NK032(khi)004:1771: sngon po legs grub la dris pa /
NK032(khi)004:1773: bzhengs dang bzhengs dang yar bzhengs dang //
NK032(khi)004:1774: mdang sum srod la thun gcig log pa'i rmi lam na //
NK032(khi)004:1775: skyes pa gzhon du nyi shu rtsa lnga yi //
NK032(khi)004:1776: khong bkral snying btsir chu ser thams cad mthur la 'dzag pa rmis //
NK032(khi)004:1777: khyed kyis shes sam bdag la bstan du gsol //
NK032(khi)004:1779: sngon po legs grub kyis lan btab pa /
NK032(khi)004:1781: srod la thun gcig log pa'i rmi lam na //
NK032(khi)004:1782: skyes pa gzhon nu'i nyi shu rtsa lnga yi //
NK032(khi)004:1783: khong bkral snying btsir chu ser thams cad mthur la zag pa de //
NK032(khi)004:1784: rgya gar mkhas pa nyi shu rtsa lnga yi //
NK032(khi)004:1785: thugs kyi dgongs pa bod du lon nas kyang //
NK032(khi)004:1786: las sgrib thams cad ma lus dag pa'i brda //
NK032(khi)004:1787: rmi lam mi ngan rmi lam bzang gsungs skad //
NK032(khi)004:1788: de nas yang bee ro tsa na gung la log pa'i rmi lam rmis pa /
NK032(khi)004:1790: nam gung thun gcig log pa'i rmi lam na //
NK032(khi)004:1791: bu mo na chung gzhon nu gsum gyis ni //
NK032(khi)004:1792: spyi bor yi ge a gcig bzhag pa rmis //
NK032(khi)004:1793: khyed kyis shes sam bdag la bstan du gsol //
NK032(khi)004:1795: sngon po legs grub kyis lan btab pa /
NK032(khi)004:1797: nam phyed thun gcig log pa'i rmi lam na //
NK032(khi)004:1798: bu mo na chung gzhon nu gsum gyis ni //
NK032(khi)004:1799: spyi bor yi ge a gcig bzhag pa ni //
NK032(khi)004:1800: bka' skyong mkha' 'gro sde gsum byin brlabs nas //
NK032(khi)004:1801: skad cig rtogs nas tshe gcig 'tshang rgya ba'i //
NK032(khi)004:1802: skye med don de khyed kyis lon pa'i rtags //
NK032(khi)004:1803: rmi lam mi ngan rmi lam bzang gsungs skad //
NK032(khi)004:1804: yang bee ro tsa nas tho rangs gzims pa'i rmi lam byung ba dris pas /
NK032(khi)004:1806: tho rangs thun gcig log pa'i rmi lam na //
NK032(khi)004:1807: nyi zla zung gcig gnam la shar ba la //
NK032(khi)004:1808: gcig ni nam mkha'i mthongs su nub pa rmis //
NK032(khi)004:1809: gcig ni has po'i ri la 'od shar nas //
NK032(khi)004:1810: slar la tsha ba'i rong du nub pa rmis //
NK032(khi)004:1811: khyed kyis shes sam bdag la bstan du gsol //
NK032(khi)004:1813: legs grub kyis lan btab pa /
NK032(khi)004:1815: tho rangs thun gcig log pa'i rmin lam na //
NK032(khi)004:1816: nyi zla zung gcig gnam la shar ba de //
NK032(khi)004:1817: rgya gar mkhas pa'i dam chos len pa'i rtags //
NK032(khi)004:1818: gcig ni nam mkha'i mthongs su nub pa de //
NK032(khi)004:1819: sngon po legs grub lam du 'gum pa'i rtags //
NK032(khi)004:1820: gcig ni has po ri la 'od shar te //
NK032(khi)004:1821: slar la tsha ba'i rong du nub pa de //
NK032(khi)004:1822: bee ro tsa na bod du byon nas kyang //
NK032(khi)004:1823: mnga' bdag rgyal po nyid la chos bstan nas //
NK032(khi)004:1824: slar la tsha ba'i rong du spyugs pa'i rtags //
NK032(khi)004:1825: rmi lam phyed bzang phyed mi bzang du gda' //
NK032(khi)004:1826: ji ltar 'dug kyang dam chos len du gshegs //
NK032(khi)004:1828: de nas khong gnyis rgya gar yul du chos len du 'gro ba la /
NK032(khi)004:1830: gser gyi pa tra dgu bardzangasa nas btab pa la /
NK032(khi)004:1831: de nas rgya gar gyi tshur 'phrang shing 'phrang bya bar brtol tsa na /
NK032(khi)004:1833: khong gnyis bsad la gser phye phrog par byas tsa na /
NK032(khi)004:1834: bee ro tsa nas cho 'phrul bstan pa /
NK032(khi)004:1835: rin po che'i za ma tog gcig gis nang du
NK032(khi)004:1836: lcags kyi spu gri rnon po reg na chod du
NK032(khi)004:1837: 'gro ba de lta bu gcig tu sku sprul nas
NK032(khi)004:1838: bsdad pas / 'phrang srung ba'i dpon ku m+aa ra
NK032(khi)004:1839: d+ha ru bya ba de shin tu ngo mtshar skyes
NK032(khi)004:1840: bsdad pas / nas / 'di bod bu gcig 'dug
NK032(khi)004:1841: 'phro la lcags kyi spu gri gcig song 'dug pa
NK032(khi)004:1842: bsdad pas / nas / / 'di bsad du mi
NK032(khi)004:1843: btub pa gcig 'dug pas 'di zhog la zla bo
NK032(khi)004:1845: legs grub bsad kyis dogs nas bee ro tsa nas
NK032(khi)004:1846: mtha'i mon bu gcig tu sprul nas 'phrang srung ba
NK032(khi)004:1847: la rnams la bka' stsal pa /
NK032(khi)004:1849: skye shi gnyis med nam mkha'i yul //
NK032(khi)004:1850: snang gsal mun sel cir yang sprul pa'i sku //
NK032(khi)004:1851: 'dzam gling mun sel nyi ma lta bu yin //
NK032(khi)004:1852: gsal khyab nam mkha' lta bu'i lus 'di la //
NK032(khi)004:1853: bsad dang ma bsad shi dang ma shi med //
NK032(khi)004:1854: srog 'di bcad na khyed la sdig pa yongs //
NK032(khi)004:1855: sgyu ma'i gser phye 'di rnams khyed khyer la //
NK032(khi)004:1856: lam rgyus ji ltar yin pa bstan du gsol //
NK032(khi)004:1858: gser khyor ba gang 'phrang srung ba la byin pas /
NK032(khi)004:1859: 'phrang srung bas kyang gsod ma nus te /
NK032(khi)004:1860: lam rgyus ma nor bar bstan nas btang ste /
NK032(khi)004:1861: rdo rje gdan du brtol nas zla ba gcig gi bar du chos grwa'i slob dpon su yis byed /
NK032(khi)004:1862: man ngag chos la su mkhas dris pas /
NK032(khi)004:1863: de tsa na slob dpon sh+r+ai sing ha pra ha bya ba de chos grwa'i slob dpon yang mdzad /
NK032(khi)004:1864: man ngag gi chos la'ang mkhas te /
NK032(khi)004:1865: spyir sgra bsgyur ba la shin tu mkhas pa gcig lags skad /
NK032(khi)004:1866: der lo ts+aa ba gnyis kyis pan+di ta sh+r+ai sing ha de gang la'ang mkhas par thag chod de /
NK032(khi)004:1867: pan+di ta sh+r+ai sing ha de rdo rje gdan gyi
NK032(khi)004:1868: byang phyogs yul d+ha he na'i 'du khang gi byang
NK032(khi)004:1869: chub kyi shing drung na bzhugs pa la /
NK032(khi)004:1870: bod kyi ban+d+he gnyis kyis chu len pa gcig la
NK032(khi)004:1871: barngana par gser phye khyor ba gang byin nas phrin
NK032(khi)004:1872: bardzangasa pa / bo d+hi sat+wa karma ku gu ta la sogs kyi yi ge zhig bskur bar /
NK032(khi)004:1873: sh+r+ai sing has bod kyi skad du 'di ltar go ste /
NK032(khi)004:1874: byang chub sems dpa' 'phags pa khyod //
NK032(khi)004:1875: 'gro ba rigs drug bsod nams mi lus sku //
NK032(khi)004:1876: rin chen 'bar ba sde snod ma lus dbyig /
NK032(khi)004:1877: yid bzhin nor ltar thugs rje'i stobs mchog can //
NK032(khi)004:1878: bod kyi dge bsnyen mi nag bdag dngos la //
NK032(khi)004:1879: ye shes 'od zer ston la thugs rje'i zhags pas zungs //
NK032(khi)004:1881: slob dpon sh+r+ai sing has de'i lan du /
NK032(khi)004:1882: sa ma ya a pa ra mi ta dz+ny+aa na bya ba gcig bskur te /
NK032(khi)004:1883: bee ro tsa nas sgra de bod skad du 'di ltar go ste /
NK032(khi)004:1884: dam tshig chen pos bdag bskul na //
NK032(khi)004:1885: mi 'phrad pa yi dbang yang med //
NK032(khi)004:1886: 'gro ba rigs drug sangs rgyas rgyur mnyam yang //
NK032(khi)004:1887: 'phags pa'i byang chub sems la ston pa khyod kyis gnyer //
NK032(khi)004:1888: sems kyi rus pas yan lag thang bcad nas //
NK032(khi)004:1889: dka' bas byon pa bdag kyang dga' bar mchis //
NK032(khi)004:1890: shes pa bsdur la khad kyis 'phrad par bgyi //
NK032(khi)004:1891: bya ba thon pa'i lan byung bas /
NK032(khi)004:1892: chu len pa des srod tsa na mjal ba'i dus btab nas dus tshod der mjal tsa na /
NK032(khi)004:1893: gser gyi pa tra gnyis dang gser phye bre gang phul te /
NK032(khi)004:1895: rgyu 'bras gnyis las la bzla ba'i chos gcig zhu 'tshal byas pas /
NK032(khi)004:1896: slob dpon sh+r+ai sing ha de la mnyes nas bod
NK032(khi)004:1897: kyi ban+d+he gnyis la rgyal pos bka' stsal ba'i steng
NK032(khi)004:1898: du khyed gnyis kyis gser phye khur nas dka' las
NK032(khi)004:1900: man ngag gi chos 'di bod kyi yul du dar ba'i dus la bab pa gcig 'dug pas /
NK032(khi)004:1901: khyod la bskur nas ni gtong ste /
NK032(khi)004:1902: thabs ni shin tu nas kyang dka' bas man ngag
NK032(khi)004:1903: gi chos zab mo 'di dag ni rgya gar gyi
NK032(khi)004:1904: yul 'di rang du'ang dar du mi ster bas /
NK032(khi)004:1905: bod yul du bskur ba tshor na 'o skol gsum
NK032(khi)004:1906: ka'i srog la nyen 'ong bas thabs legs su byed
NK032(khi)004:1907: dgos pas / khyed gnyis kyis nyin mo rgyu 'bras kyi chos bsgyur cig gsungs nas /
NK032(khi)004:1908: dus de tsa na pan+di ta phyi ma bdun po tshang bar bzhugs pas /
NK032(khi)004:1909: bdun ka la gser phye phul phyed phyed phul nas
NK032(khi)004:1910: lo gcig tu mdo sde dang sde snod kyi chos
NK032(khi)004:1911: gsan / de nas gsang sngags kyi chos lag len dang bcas pa lo gnyis su bsgyur ro //
NK032(khi)004:1912: de nas lo gcig tu dbang bzhi rdzogs par bskur ro //
NK032(khi)004:1913: de nas slob dpon sh+r+ai sing ha'i zhal nas /
NK032(khi)004:1914: da thabs legs par byas na man ngag gi chos 'chad dgos gsungs nas /
NK032(khi)004:1915: pha bong gsum la sgyed pu byas pa'i steng du rdza ma gcig bzhag ste /
NK032(khi)004:1916: de'i nang du zhugs te rdza ma yang d+r+wa bar
NK032(khi)004:1917: bcug nas kha slang chus bkang ba gcig gis bcad
NK032(khi)004:1918: de / de'i khar bya spu gtor nas rdza ma
NK032(khi)004:1919: de la brangs dung gi mchu btsugs nas khyim phug
NK032(khi)004:1920: nas zangs dung gi nang nas phar la bshad /
NK032(khi)004:1921: bod kyi ban+de gnyis kyis sha ba'i yo ba zhu
NK032(khi)004:1922: gyon nas khang pa'i phyi logs nas nam gyi gung
NK032(khi)004:1923: la chos nyan / nyin mo rgyu 'bras kyi chos bsgyur ro //
NK032(khi)004:1924: de yang sngon la man ngag gi chos bod du byung ba'i rtags su rig pa'i khu byug bshad /
NK032(khi)004:1925: man ngag gting phyin par 'byung ba'i rtags su rtsal chen sprugs pa bshad /
NK032(khi)004:1926: man ngag gi chos 'di rnams lta ba'i rgyal po yin pa'i rtags su khyung chen lding ba bshad /
NK032(khi)004:1927: man ngag gi chos 'di rnams shin tu dmar ba'i
NK032(khi)004:1928: rtags su rdo la gser zhun bya ba bshad nas
NK032(khi)004:1929: / de nas bod kyi ban+de gnyis tshim mam byas pas /
NK032(khi)004:1930: legs grub kyis tshim mo zer /
NK032(khi)004:1931: bee ro tsa na da rung ma tshim zer bar /
NK032(khi)004:1932: de nas man ngag gi chos nam mkha' che dang /
NK032(khi)004:1934: rgya mtsho'i klong la sogs pa bshad pas kyang tshim ma zer nas /
NK032(khi)004:1935: legs grub kyi bsam pa la /
NK032(khi)004:1936: bee ro tsa na kho mnga' bdag gis bkur ba'i
NK032(khi)004:1937: lo ts+aa ba yin pas kho dang 'grogs nas phyin
NK032(khi)004:1939: nga rang a ma rgas pa la snyad btags nas sngon la phyin la chos bshad dgos sems nas /
NK032(khi)004:1940: bee ro tsa na la khyod phyir na tshur la byon cig /
NK032(khi)004:1941: nga rang a ma rgas pas ma shi ba la 'gro dgos yod gsungs nas gshegs pa la /
NK032(khi)004:1942: slob dpon sh+r+ai sing ha dang bee ro tsa nas skyel chung mdzad nas log tsa na /
NK032(khi)004:1943: slob dpon sh+r+ai sing ha'i thugs kyis mkhyen nas bee ro tsa na /
NK032(khi)004:1944: sngon po legs grub gcan 'phrang dang po bas bkrongs pa gsungs pas /
NK032(khi)004:1945: grogs po bkrongs pa sems nas bee ro tsa na spyan chab shor te /
NK032(khi)004:1946: nga yang lan gcig bod du chos ma thon par de 'dra gcig 'ong nyen yod sems nas /
NK032(khi)004:1947: de'i rjes la ga re nga'i snga ma'i chos de
NK032(khi)004:1948: rnams thos pa'i shes rab sgra 'ba' zhig tu 'dug
NK032(khi)004:1949: / bsam pa'i shes rab sgra don phyed mar 'dug /
NK032(khi)004:1950: sgom pa'i shes rab don du 'dug kyang thos bsam
NK032(khi)004:1951: sgom gsum gyis blo sbyangs dgos pa'i chos su 'dug
NK032(khi)004:1952: / skad cig mas don rtogs nas tshe gcig gis
NK032(khi)004:1953: 'tshang rgya ba'i chos su snga ma'i de dag la
NK032(khi)004:1955: lam de rang du dbu skra zhar nas gser gyi
NK032(khi)004:1956: pa tra bdun rim pa thad du bkog nas de
NK032(khi)004:1957: tsho bkrus phyi bdar byas nas /
NK032(khi)004:1958: slob dpon sh+r+ai sing ha'i phyag tu phul te /
NK032(khi)004:1960: chab gser 'di dag kyang rje mnga' bdag khri srong lde'u btsan gyi phyag nas bskur ba lags pas /
NK032(khi)004:1961: rje'i zhal nas rgya gar gyi yul na chos nyid
NK032(khi)004:1962: kyi don skad cig mas rtogs nas tshe gcig gis
NK032(khi)004:1964: 'o skol de zhur btang ba yin pas /
NK032(khi)004:1965: chab gser 'di dag kyang rje'i zhal snga nas bskur ba yin pas /
NK032(khi)004:1966: slob dpon gyi phyag tu bsnams par zhu la /
NK032(khi)004:1967: chos nyid kyi don skad cig mas rtogs nas tshe
NK032(khi)004:1968: gcig gis 'tshang rgya ba gcig yod mchi bas de
NK032(khi)004:1969: 'o skol la thugs la gdags par zhu /
NK032(khi)004:1970: de thugs la ma btags na 'o skol yul du
NK032(khi)004:1971: phyin kyang rgyal pos bka' chad nas chab la gsol
NK032(khi)004:1972: du mchi bas bod du 'gro ba'i dbang mi bdog
NK032(khi)004:1973: zhus pas / slob dpon sh+r+ai sing has phyag g.yon pa na gser gyi pa tra tsho bsnams nas /
NK032(khi)004:1974: phyag g.yas pa bee ro tsa na'i spyi bor brkyang nas /
NK032(khi)004:1975: a ha ho'i zhes byin gyis brlabs pas /
NK032(khi)004:1979: 'i gnyis su med pa'i don dbyer mi phyed pa /
NK032(khi)004:1980: dbyer mi phyed pa'i dus na dbyer phyed bya ba'am
NK032(khi)004:1981: mi phyed ces bya ba'i blo'i mtha' 'am tshig gi
NK032(khi)004:1982: mtha' zab cing phra ba tsam yang mi gnas pa'i
NK032(khi)004:1983: chos nyid kyi rang sgra'i ngang du zhag bdun gyi
NK032(khi)004:1984: bar ting nge 'dzin thun gcig song ngo //
NK032(khi)004:1985: de las sad tsa na rjes kyi shes pa la
NK032(khi)004:1986: sems nyid dngos po gshis kyi gnas lugs rang byung
NK032(khi)004:1987: gi ye shes chen po de mun khung du sgron
NK032(khi)004:1988: me btegs pa bzhin du rang gsal du rgyud la
NK032(khi)004:1990: de'i dus na slob dpon kyang da rung de rang na ke re bzhugs nas 'dug pas /
NK032(khi)004:1991: sngar gyi rgyud la skyes pa'i don de brjed kyis dogs pa'am /
NK032(khi)004:1993: mi brjed mi yal bar brtan par bya ba'i phyir /
NK032(khi)004:1994: san d+ha ra zhes bstan pas /
NK032(khi)004:1995: de yang bod bu khyod rang rin po che man
NK032(khi)004:1996: shel dag pa 'di la ltos dang bya ba'i brdar
NK032(khi)004:1997: go nas / mdun na rin po che man shel
NK032(khi)004:1998: gcig 'dug nas de la bltas pas rin po che
NK032(khi)004:1999: man shel de sa thog tu bzhag na sa 'dra
NK032(khi)004:2000: go nas / / rdo thog tu bzhag na rdo 'dra /
NK032(khi)004:2001: rtsa thog tu bzhag na r+ts+wa 'dra /
NK032(khi)004:2002: shing thog tu bzhag na shing 'dra /
NK032(khi)004:2003: kha dog gang gi thog tu bzhag pa de bzhin
NK032(khi)004:2004: du rkyen gyis ci yang 'char gyi 'dug pa la
NK032(khi)004:2005: rkyen gang la yang ma brten pa'i dus na kha
NK032(khi)004:2006: dog gang gi ngo bor yang ma grub pa gsal
NK032(khi)004:2008: sngon po legs grub gcan 'phrang bas bkrongs pas bee tsa na yang bkrongs kyi dogs nas /
NK032(khi)004:2009: 'phrang srung ku m+aa ra bya ba de la slob
NK032(khi)004:2010: dpon gyi zhal nas grogs po gcig gyis shig gsungs
NK032(khi)004:2011: nas gser gyi pa tra byin nas grogs po byas
NK032(khi)004:2012: te / 'phrang tsho bsgral bar byas so //
NK032(khi)004:2013: de nas bod du byon par dgongs tsa na /
NK032(khi)004:2014: rgya gar gyi rgyal po dang mkhas pa rnams kyi
NK032(khi)004:2015: rmi lam log nas grong khyer ser skya'i gnas dpal
NK032(khi)004:2016: na len+d+ra'i sgo khar 'tshogs nas blo bsdur bas /
NK032(khi)004:2017: 'di bod kyi ban+desa nged rang gi chos bod du khyer nas 'gro ba'i rtags yin pas /
NK032(khi)004:2018: 'di sus bskur ba yin rtsad chod cig /
NK032(khi)004:2019: gang gis bskur ba la chad pa gcod dgos so byas pas /
NK032(khi)004:2020: pra sen gcig gis pra phab pas de na re /
NK032(khi)004:2021: ri chen po gsum gyi steng na lus po mig
NK032(khi)004:2022: gis khengs pa de'i steng na mtsho chags pa'i nang
NK032(khi)004:2024: mchu ring po gcig gis nang nas phar lta ru chos 'chad pa /
NK032(khi)004:2025: mi'i lus la sha ba'i mgo can gnyis kyis phyi nas chos nyan pa gnyis 'dug /
NK032(khi)004:2026: 'di lha srin gyi sprul pa zhig yin nam ngas ngo ma shes zer skad /
NK032(khi)004:2027: der khong rnams kyis rmi lam bsdur bas chos bod du 'chor bar shes nas /
NK032(khi)004:2029: 'phrang srung pa la 'dri rtsad bcad cing bsgug nas gsod dgos so byas pas /
NK032(khi)004:2030: 'phrang srung ba'i dpon po ku ma r+aa grogs po yin pas /
NK032(khi)004:2031: khong gis rmi lam bsdur ba thos pas bee ro
NK032(khi)004:2032: tsa na la bya btang nas bskul ma btab pa
NK032(khi)004:2033: 'di skad do // grogs po byang chub sems dpa' bdag la snyan gson dang //
NK032(khi)004:2034: ku ku r+aa dza phyi ma 'di skad zlos //
NK032(khi)004:2035: theg pa'i rgyal po man ngag bde chen 'di //
NK032(khi)004:2036: sa brgyad byang chub sems dpa'i sprul pa yi //
NK032(khi)004:2037: sgrib pa sbyong ba'i gnod sbyin mgo can gnyis //
NK032(khi)004:2038: 'o skol rgya gar yul du mchis pa la //
NK032(khi)004:2039: nyi zla am phrag bcug nas khyer ba rmis //
NK032(khi)004:2040: pan+di ta yis rkang mgyogs la 'ur thongs //
NK032(khi)004:2041: 'jam dpal dpal bzang rmi lam 'di skad zlos //
NK032(khi)004:2042: yang dag byang chub bde chen lhun rdzogs pa'i //
NK032(khi)004:2043: tshe 'dir 'bras bu thob pa'i man ngag chos //
NK032(khi)004:2044: spyan ras gzigs dbang sku sprul rgyal po yis //
NK032(khi)004:2045: sa la gnas pa'i ban+de mi gnyis la //
NK032(khi)004:2046: gser phye bskur nas chos len mchis pa las //
NK032(khi)004:2047: rdo rje sems dpa'i thugs rje'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK032(khi)004:2048: yang dag thugs rje'i nyi ma de shar nas //
NK032(khi)004:2049: kun la dgos pa'i yid bzhin nor bu de //
NK032(khi)004:2050: am phrag bcug nas bod du khyer ba rmis //
NK032(khi)004:2051: pan+di ta yi rkang mgyogs la 'ur thongs //
NK032(khi)004:2052: sh+r+ai sing has rmi lam 'di skad zlos //
NK032(khi)004:2053: dbang po rab mchog skal ldan don ched du //
NK032(khi)004:2054: rang bzhin ma bcos theg pa'i rgyal po 'di //
NK032(khi)004:2055: skal ldan phyi ma rnams kyi don ched du //
NK032(khi)004:2056: rdo rje gdan du lnga brgyar sbas pa de //
NK032(khi)004:2057: rigs gsum sprul pa khri srong lde'u btsan gyis //
NK032(khi)004:2058: tshe 'dir 'bras bu thob pa'i man ngag chos //
NK032(khi)004:2059: 'gro ba skal ldan smin grol dgongs nas ni //
NK032(khi)004:2060: bod kyi ban+de gnod sbyin mgo can gnyis //
NK032(khi)004:2061: gser phye bskur nas 'dir ni mchis pa la //
NK032(khi)004:2062: brtags par mi bzod sgyu ma'i gzugs phung la //
NK032(khi)004:2063: srog 'dzin snying gcig yod pa phyungs nas khyer ba rmis //
NK032(khi)004:2064: pan+di ta yi rkang mgyogs la 'ur thongs //
NK032(khi)004:2065: kun dga' mo ni rmi lam 'di skad zlos //
NK032(khi)004:2066: yang dag chos nyid ma nor bden pa'i lam //
NK032(khi)004:2067: rgya gar mkhas pa'i man ngag bde chen rnams //
NK032(khi)004:2068: byang chub sems kyi dkyil du sbas pa la //
NK032(khi)004:2069: skye ba 'di yi snga ma de nyid la //
NK032(khi)004:2070: rgya gar yul gyi bram ze dpal ldan bu //
NK032(khi)004:2071: a pa gang du dge slong tshe 'phos pas //
NK032(khi)004:2072: bod kyi spu rgyal btsan po'i lus blangs te //
NK032(khi)004:2073: bod kyi rgyal khams kha lo des bsgyur ro //
NK032(khi)004:2074: de nyid byang chub sems dpa'i sku sprul pas //
NK032(khi)004:2075: yang dag bde chen bod du dar ba'i phyir //
NK032(khi)004:2076: shes pa lus la rdzogs pa'i ban+de gnyis //
NK032(khi)004:2077: gser phye bskur nas 'di ni mchis pa las //
NK032(khi)004:2078: rdo rje gdan gyi byang chub shing drung de //
NK032(khi)004:2079: bod kyi 'tshubs nag 'jigs su rung ba yis //
NK032(khi)004:2080: rtsad nas bton te bod du khyer ba rmis //
NK032(khi)004:2081: pan+di ta yi rkang mgyogs la 'ur thongs //
NK032(khi)004:2082: de skad zer nas spyan sngar mchis pa lags //
NK032(khi)004:2083: dngos grub thob nas da gshegs da re ram //
NK032(khi)004:2084: de skad zer nas bee ro tsa na'i thugs kar snying gtugs nas ku m+aa ra bshums so //
NK032(khi)004:2085: de nas bee ro tsa nas lan btab pa /
NK032(khi)004:2086: mi ru skyes pas skye ba gzhan las 'phags //
NK032(khi)004:2087: smon lam dag pas rgya gar yul du mchis //
NK032(khi)004:2088: dngos grub thob pas rdzu 'phrul rkang mgyogs 'grub //
NK032(khi)004:2089: bla ma mchod pas cho rigs btsun par skyes //
NK032(khi)004:2090: dam tshig bsrungs pas 'di ru bsam dgu 'grub //
NK032(khi)004:2091: sgribs pa sbyangs pas mkhas pa'i bka' bgros lon //
NK032(khi)004:2092: khyod ni gzhung lugs bzang bas kun gyis brten par gyur //
NK032(khi)004:2093: dgos dgu lus la tshang bas bdag gi grogs su btsal //
NK032(khi)004:2094: lus 'di pha ma'i bskyed kyang srog 'di grogs pos 'don //
NK032(khi)004:2095: khyod rang grogs po byas pas yang dag byang chub rnyed //
NK032(khi)004:2096: bod kyi rgyal khams ma rigs mun sel ba'i //
NK032(khi)004:2097: 'gro ba ji ltar smin cing grol 'dod pa //
NK032(khi)004:2098: ku m+aa ra yi dge ba'i rtsa bar bsngo //
NK032(khi)004:2099: 'gro la phan phyir sangs rgyas 'grub gyur cig /
NK032(khi)004:2100: gsungs nas ku m+aa ra la gser phye phul gang
NK032(khi)004:2101: byin nas bya btang ba la dgyes par tshor bar
NK032(khi)004:2102: byas te / smon lam bzang po btab pas de kho na bzhin du grub pa yin skad do //
NK032(khi)004:2103: de nas bee ro tsa na bod du 'byon par dgongs pa la /
NK032(khi)004:2104: sngon po legs grub lam du bkrongs pa bzhin bar
NK032(khi)004:2105: chad 'byung gis dogs nas the tshom en gcig kyang
NK032(khi)004:2106: zos / slob dpon sh+r+ai sing ha drin che bas 'bral kyang ma phod tsa na /
NK032(khi)004:2107: slob dpon sh+r+ai sing has thugs kyis mkhyen nas phyag rgya mtho do ba gcig mdzad nas /
NK032(khi)004:2108: gu na a kar+sha ya zhes lan gsum gsungs pas /
NK032(khi)004:2110: gzhu mo dag la brten pa'i mda' //
NK032(khi)004:2111: skyes bu'i mtheb kyis rtsol phod na //
NK032(khi)004:2112: mdas kyang pha rol phyin par 'gyur //
NK032(khi)004:2114: chu bo dag la brten pa'i gru //
NK032(khi)004:2115: skya ba drag pos rtsol phod na //
NK032(khi)004:2116: grus kyang pha rol phyin par 'gyur //
NK032(khi)004:2118: gu na a kar+sha ya phyi ma de /
NK032(khi)004:2119: yon tan dag la brten pa'i mi //
NK032(khi)004:2120: sa phyogs bgrod kyang nyam mi nga //
NK032(khi)004:2122: bod kyis phyogs bgrod kyang nyam nga mi dgos /
NK032(khi)004:2123: khyod kyis mchog dang thun mong gi dngos grub gnyis ka thob pa yin pas /
NK032(khi)004:2124: ba yar 'o ma skam po be'u ser kho thag chod //
NK032(khi)004:2125: sbang ma them bu skam po chang ma kho thag chod //
NK032(khi)004:2126: slob dpon gdams ngag zad do slob bu kho thag chod //
NK032(khi)004:2127: 'gro ba'i dus la babs so da gshegs da re ran //
NK032(khi)004:2128: byas pas der the tshom ma zos te /
NK032(khi)004:2129: bar chad mi 'ong bar shes nas yul du chos
NK032(khi)004:2130: lon nas 'gro ba la rngam zhing brod drag pas
NK032(khi)004:2131: phyi phyag kyang 'tshal ba ma dran par gshegs pas
NK032(khi)004:2132: / lam du ke re rgyal po r+aa hu la bya ba dang mjal bas /
NK032(khi)004:2133: bod kyi ban+de skye ba med pa'i don bya ba ci lta bu zhig mchis pa yin /
NK032(khi)004:2134: bka' stsol dang zer ba la lan du btab pa /
NK032(khi)004:2135: bdag ni rnam par snang mdzad de //
NK032(khi)004:2136: dka' ba bcu drug dka' las bgyis //
NK032(khi)004:2137: ston pa'i thugs rje bdag la shar //
NK032(khi)004:2138: ston pa'i zhal skyin bdag gis bshad //
NK032(khi)004:2139: rgyal po bag tsam bdag la gson //
NK032(khi)004:2140: dmigs su med pa'i byang chub sems //
NK032(khi)004:2141: gzung dang 'dzin pa gnyis dang bral //
NK032(khi)004:2142: tha snyad tshig dang bral ba la //
NK032(khi)004:2143: de nyid gsal la mi dmigs pa //
NK032(khi)004:2144: skye ba med pa'i chos nyid yin //
NK032(khi)004:2145: dgongs pa'i don du de bzhag go //
NK032(khi)004:2146: skye ba phyis su mi len nges //
NK032(khi)004:2148: rgyal po de rab tu mnyes nas 'phags pa byams pa'i sku gser las byas pa gcig phul te /
NK032(khi)004:2149: sku gsum mchog gyur rnam par snang mdzad la //
NK032(khi)004:2150: rgyal po bdag gi sgrib pa sbyang ba'i phyir //
NK032(khi)004:2151: chos kyi sku la gzugs kyi sku gcig 'bul //
NK032(khi)004:2152: dbyings kyi thugs rje bdag la shar bar mdzod //
NK032(khi)004:2154: de nas bee ro tsa nas bal yul du nga
NK032(khi)004:2155: sha ka ra bya ba'i yul du sleb nas pan+di
NK032(khi)004:2156: ta pra sid+d+hi bya ba gcig rtogs tshad 'drir byung
NK032(khi)004:2157: ba ni / bod kyi ban chung rang sems ji ltar byas na rtogs //
NK032(khi)004:2158: theg pa gang la bslabs na 'bras bu thob //
NK032(khi)004:2159: mchod pa gang gis mchod na 'phags pa mnyes //
NK032(khi)004:2160: zhes dris pas lan btab pa /
NK032(khi)004:2161: sems la rang bzhin gdod nas med pa yin //
NK032(khi)004:2162: rgyu las ma byung sems nyid gnas lugs la //
NK032(khi)004:2163: gang zag mkhas kyang phyogs gcig mtshon du med //
NK032(khi)004:2164: rang bzhin 'od gsal dmigs med dag pa la //
NK032(khi)004:2165: rgyal ba rnams kyis mtshon du med par 'khums //
NK032(khi)004:2167: don dam chos nyid lta phug gcig pa la //
NK032(khi)004:2168: dbang po'i rim pas 'jug sgo so sor phye //
NK032(khi)004:2169: dam chos theg pa zhal nas gsungs pa'i bka' //
NK032(khi)004:2170: gang la rtogs kyang 'bras bu thob pa yin //
NK032(khi)004:2173: ye nas 'od gsal dbyings de sangs rgyas sku //
NK032(khi)004:2174: sems la chags med 'khor yul zang zing la //
NK032(khi)004:2175: ser sna ma zhugs kun la mnyam snyoms na //
NK032(khi)004:2176: de ni mchod pa'i nang na dam pa ste //
NK032(khi)004:2177: 'phags pa rnams kyang de yis mnyes par dgongs //
NK032(khi)004:2178: zhes gsungs pas pan+di ta mnyes so //
NK032(khi)004:2179: de nas lam du rgya gar gyi brtan mas kha ba phab pa la /
NK032(khi)004:2181: bde bar gshegs pa'i bka' 'di bden nges na //
NK032(khi)004:2182: ya rab blo dang ldan pa'i skal ldan la //
NK032(khi)004:2183: sems kyi nyi ma dri med gsal ba'i phyir //
NK032(khi)004:2184: bsam pa bzang po gser dang 'dra ba yis //
NK032(khi)004:2185: bod kyi yul nas rgya gar yul bar du //
NK032(khi)004:2186: dka' ba bcu drug bsdos pa'i man ngag btsal //
NK032(khi)004:2187: kha ba gcig gis bar du gcod 'dod pa //
NK032(khi)004:2188: bka' 'di bden na kha ba 'di ka chod //
NK032(khi)004:2190: brtan ma re ma lcam gyi lha mo dmar mo'i sku //
NK032(khi)004:2191: sprin gyi gseb nas bton nas phyag byas nas //
NK032(khi)004:2192: bran du khas blangs nas ni kha ba bcad //
NK032(khi)004:2193: de yang rgya gar gyi tsha ba thon nas byon
NK032(khi)004:2194: pas bsam yas su gro khar hril gyis brtol lo
NK032(khi)004:2195: // btsan po snga dro za 'og gi gur la bzhugs pa la /
NK032(khi)004:2196: slob dpon gyis rgyal po la mjal dgos pa'i phrin
NK032(khi)004:2197: skur bas mnga' bdag gi gshegs btsun nam sna len
NK032(khi)004:2198: du byas nas / mnga' bdag lags /
NK032(khi)004:2199: 'tshol du btang ba'i dam chos lon nas bdog pas /
NK032(khi)004:2200: rgya gar gyi ban+de phrag dog che zhing snyan phra la mi dga' ba dang /
NK032(khi)004:2201: bod glen pas phra ma snga btsan du byed pas /
NK032(khi)004:2202: ji skad zer yang mi gsan par zhu 'tshal /
NK032(khi)004:2204: chos lon pas mnga' bdag dgyes te thugs la btags
NK032(khi)004:2205: bka' nyan gsungs nas zhabs 'og gi 'bangs nas bton
NK032(khi)004:2206: slob dpon du zhus nas dbu'i mchod gnas su mdzad
NK032(khi)004:2208: slob dpon bee ro tsa nas rgya gar nas bod du chos lon pa'i lo rgyus thal lo //
NK032(khi)004:2209: de'i gong ma des slob dpon sh+r+ai sing ha'i lo rgyus thal lo //
NK032(khi)004:2210: de'i gong ma des slob dpon 'jam dpal bshes gnyen gyi lo rgyus thal lo //
NK032(khi)004:2211: de'i gong ma des slob dpon dga' rab rdo rje'i lo rgyus thal lo //
NK032(khi)004:2212: de'i gong ma des sems dag lha'i bu /
NK032(khi)004:2213: de'i gong ma rdo rje sems dpa' /
NK032(khi)004:2214: de'i gong ma dpal bde ba chen po /
NK032(khi)004:2215: dpal bde ba chen po chos kyi sku'i thugs dang gcig /
NK032(khi)004:2216: kun tu bzang po chos kyi sku'i gsung dang gnyis /
NK032(khi)004:2217: rdo rje sems dpa' chos kyi sku'i sku dang gsum /
NK032(khi)004:2218: chos kyi sku'i sku gsung thugs dbyer mi phyed pa'i ngo bo dpal rdo rje sems dpa' /
NK032(khi)004:2219: rdo rje sems dpa'i sku gsung thugs gsum rnam par
NK032(khi)004:2220: dag pa'i sprul pa sems dag lha'i bu dang bzhi
NK032(khi)004:2221: / de ni rgyal ba dgongs pa'i brgyud pa 'bras bu gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa'i rigs so //
NK032(khi)004:2222: theg pa chen po de'i rigs brgyud gang gis 'dzin
NK032(khi)004:2223: na rdo rje sems dpa'i yang sprul dga' rab rdo
NK032(khi)004:2224: rje dang gcig / 'jam dpal bshes gnyes dang gnyis /
NK032(khi)004:2226: bee ro tsa na dang bzhi'o //
NK032(khi)004:2227: de yan chad kyis gang thal na rigs ni gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa'i rigs /
NK032(khi)004:2229: brda bstan pa tsam gyi rang rgyud grol /
NK032(khi)004:2230: gcig nas gcig tu gong mas mar bshad pa bzhin
NK032(khi)004:2231: du gcig nas gcig tu brgyud pa yin pas na
NK032(khi)004:2232: hril gyis dril bas de yan chad du rig 'dzin
NK032(khi)004:2233: brdas grol ba'i brgyud pa'i skabs thal ba lags so
NK032(khi)004:2234: // slob dpon bee ro tsa na bod du gshegs
NK032(khi)004:2235: pa de'i rjes la 'phrang srung gi dpon po ku
NK032(khi)004:2236: m+aa ra d+ha tu bya ba des bee ro tsa
NK032(khi)004:2237: na bod du gshegs pa dang grong khyer ser skya'i
NK032(khi)004:2239: bod kyi ban+de des chos lon nas bod du song
NK032(khi)004:2240: ngo byas nas ram zla gshog pa'i tshul du bstan
NK032(khi)004:2241: nas / 'phrang srung ba zla bo la rkang mgyogs
NK032(khi)004:2242: byung tsa na da bod du brtol bar song 'gro
NK032(khi)004:2243: kha na med log gyis shig byas pas /
NK032(khi)004:2244: der rkang mgyogs kyis gcan 'phrang dang por brtol tsa na da mi sleb /
NK032(khi)004:2245: bod du brtol zin zer bas rkang mgyogs pa rnams theng gcig log pa lags skad /
NK032(khi)004:2246: de'i dus de'i tshe rgya gar gyi rgyal po dang /
NK032(khi)004:2247: ban+de mang po rmi ltas log nas bod du man ngag gi chos zab mo shor bar tshor nas /
NK032(khi)004:2248: bod spre'u dang brag srin gyi bu yin pas /
NK032(khi)004:2249: bod shig zan gyi yul du theg pa chen po'i chos shor bar 'phangs pas /
NK032(khi)004:2250: bod phra ma snga btsan che ba yin pas bod
NK032(khi)004:2251: du phra ma 'jug pa la a tsa ra mi
NK032(khi)004:2252: bdun btang nas / bee ro tsa na bya ba
NK032(khi)004:2253: des theg pa chen po'i chos skad cig ma'i don
NK032(khi)004:2254: rtogs nas tshe gcig gis sangs rgya ba ni ma
NK032(khi)004:2255: bdun btang nas / lon / ngan sngags dang dug
NK032(khi)004:2256: sbyor dang phra men ma'i ngan sngags mtheb rgya can
NK032(khi)004:2257: mang po gser gyis bslus nas song bas bod phung
NK032(khi)004:2258: du 'gro bas da lta tsam la spyugs shig sod
NK032(khi)004:2259: bdun btang nas / lon / cig / ces gyis la der ma bsdad par log la shog cig /
NK032(khi)004:2260: bsdad na bod bya ba thabs mkhas pas khyed rang tsho mgo bskor 'agro'o //
NK032(khi)004:2261: byas pas rkang mgyogs pa rnams kyis zhag bdun na bsam yas su shar gyis brtol nas byung ngo //
NK032(khi)004:2262: der rgya skad pa ra pe ra mang po zer
NK032(khi)004:2263: nas sgra shes pa kun la ji skad zer dris
NK032(khi)004:2264: dang byas pas / khong na re /
NK032(khi)004:2265: bee ro tsa na zer ba gcig gis rgya gar nas theg pa chen po'i chos ni ma lon /
NK032(khi)004:2266: ngan sngags dang dug sbyor dang khro chu mtheb rgya
NK032(khi)004:2267: can mang po bslus nas song bas de da lta
NK032(khi)004:2268: tsam la spyugs shig sod cig /
NK032(khi)004:2269: de ma spyugs ma bsad na bod phung ste 'od zer gyi 'dug bya bar byung ste /
NK032(khi)004:2270: de nas a tsa ra bdun po de cig char du rgya gar du log nas song ngo //
NK032(khi)004:2271: de nas li rtag po che'am li khra mi la
NK032(khi)004:2272: sogs pa rgya mi mi bdun nam bod 'bangs tsho
NK032(khi)004:2273: 'dus nas rgyal po la gros btab pa /
NK032(khi)004:2274: mnga' bdag las col chung ba med /
NK032(khi)004:2275: lha khang brtsigs zer nas bod 'bangs thams cad bkol /
NK032(khi)004:2276: rin po che thams cad bzhugs nas gyang gi logs la byugs /
NK032(khi)004:2277: lha yin no zer nas 'jim pa la kha mig dod pa mang po byas nas khyim phug brgyang /
NK032(khi)004:2278: 'phan yin zer nas dar zab thams cad gtub nas 'phan du byas /
NK032(khi)004:2279: chos zhur gtong ba yin zer nas gser mang po bskur nas /
NK032(khi)004:2280: chos mi slob par ngan sngags dang dug sbyor mang
NK032(khi)004:2281: po slob tu bcug nas rgyal po la dgra ni
NK032(khi)004:2282: mi 'ong / da bod phung du 'gro ba las ci byed /
NK032(khi)004:2283: da bee ro tsa na gsod dgos spyugs dgos zer bas /
NK032(khi)004:2284: rgyal pos de phra ma yin slob dpon mi spyugs byas pas /
NK032(khi)004:2285: blon 'khor rnams kyis da 'o na rgyal khrims 'jig go zer nas /
NK032(khi)004:2286: nan tan du yang dang yang du gtugs pas phra
NK032(khi)004:2287: ma snga btsan du song bas bshag rdeb sa mi
NK032(khi)004:2288: 'dug nas der rgyal pos slob dpon chu la bskyur
NK032(khi)004:2290: dus nam zhig na sprang po ldom bu pa gcig
NK032(khi)004:2291: bzung nas slob dpon bee ro tsa na'i na bza'
NK032(khi)004:2292: rnams de la bskon nas 'phral la dgos pa'i bza'
NK032(khi)004:2293: btung rnams kyang der bcug nas bsam yas ka chu
NK032(khi)004:2294: nas / kwa ye bod 'bangs rnams 'dir 'dus shig /
NK032(khi)004:2295: ngas bee ro tsa na chu la bskyur ba 'di yin no gsungs nas /
NK032(khi)004:2296: mi rnams kyis glo ru btol la khad tsa na
NK032(khi)004:2297: sprang po de zangs kyi nang du bcug nas zangs
NK032(khi)004:2298: kyi kha la lcags kyi gzer btab nas gtsang po
NK032(khi)004:2299: la bskyur ro // der slob dpon bee ro tsa
NK032(khi)004:2300: na'i thugs la kho nga'i dod por btang ba yin
NK032(khi)004:2301: snyam nas thugs rje'i lcags kyus gzung bas 'ol kha
NK032(khi)004:2302: mkhar ltag gi 'khor mar chags so //
NK032(khi)004:2303: der 'khor gyi bdag po gcig gis rnyed nas lcags
NK032(khi)004:2304: kyus bzung nas nang na ci 'dug bltas pas btsun
NK032(khi)004:2305: pa gcig byung nas 'di glud du btang ba gcig
NK032(khi)004:2306: 'dug pa zer nas de rang mi byas nas phog
NK032(khi)004:2307: pas / de da lta 'ol ka rgyug thang gi lhu mi bya ba de tsho yin skad do //
NK032(khi)004:2308: de nas slob dpon nyin mo gdugs khang byed gsungs nas /
NK032(khi)004:2309: ka ba sbom po gcig la nang brus nas nyin
NK032(khi)004:2310: mo ka ba'i nang du bzhugs nas tshon gyi gseb
NK032(khi)004:2312: nub mo glo 'bur gyi 'og la sgra don bsdebs nas bka' bsgyur ba ni /
NK032(khi)004:2313: nyin mo ni rgyu 'bras kyi chos lkog par bsgyur /
NK032(khi)004:2314: nub mo ni man ngag gi chos bsgyur ro //
NK032(khi)004:2315: de yang rgyu 'bras kyi chos la shes rab kyi
NK032(khi)004:2316: pha rol tu phyin pa bam po lngas kha ma
NK032(khi)004:2318: mdo lang kar gshegs pa bam po lnga bod du bsgyur ro //
NK032(khi)004:2319: gzhan rgya gar du lus so //
NK032(khi)004:2320: dkon mchog brtsegs pa bam po sum cu rtsa lnga kha ma longs pa bod du bsgyur ro //
NK032(khi)004:2321: sangs rgyas phal po che la bam po brgya dang brgyad ma bsgyur ba lags skad do //
NK032(khi)004:2322: lung gi rgyud la gshin rje'i gnas rgyud /
NK032(khi)004:2324: dbang bskur rgyal po'i rgyud tsho bsgyur ro //
NK032(khi)004:2325: man ngag gi rgyud la nam mkha' che la sogs pa snga 'gyur gyi rgyud lnga /
NK032(khi)004:2326: rmad du byung ba dang drug /
NK032(khi)004:2329: rna brgyud tan+t+ra sde bcu drug bsgyur ro //
NK032(khi)004:2330: de rnams bka' babs rgyal po la bab pa'i chos tsho lags so //
NK032(khi)004:2331: dus tshod de tsam na rgyal po nang nub kyi
NK032(khi)004:2332: ring la gar song cha med par re rer gshegs
NK032(khi)004:2333: kyin byung bas / der jo mo tshe spong bza'
NK032(khi)004:2334: dmar rgyan mig ser che bas rgyal po bud med
NK032(khi)004:2335: gzhan zhig gi gam du song ba yin nam sems
NK032(khi)004:2336: kyin byung bas / nas / mos rgyal po gar gshegs bltas pas /
NK032(khi)004:2337: rgyal po glo 'bur gyi nang na slob dpon la
NK032(khi)004:2338: tsha ba drangs nas dar gyis thod phud nas khrus
NK032(khi)004:2339: bshal byed kyin yod pa la /
NK032(khi)004:2340: jo mos sgo gseb nas mar la bltas pas mthong
NK032(khi)004:2341: nas rgyal po dang gnyis spyan zur dkrug gis 'dres
NK032(khi)004:2342: te / rgyal po'i thugs la mos bod 'bangs la
NK032(khi)004:2343: bshad 'gro nyen yod sems nas rgyal pos jo mo'i
NK032(khi)004:2344: phyi na phar la phyin pas ma zin te /
NK032(khi)004:2345: dus de tsa na rgyal po'i bka' khrims la zangs dung 'bud na dmag la shog bya ba yin /
NK032(khi)004:2346: dung 'bud na tsha ba la shog bya ba yin /
NK032(khi)004:2347: gan+d+ai brdung na chos la byon bya ba yin /
NK032(khi)004:2348: rnga bo brdung na 'dun ma la shog bya ba yin pas mos rnga bo che brdungs pas /
NK032(khi)004:2352: mnga' bdag las col chung ba mi 'dug /
NK032(khi)004:2353: chu la bskyur ba de sprang po yin par 'dug ste /
NK032(khi)004:2354: slob dpon ngan thabs mkhan de da rung glo 'bur
NK032(khi)004:2355: na sbas nas 'dug pas bod phung zin pa las
NK032(khi)004:2356: mi tshor ba sa da lta tsam la rgyal por
NK032(khi)004:2357: gros thob la sod cig byas pas /
NK032(khi)004:2358: der rgya mi mi bdun la sogs pa bod 'bangs kun na re /
NK032(khi)004:2360: mnga' bdag gi drung du byung nas mnga' bdag rgyal po nyid las col chung ba med /
NK032(khi)004:2361: lha khang byed zer nas gser dngul la sogs pa'i
NK032(khi)004:2362: rin po che thams cad bzhus nas gyang logs la
NK032(khi)004:2363: byugs / lha yin no zer nas lder tsho mang po khyim phugs su bcug /
NK032(khi)004:2364: chos len du gtor zer nas ngan sngags dug sdong dang /
NK032(khi)004:2365: khro chus theb rgya can gser gyis bslus /
NK032(khi)004:2366: ngan sngags mkhan po spyugs byas nas sprang po chu la bor //
NK032(khi)004:2367: chos dang ci'i chos da rung ngan sngags mkhan po
NK032(khi)004:2368: glo 'bur na sbas nas 'dug zer bas de gsod
NK032(khi)004:2370: rgyal pos da khyed rnams nan tan gyis de skad zer na /
NK032(khi)004:2371: nga'i slob dpon yin pas gsod pa mi yong /
NK032(khi)004:2373: khong na re snga ma yang rgyal pos ma spyugs par sbas nas 'dug zer bas /
NK032(khi)004:2374: da res gsod pa mi 'ong na nged rang dang 'grogs nas spyugs dgos zer ba la /
NK032(khi)004:2375: de nas rgyal pos slob dpon la ngas thabs ji
NK032(khi)004:2376: ltar byas kyang slob dpon mchod gnas su bsten dbang
NK032(khi)004:2378: da 'o brgyal te slob dpon gshegs par zhu dgos 'dug byas nas zhu ba phul bas /
NK032(khi)004:2379: chibs bzang po gcig la bskyon nas dngul bya'o gang
NK032(khi)004:2380: rta gong du gshegs skye mas kyi dod por byas
NK032(khi)004:2381: / tsha ba'i rong du 'gro ba la tshad khung
NK032(khi)004:2382: che bas bsil sman du ga bur bre gang la
NK032(khi)004:2383: sogs pa'i sman mang po yang bskur nas /
NK032(khi)004:2384: rgyal blon btsun mo dang bcas pa rnams kyis slob dpon skyel du phyin pas /
NK032(khi)004:2385: dbu ru'i skyi gtsang la brgal ba'i dus su slob
NK032(khi)004:2386: dpon gru nang du bzhugs nas yod tsa na 'di
NK032(khi)004:2388: ma myong dgu myong shi ba ma myong tsam gyi bee ro tsa na nga //
NK032(khi)004:2389: yang dag bcu gcig don dang ye nas ldan //
NK032(khi)004:2390: rgya gar yul nas chos blangs nas //
NK032(khi)004:2391: sgra don bsdebs nas bka' bsgyur nas //
NK032(khi)004:2392: mnga' bdag rgyal po nyid la gtad //
NK032(khi)004:2393: rgyal po mnga' dbang chung bas dam chos zhu dbang med //
NK032(khi)004:2394: btsun mo phra ma mkhas pas mchod gnas bsten dbang med //
NK032(khi)004:2395: blon po gdug pa che bas slob dpon spyugs par byed //
NK032(khi)004:2396: ma myong dgu myong shi ba ma myong tsam gyi bee ro tsa na nga //
NK032(khi)004:2397: dka' ba bcu drug bsdos nas dam chos btsal nas su //
NK032(khi)004:2398: bod du dam chos nyi ma lan gcig shar ba de //
NK032(khi)004:2399: rgyal blon btsun mor bcas pas tsha ba'i rong du spyugs //
NK032(khi)004:2400: bod 'bangs lan gcig 'gyod pa dus shig mchi //
NK032(khi)004:2402: blon 'khor jo mo bcas pa rnams kyang the tshom zos te /
NK032(khi)004:2404: rgyal khrims nyams par 'dug kyang dbang med byas nas gru'i nyag thag la 'then pas /
NK032(khi)004:2405: slob dpon gyis sked gseb nas o pa bton nas /
NK032(khi)004:2406: sems kyi nyag thag de gong nas bcad /
NK032(khi)004:2407: gru'i nyag thag de tshur la rang thong gsungs nas gru'i nyag thag phar bcad nas gshegs so //
NK032(khi)004:2408: der rgyal po dang blon 'khor nyi shu rtsa lnga
NK032(khi)004:2409: tsam gyis byang dkar la'i la thog bar du bskyal
NK032(khi)004:2410: nas da dung yar la gshegs par zhu byas pas
NK032(khi)004:2411: ma gnang ngo // da dung rgyal pos byed ngo ma shes nas /
NK032(khi)004:2412: da nga'i chos kyi byed lugs 'di ji ltar du bgyi /
NK032(khi)004:2413: zhes slob dpon la 'phral chos su zhus pas slob dpon gyi zhal nas /
NK032(khi)004:2414: yar sangs rgyas la re mi dgos par rtogs kyang spyi bor bla ma sgoms shig /
NK032(khi)004:2415: mar 'khor ba la 'khyams rgyu med par rtogs kyang rgyu 'bras rnam smin la 'dzems shig /
NK032(khi)004:2416: chos nyid bsam du med pa'i don la longs spyod kyang /
NK032(khi)004:2417: 'dus byas kyi dge ba'i rtsa ba ma chag par mdzod cig /
NK032(khi)004:2419: de nas tsha ba'i yul mthong ba dang bod mthong
NK032(khi)004:2420: ba'i mtshams su byon nas yar la bod kyi yul
NK032(khi)004:2422: ri thams cad bya rgod spungs pa'am shel gyi mchod rten bzhin du 'dug /
NK032(khi)004:2423: lung pa thams cad kha ba babs pa'am nam langs pa bzhin du 'dug /
NK032(khi)004:2424: mar la tsha ba'i rong du bltas pas chu dong rnyogs pa'am sol dong kha phye ba'am /
NK032(khi)004:2425: char mun 'thibs pa bzhin du nag subs se 'dug nas /
NK032(khi)004:2426: thugs ma dgyes nas 'di skad du gsungs so //
NK032(khi)004:2427: ri mtho sa gtsang gser dag bod kyii ri //
NK032(khi)004:2428: mi rje lhas mdzad dpag bsam ljon shing 'dra //
NK032(khi)004:2429: 'dod pa phun sum tshogs pa yod bzhin du //
NK032(khi)004:2430: rin chen mtsho gling gser gyi ngang khyu nas //
NK032(khi)004:2431: ngang mo gcig ni yar ba su yis bshugs //
NK032(khi)004:2432: glo ba g.yar la bcags pas snying ma dga' //
NK032(khi)004:2433: gsungs nas de nas rgyal pos slob dpon la dar dkar gyi yol ba bzhugs gdan du bting /
NK032(khi)004:2434: de'i steng du slob dpon bzhugs su gsol nas mgur 'di gsungs so //
NK032(khi)004:2435: dus gsum pha ma dkon mchog yi dam lha //
NK032(khi)004:2436: dngos grub ster ba'i rdo rje slob dpon rnams //
NK032(khi)004:2437: brtse bas yud tsam 'bral yang mi phod na //
NK032(khi)004:2438: rje 'bangs 'grogs la gshegs sam ji ltar bgyi //
NK032(khi)004:2441: blon po rnams kyis rgyal po bzung nas /
NK032(khi)004:2442: slob dpon gyis rgyal po bag bsro ba'i mgur 'di gsungs so //
NK032(khi)004:2443: rje blon rnams tsho bdag la snyan gson dang //
NK032(khi)004:2444: yul la nges pa med pas spyugs kyang nyam mi nga //
NK032(khi)004:2445: sems la skye shi med pas bsad kyang bdag mi 'jigs //
NK032(khi)004:2446: yon tan sgyu mar shes pas skyon la dngos gzhi med //
NK032(khi)004:2447: gnyen la dang mi chags pas dgra la zhe mi sdang //
NK032(khi)004:2449: rgyal pos da gdod mjal bar lkog tu zhu ba phul bas /
NK032(khi)004:2450: lan gcig 'ong bar zhal gyis bzhes nas tsha ba'i
NK032(khi)004:2451: yul na mar la byil gyis 'tsher med du bzhud
NK032(khi)004:2452: nas song ngo // rgyal blon 'khor bcas rnams bod du log go //
NK032(khi)004:2453: de nas slob dpon tsha ba rong pa'i ri'i nags khrod na bzhugs yod tsa na /
NK032(khi)004:2454: bod kyi bya phug ron dang /
NK032(khi)004:2456: pho rog la sogs pa slob dpon gyi phyi la 'brangs nas /
NK032(khi)004:2457: rgyal mo tsha ba rong pa'i grong khrod na mar la skad 'don gyin song bas /
NK032(khi)004:2458: rgyal mo dpal bzher 'phan bu la sogs pa na re /
NK032(khi)004:2459: bod kyi bya byung ba 'di nged kyi yul 'phrog
NK032(khi)004:2460: pa'i so rtog pa'i rtog chen po yod pa'i rtags
NK032(khi)004:2461: yin pas / 'di ma legs pas ri thams cad
NK032(khi)004:2462: bshus nas ga na 'dug pa btsal nas rnyed na
NK032(khi)004:2464: che med chung med thams cad lag sbrel nas btsal bas slob dpon bee ro tsa na rnyed de /
NK032(khi)004:2465: slob dpon sngags btsun gyi cha lugs su yod pas /
NK032(khi)004:2466: khong dang skad rigs mi gcig pas btsun pa la 'bug thu lum pa zer te /
NK032(khi)004:2467: 'dir bod kyi 'bug thu lum pa gcig 'dug pas
NK032(khi)004:2468: nged kyi yul 'phrog pa'i so rtog pa'i rtog chen
NK032(khi)004:2469: pa yin pas mig 'bru nas ma bsad na da
NK032(khi)004:2470: dung du 'ong nyen yod zer nas la las phul
NK032(khi)004:2471: / la las rtsog grung byas pas /
NK032(khi)004:2472: slob dpon gyis nga chos byed pa yin /
NK032(khi)004:2473: de ltar ma byed mi rung ba 'ong ngo byas pas /
NK032(khi)004:2474: khyod la chos 'dug gam mi 'dug blta yi zer nas /
NK032(khi)004:2475: rgyal mo dpal bzher 'phan bu'am rgyal mo gru bya
NK032(khi)004:2476: bas sna drangs nas nan tan du don du sdug
NK032(khi)004:2477: pa byas te / sbal dong gi nang du zhag
NK032(khi)004:2478: gsum du bcug nas rgyal mo grus zhag gsum gyi
NK032(khi)004:2479: pa byas te / nangs par / dong khar bltar phyin pas /
NK032(khi)004:2480: slob dpon bee ro tsa nas dong nang nas 'di skad smras so //
NK032(khi)004:2481: yul phyogs 'di'i rgyal blon che btsun dra ma rnams 'jig khung dmyal dong khar 'dir 'byon par zhu /
NK032(khi)004:2482: bod kyi ban+de'i bka' mchid gcig bdog na byas pas /
NK032(khi)004:2483: rgyal mo'i mi dra ma rnams kyis dong khar phyin pas dong nang nas bka' stsal ba /
NK032(khi)004:2484: yul phyogs 'di yi rgyal blon dra ma rnams //
NK032(khi)004:2485: bco lnga lon nas lnga bcu rtsa bdun du //
NK032(khi)004:2486: bod kyi rgyal khams dkar por yongs bsgyur te //
NK032(khi)004:2487: theg pa'i nang mchog 'bras bu sangs rgyas chos //
NK032(khi)004:2488: rgya gar mkhas pa nyi shu rtsa lnga yis //
NK032(khi)004:2489: bstan pa'i man ngag bod du mchis pa las //
NK032(khi)004:2490: rgyal khams phung la sbyor ba'i blon po dang //
NK032(khi)004:2491: dam tshig nyams la smyo ba'i dmar rgyan dang //
NK032(khi)004:2492: bod khams sil bur 'gro rtags btsad po bcos sla bas //
NK032(khi)004:2493: bod kyi mun sel nyi ma mkhas pa bdag spyugs te //
NK032(khi)004:2494: tshe 'dir 'bras bu thob pa'i man ngag dang //
NK032(khi)004:2495: 'gal ba cham la phab pa'i drag sngags dang //
NK032(khi)004:2496: rin chen phung po kun gyi bstan bcos rnams //
NK032(khi)004:2497: bod kyi ban+de'i lus la mchis lags kyis //
NK032(khi)004:2498: 'jigs dong sbal pa'i dong las dbyung du gsol //
NK032(khi)004:2499: rgyal mo rin chen gru zhes bya bas bka' lan btab pa /
NK032(khi)004:2500: bod kyi rgyal po spu rgyal btsad po 'di //
NK032(khi)004:2501: tshan du chung la bya ba mang ba ste //
NK032(khi)004:2502: jo mo len na go kho'i khol mo len //
NK032(khi)004:2503: mkhas blon byed na nyon mongs che dgus byed //
NK032(khi)004:2504: zas su za na sha chen sna dgu za //
NK032(khi)004:2505: gos su gon na mtha' yi mon gos gon //
NK032(khi)004:2506: nor du bsrel na rdo la nor du byed //
NK032(khi)004:2507: las su byed na chom rkun dmag dpon byed //
NK032(khi)004:2508: lha ru bsten na gnod byed pho mo bsten //
NK032(khi)004:2509: srin po gdong dmar rgyal po'i 'dod pa la //
NK032(khi)004:2510: yid la ches rgyu ma mchis b+ha shi khyod //
NK032(khi)004:2511: blon po che btsun rnams kyis bka' bgros la //
NK032(khi)004:2512: sbal pa'i dong nas shig gi dong du bskyur //
NK032(khi)004:2513: dgu bdun bar la dmag dpung ma byung na //
NK032(khi)004:2514: khyed kyi bka' mchid gtsor bgyi spyi bor 'khur //
NK032(khi)004:2515: zer nas sbal pa'i dong nas shig gi dong du bskyur ro //
NK032(khi)004:2516: de nas zhag bdun lon tsa na bltas pas shig rnams kha phyir log ste /
NK032(khi)004:2517: slob dpon zar ma btub par slob dpon zil pa phrum me mdangs yal le bzhugs 'dug go //
NK032(khi)004:2518: de nas slob dpon bee ro tsa nas sbal pa
NK032(khi)004:2519: dang shig la dong nang nas bshags pa byas pa
NK032(khi)004:2520: / bdag nyid bee ro tsa na mchis pa 'di //
NK032(khi)004:2521: tshe 'di dag gi snga ma'i gong rol du //
NK032(khi)004:2522: dge slong sdom pa nyams pa yis //
NK032(khi)004:2523: yul phyogs 'di yi ne'u ler skyes //
NK032(khi)004:2524: sbrul dang sbal pa mang po bsad //
NK032(khi)004:2525: rnam par smin pa da res byung //
NK032(khi)004:2526: lan chags phra mo ma 'khor bar //
NK032(khi)004:2527: da res 'di ru smin gyur cig /
NK032(khi)004:2528: skye ba 'di yi gong rol du //
NK032(khi)004:2529: rgyal mo tsha ba rong 'di ru //
NK032(khi)004:2530: yul phyogs 'di yi rgyal po'i bu //
NK032(khi)004:2531: dge slong pur+na bya bar skyes //
NK032(khi)004:2532: stod shag gong ba shig za bas //
NK032(khi)004:2533: rang gi 'thu bar ma nus nas //
NK032(khi)004:2535: de yi rnam smin 'di ru byung //
NK032(khi)004:2536: lan chags phra mo ma 'khor bar //
NK032(khi)004:2537: tshe 'di nyid la smin gyur cig /
NK032(khi)004:2538: slob dpon sh+r+ai sing ha la //
NK032(khi)004:2539: bod du rings pas 'gro khar phyi phyag brjed //
NK032(khi)004:2540: rnam smin tsha ba'i rong du spyugs //
NK032(khi)004:2541: skye ba snga ma'i bag chags kyis //
NK032(khi)004:2542: da lta tsha ba'i rong du lhung //
NK032(khi)004:2543: nga yi rnam smin da res zad //
NK032(khi)004:2544: ces gsungs pas rgyal mo'i mi rnams kyis slob dpon la ngan byas pas 'gyod /
NK032(khi)004:2545: rgyal mo gru bya ba la sogs pa nged rang
NK032(khi)004:2546: gi rgyal po'i sras dge slong pur+na bya ba de
NK032(khi)004:2547: 'dir tshe 'phos pa yin 'dug pa zer nas dga'
NK032(khi)004:2548: / byang chub sems dpa' khyed lta bu la nongs
NK032(khi)004:2549: pa gnyis la sogs pa byas pa bzod par gsol
NK032(khi)004:2550: lo zer nas lha phyag gyang 'gyel ba tsam byed
NK032(khi)004:2551: kyin bshags pa byas pa ni /
NK032(khi)004:2552: bod la mi med rgyal po 'dod pa can //
NK032(khi)004:2553: skye ba snga phyi mkhyen pa'i byang chub sems dpa' khyed //
NK032(khi)004:2554: 'gro ba'i don du 'dzam gling kun tu byon //
NK032(khi)004:2555: khyad par du yang srin po gdong dmar gyi //
NK032(khi)004:2556: bod kyi don mdzad blon po nag po rnams //
NK032(khi)004:2557: 'dul ba'i dus la ma bab 'dir byon te //
NK032(khi)004:2558: byang chub sems dpa' 'gro don mdzad pa la //
NK032(khi)004:2559: spyod ngan gnyis byas byang chub gegs gyur pa //
NK032(khi)004:2560: 'gro ba'i don du ci yang bzod thub pas //
NK032(khi)004:2561: byang chub sems dpa' khyod la bzod par gsol //
NK032(khi)004:2563: de nas rgyal mo grus sna drangs te /
NK032(khi)004:2564: slob dpon gyi zhabs spyi bor blangs /
NK032(khi)004:2565: gab tshe'i gdan la slob dpon bzhugs su gsol nas /
NK032(khi)004:2566: gser dang dngul gyi dong tse dang pa tra'i me tog lag tu thogs nas /
NK032(khi)004:2567: rigs drug 'gro ba'i don mdzad byang chub sems dpa'i sku //
NK032(khi)004:2568: sde snod gsum mnga' bde chen don gyi gsung //
NK032(khi)004:2569: yid bzhin nor ltar dgos dgu 'byung ba'i thugs //
NK032(khi)004:2570: dus gsum rgyal ba'i sku gsum lhun grub pa'i //
NK032(khi)004:2571: gnyis med nyams myong 'gro ba'i mgon po la //
NK032(khi)004:2572: gser dang dngul gyi dong tse'i me tog 'bul //
NK032(khi)004:2573: thugs rjes 'khor ba'i rgya mtsho sgrol ba'i phyir //
NK032(khi)004:2574: ye shes thugs kyi zhags pas gzung du gsol //
NK032(khi)004:2575: me tog gtor nas chos gnang bar zhu ba phul lo //
NK032(khi)004:2576: de nas slob dpon bee ro tsa nas tsha ba rong pa la chos bstan dgos sems nas /
NK032(khi)004:2577: sngon la slob dpon sh+r+ai sing ha la phyi phyag brjed pa'i bshags pa byas pa ni /
NK032(khi)004:2578: gter chen rnyed pa'i rin chen dbang phyug bdag /
NK032(khi)004:2579: rtogs pa ma smin rin chen 'dam du byings //
NK032(khi)004:2580: rgyal po bcos sla 'jag ma rlung khyer 'dra //
NK032(khi)004:2581: gser sbrul dug can blon po nyon re mongs //
NK032(khi)004:2582: rdo rje'i zhabs la gnong bas mthol lo bshags //
NK032(khi)004:2584: de nas tsha ba rong pas chos kyi sgra shes sam mi shes blta ba la /
NK032(khi)004:2585: rdo rje sems dpa' sems dpa' che //
NK032(khi)004:2587: ldos se ldos se rno sbom khri bya ba las ma byung ste /
NK032(khi)004:2588: der mi 'ong bar 'dug sems tsa na /
NK032(khi)004:2589: byis pa rid po thal skya ba gcig byung nas /
NK032(khi)004:2590: rdo rje sems dpa' sems dpa' che //
NK032(khi)004:2593: bu de ci 'dra ba gcig yin zhes dris pas /
NK032(khi)004:2594: khong na re bu 'di'i ma snga gong du shi /
NK032(khi)004:2595: pha yod kyang dwa'u zhad du 'dug pa zer skad /
NK032(khi)004:2598: 'dis sgra don shes 'ong bar 'dug pas 'di la chos bslab gsungs pas /
NK032(khi)004:2599: der yod kha 'cham par bod kyi stong sbos la
NK032(khi)004:2600: byin cig nged rang gso res byas pas chog go
NK032(khi)004:2601: zer nas slob dpon gyi slob mar byin no //
NK032(khi)004:2602: de yang sgra don shes pa de skye ba snga
NK032(khi)004:2603: ma'i gtsang sngon po legs grub tshe 'phos pa yin
NK032(khi)004:2604: skad / de la sgra bsgyur rigs mi gcig pa bcu gsum bslab /
NK032(khi)004:2605: snga 'gyur rnam pa lnga la sogs pa man ngag dang mdo mang bar bslab skad do //
NK032(khi)004:2606: sems phyogs kyi chos mtha' dag du ma mkhyen no //
NK032(khi)004:2607: de yang rus rgyal mo'i nang tshan g.yu sgra /
NK032(khi)004:2608: ming snying po bya ba yin pas /
NK032(khi)004:2609: rgyal mo g.yu sgra snying po bya bar thogs so //
NK032(khi)004:2610: dus de tsa na mdo dkon mchog brtsegs pa'i 'bum bsgyur /
NK032(khi)004:2611: mtshan mo byang chub sems sgom la sogs pa'i man ngag bshad /
NK032(khi)004:2612: nam gyi gung la gsang sngags bsgyur ba'o //
NK032(khi)004:2613: de thams cad rgyal mo gru dang g.yu sgra snying pos legs par mkhyen pa lags skad /
NK032(khi)004:2614: der dus nam zhig na bod du bskor nas log
NK032(khi)004:2615: pa'i r+ts+wa mi shing mi'i tshong pa mang po byung
NK032(khi)004:2616: nas slob dpon bee ro tsa nas tshong pa rnams
NK032(khi)004:2617: la bod du bskor ba yin nam byas pas /
NK032(khi)004:2618: bod du bskor ba yin zer bar /
NK032(khi)004:2619: 'o na rgyal po khri srong lde'u btsan sku khams bde bar 'dug gam /
NK032(khi)004:2621: rgyal khrims ma zhig par 'dug gam byas pas /
NK032(khi)004:2622: rgyal po sku khams shin tu bde bar 'dug /
NK032(khi)004:2623: mchod gnas su pan+di ta bi ma la mi tra
NK032(khi)004:2624: bya ba bzhugs nas bsam yas sgo mo'i thang la
NK032(khi)004:2626: rgyal khrims ma zhig par shin tu bzang bar 'dug zer ro //
