NK032(khi)004:2627: de yang pan+di ta bi ma la mi tra bya
NK032(khi)004:2628: ba de rgya gar gyi chos skyong ba'i rgyal po
NK032(khi)004:2629: la rgyal po khri srong lde'u btsan gyis gser phye
NK032(khi)004:2630: mang po skyes su bskur bas /
NK032(khi)004:2631: bod kyi rgyal po chos 'dod pa yin zer nas /
NK032(khi)004:2632: rgya gar gyi rgyal pos pan+di ta lnga brgya'i gseb nas mkhas pa /
NK032(khi)004:2633: theg pa chen po'i chos bye ma'i la tsam zhig pa /
NK032(khi)004:2634: pan+di ta bi ma la mi tra bya ba de
NK032(khi)004:2635: bod kyi rgyal po'i mchod gnas su bardzangasa pa lags
NK032(khi)004:2636: skad / der slob dpon bee ro tsa nas thugs
NK032(khi)004:2637: la khong theg pa chen po'i chos 'chad nges med
NK032(khi)004:2638: pas bod du la yog gcig 'dor du btang dgos
NK032(khi)004:2639: skad / sems nas / rgyal mo g.yu sgra snying po la khyod bod du song la /
NK032(khi)004:2640: nga'i 'di ni sngags yin 'dug gam mi 'dug ston
NK032(khi)004:2641: pa'i ched du bod du khyod kyis bka' sgrogs shig
NK032(khi)004:2642: gsungs nas / der g.yu sgra snying pos ban+de pa la gcig tu byas te /
NK032(khi)004:2643: ral bu skya bo phu dung can gcig la ras ma se ru'i lhan pa btab pa gcig gsol /
NK032(khi)004:2644: zhwa spyi rengs gcig gi nang du snga 'gyur rnam pa lnga shog dril du byas nas bcug /
NK032(khi)004:2645: lag tu sba dkar gyi mkhar ba gcig thogs nas
NK032(khi)004:2646: phyin pas bsam yas su dus tshod la brtol nas
NK032(khi)004:2647: / bi ma la mi tra bya ba gtsug lag
NK032(khi)004:2648: khang gi nang na pra kar na sde brgyad bya
NK032(khi)004:2650: sgra brtags pas theg pa chung du'i chos 'chad kyin 'dug nas /
NK032(khi)004:2651: g.yu sgras mjal bar zhu bya ba'i phyag phrin bardzangasa pa la /
NK032(khi)004:2652: chos kyi thun ma thon pa'i skabs la ma bab pas bag tsam zhig bzhugs shig /
NK032(khi)004:2653: de nas mjal lo byas pas g.yu sgra snying pos
NK032(khi)004:2654: bzhugs su ma btub par nang du 'tshangs kyis byon
NK032(khi)004:2655: nas phyag mi 'tshal bar 'khar ba la tshugs su
NK032(khi)004:2656: byas te / bi ma la mi tra la spyan
NK032(khi)004:2657: gzigs nas ka ka pa ri ka ka pa ri
NK032(khi)004:2658: byas te / zhes gsungs pas / bi ma la
NK032(khi)004:2659: mi tra dbu smad nas brda thim brda thim zhes
NK032(khi)004:2661: der g.yu sgra snying pos btsad po la spyan cer gyis gzigs nas /
NK032(khi)004:2662: bod kyi mnga' bdag rgyal po'i bka' 'khor rnams //
NK032(khi)004:2663: skye med lhun rdzogs man ngag brgya'i sdong po //
NK032(khi)004:2664: rgya gar mkhas pa nyi shu rtsa lnga yi //
NK032(khi)004:2665: man ngag bde chen btsal du med pa'i chos //
NK032(khi)004:2666: tshig dang don gyi 'bras bu 'tshang rgya ba'i //
NK032(khi)004:2667: man ngag snying po tsha ba'i yul du spyugs //
NK032(khi)004:2668: ka ka pa ri zer nas ma mgu ste spyan
NK032(khi)004:2669: log pa gcig byas te phyi rol du bzhud nas
NK032(khi)004:2670: song ngo // rgyal po rje blon gyi slob dpon
NK032(khi)004:2671: bi ma la mi tra la sgra de 'dra ba
NK032(khi)004:2672: ji skad zer ba yin nam zhes dris pas /
NK032(khi)004:2673: bi ma la mi tra'i zhal nas /
NK032(khi)004:2674: wa dang spre'u'i skad kyis seng ge'i sgrar mi 'gyur //
NK032(khi)004:2675: pho rog rdo rje'i 'gros kyis sa mi chod //
NK032(khi)004:2676: nyan thos byis pa'i chos kyis sangs mi rgya //
NK032(khi)004:2677: theg pa chen po'i chos mi 'chad par zer ba yin gsungs /
NK032(khi)004:2678: ngas brda thim brda thim byas pa de kha rog sdod /
NK032(khi)004:2679: dus la ma bab dus la ma bab byas pa yin gsungs /
NK032(khi)004:2680: gnyags dz+ny+aa na kun m+aa ras chos thon pa dang
NK032(khi)004:2681: sprang po de ku co re che slob dpon gsung
NK032(khi)004:2682: re zhan / khyed gnyis kyi sgra de ngas ma go bas /
NK032(khi)004:2684: slob dpon gyis ji skad gsungs pa lags zhus pas /
NK032(khi)004:2685: de yang sngar bzhin du gsungs so //
NK032(khi)004:2686: 'o na khos shes pa 'dug gam byas pas /
NK032(khi)004:2687: khos shes pa gcig 'dug pas khyod song la ltos la shog dang gsungs nas /
NK032(khi)004:2688: der a tsa ra dz+ny+aa nas btsal bas /
NK032(khi)004:2689: bsam yas kyi gling bar na btsong mo gcig gi
NK032(khi)004:2690: gam na chang nyo yin 'dug pa dang 'phrad nas
NK032(khi)004:2691: der chang mnyam por nyos nas khyed kyi slob dpon
NK032(khi)004:2692: su yin / chos ci shes pa yin /
NK032(khi)004:2693: khyod rang gi ming ji skad zer ba yin dris pas /
NK032(khi)004:2694: khong gi zhal nas nga'i slob dpon bee ro tsa na bya ba yin /
NK032(khi)004:2695: bka' rdzogs pa chen po'i chos shes pa yin /
NK032(khi)004:2696: mdo khams smad nas 'ongs pa yin //
NK032(khi)004:2697: ming rgyal mo g.yu sgra snying po bya ba yin gsungs nas /
NK032(khi)004:2698: der gnyags dz+ny+aa na ku m+aa ras 'o na nga chos shig zhu ba yin byas pas /
NK032(khi)004:2700: yang na rig pa dang rig pa barje /
NK032(khi)004:2701: yang na rig pa yon gyis bslu /
NK032(khi)004:2702: yang na rig pa bu la byin bya ba yin pas /
NK032(khi)004:2703: khyod nga'i bu ni min sbyin don med /
NK032(khi)004:2704: lo ts+aa ba nga mkhas pa yin te /
NK032(khi)004:2705: khyed mnga' bskur ba'i lo ts+aa bar 'dug pas bar zhugs byar mi rung bas /
NK032(khi)004:2706: slob dpon bi ma la mi tra 'di phyi 'gyur
NK032(khi)004:2707: bcu gsum la mkhas pa yin 'dug pas khyod kyi
NK032(khi)004:2708: lo ts+aa ba gyis la nga la shod /
NK032(khi)004:2709: ngas snga 'gyur rnam pa lnga khyod la bshad cing /
NK032(khi)004:2710: rig pa dang rig pa barje'o //
NK032(khi)004:2711: yang na rig pa yon gyis bslu bya ba yin pas /
NK032(khi)004:2712: i ha ha dang rde'u ser po spyang khu'i r+ts+wa dang chu khams pa dang bcas khyer la shog /
NK032(khi)004:2713: ngas chos sbyin gyi zer nas /
NK032(khi)004:2714: der rig pa dang rig pa yang barjesa te /
NK032(khi)004:2715: phyi 'gyur bcu gsum gyi lo ts+aa ba byas nas
NK032(khi)004:2716: g.yu sgra snying po la gnyags dz+ny+aa na ku m+aa
NK032(khi)004:2718: snga 'gyur rnam pa lnga a tsa ra dz+ny+aa na la g.yu sgra snying pos tshur la bshad /
NK032(khi)004:2719: der bka' sems smad bco brgyad gnyis kas shes par byas so //
NK032(khi)004:2720: rig pa yon gyis kyang bslus te phra yol zung zhig chang gis bkang nas phyag tu phul /
NK032(khi)004:2721: na bza' ci yod phud nas slob dpon g.yu sgra snying po la bskon /
NK032(khi)004:2722: sring mo la lto skal bskur nas nye gnas byed
NK032(khi)004:2723: pa'i zhabs bar 'dir ma phyir ldeb grangs gcig chad
NK032(khi)004:2725: theg pa thams cad lam rmongs pa ston pa'i zhal skyin gcig yin yang dag /
NK032(khi)004:2726: ces yang dag bcu gcig gi sgo nas bstod cing bsgrags so //
NK032(khi)004:2727: de nas rgyal mo g.yu sgra snying pos slob dpon bee ro tsa na dang mjal /
NK032(khi)004:2728: thugs kyang tshim par byas nas grub pa thob ste /
NK032(khi)004:2729: yar stod tsha lung phug par klu dam la btags
NK032(khi)004:2730: nas rigs rgyud ma nor ba la nad du mdze
NK032(khi)004:2732: rigs rgyud ni yar stod kyi rgyal mo 'di tsho yin skad do //
NK032(khi)004:2733: de nas gnyags a tsa ra dz+ny+aa na yang grub pa thob pa yin te /
NK032(khi)004:2734: skyam gyi khyer thog dang bong zan dgon par bzhugs
NK032(khi)004:2735: te rigs rgyud ni lan gar gyi gnyags tsho dang
NK032(khi)004:2737: de nas slob dpon bee ro tsa na de g.yu
NK032(khi)004:2738: sgra snying po yang med de thugs skyo bar byung
NK032(khi)004:2739: nas rgyal mo tsha ba'i shod bya ba nas rgyal
NK032(khi)004:2740: mo tsha ba'i rong na mar la nyin lam bcu
NK032(khi)004:2741: gsum gyi thag ring ba'i sa ru skyo sangs la
NK032(khi)004:2742: byon pas / rgyal mo stag rtse mkhar bya ba na /
NK032(khi)004:2743: spang mi pham mgon po bya ba dgung lo dgu bcu rtsa lnga tsam du lon pa /
NK032(khi)004:2744: bod skad byang ba dad pa che ba gcig dang mjal nas /
NK032(khi)004:2745: khong na re bod na slob dpon bee ro tsa
NK032(khi)004:2746: na bya ba la skad cig mas don rtogs nas
NK032(khi)004:2747: tshe gcig la sangs rgya ba'i chos yod zer ba
NK032(khi)004:2748: la / khyod der chos zhu yin mi sdod par
NK032(khi)004:2749: chos med pa'i yul 'di na mar la 'ong ba
NK032(khi)004:2750: stangs re zhan zer ba la /
NK032(khi)004:2751: slob dpon gyi zhal nas de lta bu shes pa'i
NK032(khi)004:2752: bee ro tsa na bya ba de nga rang yin
NK032(khi)004:2753: te / rgya gar gyi ban+desa phra ma bcug pa
NK032(khi)004:2754: la bod glen pas phra ma snga btsan du song
NK032(khi)004:2755: te / bas / rgyal blon rnams kyis nga 'di na mar la spyugs pa yin gsungs pas /
NK032(khi)004:2756: spang rgan po de na re /
NK032(khi)004:2757: gzhon pa'i tshe na chos ma nus dka' sla ni shor /
NK032(khi)004:2760: sdug la tshe ring ba 'dis ci byed shi na rung shi na rung sems tsa na /
NK032(khi)004:2761: slob dpon dang mjal ba ma shi bas 'tshengs zer nas /
NK032(khi)004:2762: slob dpon gyi mgul nas 'khyud nas nyin zhag phrug
NK032(khi)004:2763: gcig tu ma btang bar khyed kyis rtogs pa bdag
NK032(khi)004:2764: la bskyed par zhu 'tshal byas pas /
NK032(khi)004:2765: slob dpon bee ro tsa nas phyag spyi bor bzhag nas /
NK032(khi)004:2766: a ha ho'i zhes byin gyis brlabs pas /
NK032(khi)004:2767: chos med pa'i yul du grub mthas blo ma bsgyur
NK032(khi)004:2768: ba 'byung ba rgud pas shes pa nyams pa'i mi
NK032(khi)004:2769: nag rgad po las sgrib yod pas rgyud la skyer
NK032(khi)004:2770: ma btub ste / skyabs 'gro khyad par can la
NK032(khi)004:2771: brten nas sems bskyed dbang bskur byin rlabs mdzad nas
NK032(khi)004:2772: ma btub ste / / smrar btub tshad tshig tu bshad /
NK032(khi)004:2773: smrar ma btub pa brdas bstan /
NK032(khi)004:2774: brdas sems kyi yul du bstan /
NK032(khi)004:2775: ngag rna ba'i dbang por blugs nas yang dag thugs kyi sgrub pa la brten nas /
NK032(khi)004:2776: sgom tshul bla ma'i byin rlabs kyis sems nyid dngos
NK032(khi)004:2777: po'i gnas lugs de ji bzhin par rtogs kyang don
NK032(khi)004:2778: mngon du ma gyur gyi bar du rgyud la goms
NK032(khi)004:2779: par byed pa la rgas pas lus tshugs ma thub
NK032(khi)004:2780: ste pus 'khyud zer te sgom thag gis bcings /
NK032(khi)004:2781: bcings kyang 'gyel 'gro bas sgom rten btsug /
NK032(khi)004:2782: don chos nyid kyi ngang ngam tshul de las mi
NK032(khi)004:2783: 'da' bar yid ches par bya ba'i ched du tshul
NK032(khi)004:2784: shing gtad nas dbang bzhi rdzogs par bskur nas /
NK032(khi)004:2785: der mi pham mgon po'i thugs la skad cig mas
NK032(khi)004:2786: don rtogs nas tshe gcig gis sangs rgya ba'i chos
NK032(khi)004:2787: skye ba med pa'i don nam mkha' lta bur thugs
NK032(khi)004:2789: slob dpon bee ro tsa na de la mnyes nas /
NK032(khi)004:2790: ga re rgyal po la ngas lan gcig 'ong bar khas blangs pa yin pas /
NK032(khi)004:2791: da yang bod du 'gro dgos sems nas /
NK032(khi)004:2792: mi pham mgon po'i drung du phyag rgya mtho do ba mdzad nas 'di skad du brjod pa'o //
NK032(khi)004:2793: bdag nyid bee ro tsa na mchis pa 'di //
NK032(khi)004:2794: yang dag bcu gcig don dang ye nas ldan //
NK032(khi)004:2795: rgya gar yul nas chos blangs nas //
NK032(khi)004:2796: sgra don bsdebs nas bka' bsgyur te //
NK032(khi)004:2797: mnga' bdag rgyal po nyid la gtad //
NK032(khi)004:2798: bod kyi rgyal khams dkar por btang //
NK032(khi)004:2799: rgyal dang blon po kun log nas //
NK032(khi)004:2800: spyugs nas tsha ba'i rong du mchis //
NK032(khi)004:2801: chos rgyud sde dang klong sde bka' bkrol nas //
NK032(khi)004:2802: g.yu sgra snying po nyid la gtad //
NK032(khi)004:2803: tsha ba'i rgyal khams dkar por btang //
NK032(khi)004:2804: yang dag don gcig mchis pa de //
NK032(khi)004:2805: mi pham mgon po nyid la gtad //
NK032(khi)004:2806: skyed med nam mkha'i mtha' bzhin rgyas //
NK032(khi)004:2807: ri mtho sa gtsang bod yul dbus //
NK032(khi)004:2808: tha ma gangs kyis bskor bas gcan gzan dug sbrul med //
NK032(khi)004:2809: dgos dgu sa la 'byung bas bod yul dbus de bzang //
NK032(khi)004:2810: bdag nyid bee ro tsa na mchis pa 'di //
NK032(khi)004:2811: sgyu ma'i phung po bod du smin //
NK032(khi)004:2812: sgyu ma'i phung po bod smin pas //
NK032(khi)004:2813: bdag nyid slar la bod du mchis //
NK032(khi)004:2814: gsungs nas spang mi pham mgon po'i sog pa'i khar thal lcag gcig rgyab pas /
NK032(khi)004:2815: khyod kyi mi pham gyis sangs rgyas pa rang yin cing /
NK032(khi)004:2816: 'gro ba'i mgon gyis gsungs nas gshegs te /
NK032(khi)004:2817: tsha ba rong nas tsha ba thon nas byon pas bsam yas su gro khar brtol lo //
NK032(khi)004:2818: de nas bsam yas sgo mo'i thang nas yar la
NK032(khi)004:2819: sgra rigs mi 'dra ba mang po bsgyur gyin glag
NK032(khi)004:2820: cor glag cor byon tsa na /
NK032(khi)004:2821: slob dpon rang gi yum de dang mjal ba la mos ngo shes pas /
NK032(khi)004:2822: der dri mol byas na yang mi gzhan gyis go
NK032(khi)004:2823: na gzhan gyis gtam ngan pa sgrogs kyi dogs nas
NK032(khi)004:2824: / slob dpon gyis phyag gis brda byas pa la mos kyang gsongs shig bya bar go nas /
NK032(khi)004:2825: ngo mi shes pa'i bardzu btab ste /
NK032(khi)004:2827: ci skad bya ba yin byas pas /
NK032(khi)004:2828: slob dpon gyis mdo khams smad nas 'ongs pa yin /
NK032(khi)004:2829: ming ban chung ye shes sde bya ba yin gsungs so //
NK032(khi)004:2830: der yab dang mnga' bdag rgyal po dang pan+di ta
NK032(khi)004:2831: bi ma la mi tra dang kun gyis ngo shes
NK032(khi)004:2832: par byung ba la gsongs shig bya ba'i phyag brda
NK032(khi)004:2836: sgra don bsgyur ba'i lo ts+aa ba shes sam byas pas /
NK032(khi)004:2837: khong gi zhal nas mdo khams kyi smad nas 'ongs pa yin /
NK032(khi)004:2838: ming ban chung ye shes sde bya ba yin /
NK032(khi)004:2839: sgra dang don bsgyur ba'i lo ts+aa ba nga mkhas pa yin gsungs nas /
NK032(khi)004:2840: dus de tsa na bsam yas na rgya gar gyi pan+di ta pad+ma sam b+ha wa dang /
NK032(khi)004:2842: bi ma la mi tra la sogs pa bzhugs so //
NK032(khi)004:2843: sgra bsgyur ba'i lo ts+aa ba ska ba dpal brtsegs dang /
NK032(khi)004:2844: cog ro klu'i rgyal mtshan no //
NK032(khi)004:2845: yi ge bsgyur ba'i lo ts+aa ba thon mi sam b+ho ta mi chung dang /
NK032(khi)004:2846: la gsum rgyal ba'i byang chub bo //
NK032(khi)004:2847: de'u dus de'i tshe sgra dang don bsgyur ba la
NK032(khi)004:2848: lo ts+aa ba mkhas pa gcig ni ban chung bee
NK032(khi)004:2850: de yang mtshan ban chung ye shes sde zhes bya bar grags so //
NK032(khi)004:2851: mdo rgyud kun na ban chung ye shes sdes bsgyur cing zhus te gtan la phab pa'o //
NK032(khi)004:2852: zhes bya bar gsungs nas yod do //
NK032(khi)004:2853: dus de tsa na bee ro tsa na'i yum bsgres
NK032(khi)004:2854: par 'dug pas tshe la long mi 'dug pas sngon
NK032(khi)004:2855: la yum la bsnyen gnas kyi sdom pa phog /
NK032(khi)004:2858: bar slob ma'i sdom pa dang /
NK032(khi)004:2859: dge slong ma'i sdom pa rnams rim gyis zhag bdun
NK032(khi)004:2860: bdun bar du bcug nas yum rab tu byung ste
NK032(khi)004:2861: dge slong ma byas nas dpal phug po cher bzhugs
NK032(khi)004:2862: su bcug go // phug po cher grongs nas pur
NK032(khi)004:2863: bsam yas has po ri la sbyangs te yum gyi
NK032(khi)004:2864: sku tshab tu has po'i ri'i rtse la mchod rten
NK032(khi)004:2865: su bcug go // gcig bzhengs pas / da lta
NK032(khi)004:2866: bee ro tsa na'i mchod rten zer ba de yin
NK032(khi)004:2867: su bcug go // gcig bzhengs pas / no //
NK032(khi)004:2868: slob dpon bee ro tsa na'i yab kyi zhal nas
NK032(khi)004:2869: su bcug go // gcig bzhengs pas / no // / gzhon pa'i lus dang dar ma'i mdangs //
NK032(khi)004:2870: na so rgas pas gnas skabs 'gyur //
NK032(khi)004:2871: mi sdug skra dkar gnyer mas gos //
NK032(khi)004:2872: lang tsho yol nas 'chi la nye //
NK032(khi)004:2873: dgos pa'i dus su dam chos med //
NK032(khi)004:2874: 'khor bar 'khyams pa 'di ru mi dga' na //
NK032(khi)004:2875: byas nas bu la gyod brdungs pas /
NK032(khi)004:2876: yab dang rgyal po gnyis la rgyal blon gyi snying gtam tshig gcig bya ba gcig btab pas /
NK032(khi)004:2877: der yab kho thag chod thugs tshim nas yab 'chi
NK032(khi)004:2878: khar 'tsher med du grol nas bde bar gshegs te
NK032(khi)004:2879: bus lan lon cing yab mnyes pa lags skad /
NK032(khi)004:2880: der slob dpon bee ro tsa nas chos thams cad dar bar mdzad //
NK032(khi)004:2881: khyad par du'ang man ngag gi chos zab mo rnams
NK032(khi)004:2882: dar bar mdzad nas bod la phan thogs par mdzad
NK032(khi)004:2883: / yab yum kyang bde ba'i gnas su gshegs /
NK032(khi)004:2884: mnga' bdag rgyal po thugs kyang tshim nas sgrags kyi
NK032(khi)004:2885: yang rdzong la gshegs nas phyag rgya mtho do ba
NK032(khi)004:2886: zhig mdzad nas tshigs bcad 'di skad gsungs te /
NK032(khi)004:2887: bdag nyid bee ro tsa na mchis pa 'di //
NK032(khi)004:2888: yang dag bcu gcig don dang ye nas ldan //
NK032(khi)004:2889: rgya gar yul nas chos bslabs nas //
NK032(khi)004:2890: sgra don bsdebs nas bka' bsgyur te //
NK032(khi)004:2891: mnga' bdag rgyal po nyid la gtad //
NK032(khi)004:2892: bod kyi rgyal khams dkar por btang //
NK032(khi)004:2893: rgyal dang blon po kun log nas //
NK032(khi)004:2894: spyugs pas tsha ba'i rong du mchis //
NK032(khi)004:2895: chos rgyud sde dang klong sde bka' bkrol nas //
NK032(khi)004:2896: g.yu sgra snying po nyid la gtad //
NK032(khi)004:2897: tsha ba'i rgyal khams dkar por btang //
NK032(khi)004:2898: yang dag don gcig mchis pa de //
NK032(khi)004:2899: mi pham mgon po nyid la gtad //
NK032(khi)004:2900: skye med nam mkha'i mtha' bzhin rgyas //
NK032(khi)004:2901: bdag nyid bee ro tsa na mchis pa 'di //
NK032(khi)004:2902: sgyu ma lta bu'i chos rnams la //
NK032(khi)004:2903: sgyu ma lta bu'i gang zag gis //
NK032(khi)004:2904: sgyu ma lta bur mngon spyad nas //
NK032(khi)004:2905: sgyu ma lta bur mngon sangs rgyas //
NK032(khi)004:2906: nam mkha' lta bu'i chos nyid la //
NK032(khi)004:2907: nam mkha' lta bu'i sems nyid kyis //
NK032(khi)004:2908: nam mkha' lta bur mngon spyad nas //
NK032(khi)004:2909: nam mkha' lta bur mngon sangs rgyas //
NK032(khi)004:2911: a ha ho'i gnyis su med pa'i don la gsal
NK032(khi)004:2912: 'grib med gsungs nas glal dang bya rmyang dal gyis
NK032(khi)004:2913: byas nas nam mkha'i dbyings su 'aja'i sna bsdus pa
NK032(khi)004:2914: bzhin du 'od du 'ubs kyis phung po lhag med
NK032(khi)004:2916: yang dag don gcig mchis pa de //
NK032(khi)004:2917: mi pham mgon po nyid la gtad //
NK032(khi)004:2918: bya ba'i tshigs bcad de ngan lam byang chub rgyal mtshan gyi snyan du gsan nas /
NK032(khi)004:2919: ngan lam byang chub rgyal mtshan zhes bya ba dbu
NK032(khi)004:2920: ru ngan lam ral gsum pa yin te dge slong
NK032(khi)004:2921: dgung lo drug cu rtsa bdun lon pa gcig gis
NK032(khi)004:2922: rgyal mo stag rtse mkhar du spang mi pham mgon
NK032(khi)004:2924: slob dpon bee ro tsa na'i yang dag pa'i don de khyod la yod mchi bas /
NK032(khi)004:2925: 'o skol la thugs la gdags par zhu byas pas /
NK032(khi)004:2926: der khong gis brda sems kyi yul du bstan /
NK032(khi)004:2927: ngag rna ba'i dbang por blugs /
NK032(khi)004:2929: byin gyis brlabs pa yang mdzad do //
NK032(khi)004:2930: de nas bla ma'i zhal nas /
NK032(khi)004:2931: khyod yul du ma 'gro bar mdo khams kyi smad
NK032(khi)004:2932: na wa seng ge brag bya ba gcig yod cing
NK032(khi)004:2933: / der sgom du song zhig gsungs nas /
NK032(khi)004:2934: khams kyi wa seng ge brag tu byon no //
NK032(khi)004:2935: de nas za ngam rin chen dbyig bya ba mdo
NK032(khi)004:2936: khams stod pa gcig gis khams kyi wa seng ge
NK032(khi)004:2937: brag tu byon nas ngan lam byang chub rgyal mtshan
NK032(khi)004:2939: ngan lam byang chub rgyal mtshan gyis za ngam rin chen dbyig la brda sems kyi yul du bstan /
NK032(khi)004:2940: ngag rna ba'i dbang por blugs /
NK032(khi)004:2942: byin gyis brlabs pa yang mdzad nas wa seng ge brag tu bla ma'i rtsar bzhugs so //
NK032(khi)004:2943: yang dag don gcig mchis pa de //
NK032(khi)004:2944: mi pham mgon po nyid la gtad //
NK032(khi)004:2945: bya ba de yar klungs kyi khu 'gyur gsal ba mchog gi snyan du gsan nas /
NK032(khi)004:2946: dge slong dgung lo lnga bcu rtsa bdun lon pa gcig gis rgyal mo stag rtse mkhar byon nas /
NK032(khi)004:2947: spang mi pham mgon po la zhus pas /
NK032(khi)004:2948: nga'i gdams ngag 'di gcig brgyud du yod pas ngas
NK032(khi)004:2949: bstan du mi rung bas khams kyi wa seng ge
NK032(khi)004:2950: brag na ngan lam byang chub rgyal mtshan bya ba
NK032(khi)004:2951: nga'i slob ma gcig yod kyi /
NK032(khi)004:2952: de la zhus shig byas nas lung bstan pas /
NK032(khi)004:2953: khu 'gyur gyis der byon nas gdams ngag zhus pas /
NK032(khi)004:2954: ngan lam gyi zhal nas 'di gcig brgyud kyi gdams ngag yin pas ngas bstan du mi rung bas /
NK032(khi)004:2955: khyod rang nga'i slob ma za ngam rin chen dbyig
NK032(khi)004:2956: bya ba nga rang gi rtsa na yod pa 'di
NK032(khi)004:2958: der za ngam rin chen dbyig la zhus pas khong gis brda sems kyi yul du bstan /
NK032(khi)004:2959: ngag rna ba'i dbang por blugs /
NK032(khi)004:2961: byin gyis brlabs pa yang mdzad do //
NK032(khi)004:2962: de nas khu 'gyur gsal ba'i mchog de yang wa seng ge'i brag de rang du bzhugs te /
NK032(khi)004:2964: yang dag don gcig mchis pa de //
NK032(khi)004:2965: mi pham mgon po nyid la gtad //
NK032(khi)004:2966: bya ba'i tshig de gtsang gi nyang g.yu 'brug stong
NK032(khi)004:2967: pa nyang byang chub grags pa bya ba'i snyan du
NK032(khi)004:2968: gsan nas / nyang byang chub grags pa dge slong
NK032(khi)004:2969: lo nyi shu rtsa gnyis bzhi bcu yang snang lon
NK032(khi)004:2970: pa gcig gis mi pham mgon po'i spyan sngar byon
NK032(khi)004:2971: gsan nas / nas / gdams ngag de zhu byas
NK032(khi)004:2972: pas ma gnang bar khyod rang khams kyi wa seng
NK032(khi)004:2973: ge brag tu zhus dang gsungs nas /
NK032(khi)004:2974: der khams su byon nas ngan lam la zhus pas za ngam la zhus zer /
NK032(khi)004:2975: za ngam la zhus pas khu 'gyur mchog la zhus
NK032(khi)004:2976: zer nas der khu 'gyur gsal ba'i mchog la zhus
NK032(khi)004:2977: pas / brda sems kyi yul du bstan /
NK032(khi)004:2978: ngag rna ba'i dbang por blugs /
NK032(khi)004:2980: byin gyis brlabs pa yang mdzad do //
NK032(khi)004:2981: de nas nyang byang chub grags pa khams su ma
NK032(khi)004:2982: bzhugs par bod du byon te bsam yas mchims phu
NK032(khi)004:2983: na bzhugs nas yod tsa na /
NK032(khi)004:2984: dbu ru zhwa'i nyang shes rab 'byung gnas bya ba
NK032(khi)004:2985: dge slong bsgres po gcig bzhugs nas 'dug pa de
NK032(khi)004:2986: na re / bsnyen par nga rdzogs /
NK032(khi)004:2987: na song rgan kyang gdams ngag khyed che bar 'dug pas /
NK032(khi)004:2988: nga'i slob dpon khyed la zhu gsungs nas /
NK032(khi)004:2989: der nyang shes rab 'byung gnas la nyang byang chub grags pa brda sems kyi yul du bstan /
NK032(khi)004:2990: ngag rna ba'i dbang por blugs /
NK032(khi)004:2992: byin gyis brlabs pa yang mdzad de /
NK032(khi)004:2993: nyang shes rab 'byung gnas des res bsam yas mchims phur bzhugs /
NK032(khi)004:2994: res sgrags kyi yang rdzong dang ngam shod phug po cher bzhugs pa lags skad /
NK032(khi)004:2995: mjug tu phug po che na phug chung zur ri
NK032(khi)004:2996: bya ba'i dgon pa gcig yod pas de na bzhugs
NK032(khi)004:2998: slob dpon rba sgom de lo mo'i rba yin te mtha' bzhi rgya tsho'i jo bo yin pas /
NK032(khi)004:3000: nged kyi yul na 'khrugs pa che bas bu 'di
NK032(khi)004:3001: sring mo drug gi ming po gcig pu yin pas
NK032(khi)004:3002: / slob dpon myang shes rab 'byung gnas la 'chol /
NK032(khi)004:3003: ma shi bas chog zer nas rba sgom lo bcu
NK032(khi)004:3004: drug tsam lon pa gcig byol nas lag bde dang
NK032(khi)004:3005: slob gnyer byed srung skyob zhus nas nyang shes rab
NK032(khi)004:3007: nyang byang chub grags pa rgyam nye kha na phung
NK032(khi)004:3008: po ri bo che zer ba'i sgrub gnas brgya rtsa
NK032(khi)004:3009: brgyad chu mig brgya rtsa brgyad yod /
NK032(khi)004:3010: spyi bo na shug pa phung po gcig yod zer ba gcig tu gshegs /
NK032(khi)004:3011: res 'ga' sgrags kyi yang rdzong ngam mchims phu'am phug po cher yar byon 'ong ba yin skad /
NK032(khi)004:3012: nyang sha ba can kyang zer te sha ba gson po gcig khrid kyin 'ong skad /
NK032(khi)004:3013: phug po cher phyi dag ma la byon pa gcig
NK032(khi)004:3014: la nyang byang chub grags pa'i zhal nas khyed pha
NK032(khi)004:3015: spad gnyis la de bas ltad mo gcig ston gyi
NK032(khi)004:3016: / nga la ltos shig gsungs nas /
NK032(khi)004:3017: slob dpon shes rab 'byung gnas dang rba sgom gnyis kyis g.yas dang g.yon nas bltas pas /
NK032(khi)004:3018: khong dbus na bzhugs nas yod pa de mi snang bar song /
NK032(khi)004:3019: de nas rlung 'tshubs khru gang ba gcig tu song
NK032(khi)004:3020: nas phar bskyil tshur bskyil byas nas de yang mer
NK032(khi)004:3021: song / chu gtor btang ba'i snod mkhar gzhong gcig
NK032(khi)004:3022: yod pas de'i nang du chur ltem gyis song ngo
NK032(khi)004:3023: song / // de yang gzhug tus 'tshubs su 'ong
NK032(khi)004:3024: ring la mdun na slob dpon krong gis byung nas
NK032(khi)004:3026: dwangs ma la yal ba'i bar du de ltar 'ong ba yin /
NK032(khi)004:3027: bag chags kyi blo snang zad /
NK032(khi)004:3028: 'byung ba'i lus dang ma bral ba'i dus su zad
NK032(khi)004:3029: par gyi skye mched bya ba de ltar 'ong ba
NK032(khi)004:3030: yin no // shes rab la sgom rgyu med pa'i
NK032(khi)004:3031: don mthong kyang brda la yengs pa med par bskyangs
NK032(khi)004:3032: na de ltar rang dbang thob pa la tshegs med
NK032(khi)004:3033: yin no // / ma yengs pa skyong ba gal che ba yin no gsungs skad /
NK032(khi)004:3034: de nas gtsang du gshegs nas song ngo //
NK032(khi)004:3035: de nas dus nam zhig gi tshe /
NK032(khi)004:3036: slob dpon rba sgom gyis bal bu'i nags la shing
NK032(khi)004:3037: bsgrub tu phyin pas rba sgom gyis kho rang gi
NK032(khi)004:3038: 'jag spyil me dmar ring der 'dug pa mthong nas
NK032(khi)004:3039: / slob dpon rang thang me mi 'bud pa la
NK032(khi)004:3040: de ring gi de 'dra ci tsug yin nam sems
NK032(khi)004:3041: nas shing 'thu 'phro bcad nas bltar phyin tsa na
NK032(khi)004:3042: ci yang ma byas par 'dug nas /
NK032(khi)004:3043: spyil po la mer mthong ba de 'dra ba ci tsug yin nam byas nas /
NK032(khi)004:3044: 'o de ngas mer sgom pa yin /
NK032(khi)004:3045: slob dpon byang chub grags pa'i de ma dran nam gsungs skad /
NK032(khi)004:3046: de nas nang ma gcig slob dpon gyi bzhugs sa na chu gcig ltem mer gda' skad /
NK032(khi)004:3047: der rgab rdul song ba sems byed pa gcig byung
NK032(khi)004:3048: nas nangs par slob dpon gyi spyan ya gcig zim
NK032(khi)004:3049: me gda' skad / spyan ci nyes byas pas nga'i
NK032(khi)004:3050: mal na chu gcig 'dug pa ma dran nam gsungs
NK032(khi)004:3051: me gda' skad / skad / chu gcig 'dug pa
NK032(khi)004:3052: la ci byed pa yin nam sems nas rgab rdul
NK032(khi)004:3054: da 'dug na rdul de bsal gcig gsung nas sa
NK032(khi)004:3055: rdul 'dug pa bsal tsa na slob dpon gyi spyan
NK032(khi)004:3056: g.yas pa tshags pa hur re la sos nas gda'
NK032(khi)004:3057: skad / der dang po chur sgom shes pa la rdul de 'don shes su gsha' byas pas /
NK032(khi)004:3058: chur sgom pa gcig dang rdul sel ba gcig gnyis su mi 'ong gsungs skad /
NK032(khi)004:3059: de nas nang ma gcig na nga mi 'dug na lha ri'i rtse mo la ltos shig gsungs nas /
NK032(khi)004:3060: dus nam zhig slob dpon ri la skyo sangs la song ba ma byon nas /
NK032(khi)004:3061: sang dgong byon du re ba yang ma byon /
NK032(khi)004:3062: de ci tsug yin snyam nas bsam pa la /
NK032(khi)004:3063: nga mi 'dug na lha ri'i rtse mo la ltos shig gsungs pa de dran nas /
NK032(khi)004:3064: nangs par bltar phyin tsa na /
NK032(khi)004:3065: slob dpon phung po lhag med du gshegs nas na
NK032(khi)004:3066: bza' dang chos gos dang gsag ka li khru ga
NK032(khi)004:3067: nga ba gcig la sa ga ram gyi thur ma
NK032(khi)004:3068: la dngul gyi seng chung btang ba gcig dang dbu
NK032(khi)004:3069: zhwa tro pi gcig dang bo d+hi tse'i phreng ba
NK032(khi)004:3070: gcig de rnams lha ri'i rtse mo'i shug pa rkang
NK032(khi)004:3071: gcig gi yal ga la gzar nas /
NK032(khi)004:3072: slob dpon mi bzhugs par lhag med du gshegs nas mi gda' skad do //
NK032(khi)004:3073: slob dpon rba sgom ye shes byang chub kyis dgung
NK032(khi)004:3074: lo nyi shu rtsa bzhi lon tsa na slob dpon
NK032(khi)004:3075: shes rab ye shes kyis brda sems kyi yul du
NK032(khi)004:3076: bstan / ngag rna ba'i dbang por blugs /
NK032(khi)004:3078: byin gyis brlabs pa yang mdzad pa lags skad /
NK032(khi)004:3079: slob dpon rba sgom de rten yang dge bsnyen sngags par bzhugs /
NK032(khi)004:3080: bzhugs gnas kyang phug chung zur ri na bzhugs nas
NK032(khi)004:3081: nye gnas btsun chung gcig gis byed kyin yod pa'i
NK032(khi)004:3082: dus de tsa na slob dpon 'dzeng chen pos de
NK032(khi)004:3084: slob dpon gyi yab 'dzeng bdag bkra shis g.yung drung
NK032(khi)004:3085: bya ba tshe smad la rab tu byung ba tshul
NK032(khi)004:3086: khrims rgyal mtshan bya ba dgung lo drug cu rtsa
NK032(khi)004:3087: bdun la phur pa man ngag ur nan gyi lugs
NK032(khi)004:3089: rdo rje gzhon nu'i zhal gzigs pa /
NK032(khi)004:3090: brgyad cu gya lnga la 'das nas pur sbyangs pas rdo rje gzhon nu'i sku gcig byon /
NK032(khi)004:3091: ring bsrel mang po byon pa la kyi khung gi spyil po'i nang na bzhugs nas yod skad /
NK032(khi)004:3092: slob dpon gyi yum mtshar dgu bza' skyid de mtsho
NK032(khi)004:3093: yar lung gi thang chung na jo mo byas nas
NK032(khi)004:3094: yod pa thang chung btsad po'i bu che ba slob
NK032(khi)004:3095: dpon gyi yab kyis phab nas slob dpon sku 'khrungs
NK032(khi)004:3096: pa yin skad / slob dpon gyi zhal nas nga
NK032(khi)004:3097: la mig gi ka ba yod pas yar lung nub
NK032(khi)004:3098: phyogs na yar la phyin pas /
NK032(khi)004:3099: thang chung btsad po byung zer ba yang byung gsung /
NK032(khi)004:3100: da lta zim shi 'dzing a jo rgyud bya ba yin gsung /
NK032(khi)004:3101: lo brgyad kyi bar du mtshar dgu'i klungs su zhang po'i gan du bsdad /
NK032(khi)004:3102: de nas gung po dben tshar bsdad /
NK032(khi)004:3103: de nas kyi khung du lo lnga tsam bsdad /
NK032(khi)004:3104: de nas lo bcu bdun lon tsa na /
NK032(khi)004:3105: zhang po gshen tsha dar ma 'od kyi slob dpon
NK032(khi)004:3106: rtsang pa ral gcig mo'i g.yog po rdo rje snying
NK032(khi)004:3107: po / byo shwa re gnyags dge ba 'bar dang /
NK032(khi)004:3108: tshos dol gyi gdung sna ru tshong la phyin tsa na /
NK032(khi)004:3109: dol gyi 'tsher chung bya ba na mi mang po spung nge 'dug /
NK032(khi)004:3110: der bltar phyin pas dam pa rgya gar dang mjal /
NK032(khi)004:3111: zla ba ril po bcu bzhi phyag phyir 'brangs /
NK032(khi)004:3112: dam pas nga la lwa ba'i snam bu gcig bskon /
NK032(khi)004:3113: gtsang gi gnas gzhi zangs can du brtol tsa na /
NK032(khi)004:3114: khong dang thung 'dug khyod rang yul du log /
NK032(khi)004:3115: shar phyogs dwags po nas kham bu khyer la shog gsungs /
NK032(khi)004:3116: dol du 'gro ba'i zla bo 'dug go gsungs nas phyin tsa na /
NK032(khi)004:3117: dam pa phyi na tshur la brengs kyis byon nas skal ldan bu gnyis la phyag gis 'jus nas /
NK032(khi)004:3118: ci yang ma yin gnas 'gyur ba //
NK032(khi)004:3119: gnas gyur ba la gnyis 'dzin med //
NK032(khi)004:3120: gsungs nas mgo thug lan gnyis rgyab /
NK032(khi)004:3121: kha na tshur la chu 'dur la sems ci yang
NK032(khi)004:3122: ma dran pa shes pa sal le ba gcig byung
NK032(khi)004:3123: / de dam pas byin gyis brlabs pas sgrib pa dag /
NK032(khi)004:3124: rdo rje zam pa'i rdo rje'i tshig dang mthun /
NK032(khi)004:3126: chos 'di dang mjal bar lung bstan pa yin 'dug pa la /
NK032(khi)004:3127: da gdod las ma go gsungs /
NK032(khi)004:3128: dam pa de brda chos las tshig mang po dang long gtam lar mi gsung ba gcig 'dug /
NK032(khi)004:3129: da lta zhi byed pa la tshig mang po 'dug
NK032(khi)004:3130: ste dam pas de tsam gsung mi srid pa gcig
NK032(khi)004:3131: yod / dus tshod la chos thams cad mang nas lad 'gro ba yin /
NK032(khi)004:3132: rdo rje zam pa 'di rang yang cir nan lad pa'i dus gcig 'ong bas /
NK032(khi)004:3133: de tsa na bshad pa 'phro chod la brda bzhi la sgom khrid du skyongs shig /
NK032(khi)004:3134: dang po ma bshad na gdams ngag zab mo yod pa'i khungs mi phyin /
NK032(khi)004:3135: bar du sgom khrid ma byas na dad pa can bsrangs su mi tshud /
NK032(khi)004:3136: tha ma grub rtags gcig ma thon na phyi ma
NK032(khi)004:3137: tsho spro ba mi skye bas chos nub tu 'gro
NK032(khi)004:3138: ba yin pas mjug tu rtags thon par nyams su
NK032(khi)004:3139: longs shig / des brgyud pa 'dzin pa je mang la 'gro ba yin no gsungs /
NK032(khi)004:3140: nga dang slob dpon rba sgom gnyis mjal ba ni /
NK032(khi)004:3141: ngas lo sum cu so lnga tsam lon tsa na
NK032(khi)004:3142: gtsang ba skor nas spyang rtsigs su brtol tsa na
NK032(khi)004:3143: / phug po che'i la kha na dge bshes btsan
NK032(khi)004:3144: kha bo che bya ba rgya gar nas byon ma
NK032(khi)004:3145: thag pa zhig cig jo mos spyan drangs nas chos
NK032(khi)004:3146: dang bza' ba dang ltad mo yod zer gyin 'dug
NK032(khi)004:3147: pas nangs par snga ba nas byon tsa na /
NK032(khi)004:3149: khrab nas lam zur 'di na yar la phyin na
NK032(khi)004:3150: slob dpon rba sgom bya ba byung tsho la lto
NK032(khi)004:3151: ster ba gcig yod zer nas phyin pas /
NK032(khi)004:3152: rnal 'byor pa tsho gcig gis brtol zin nas de
NK032(khi)004:3153: tsho la slob dpon gyis tsha ba drangs nas phye
NK032(khi)004:3154: zangs kyi khyem bu re re gtong gin 'dug /
NK032(khi)004:3155: de tsho khyer nas 'o de na gcig kyang 'dug pa gsungs nas /
NK032(khi)004:3156: der chu bum pa gang len du bcug /
NK032(khi)004:3157: chab gtor btang nas khyim du khrid nas sran ma ke ru'i tshod ma phu ru gang drangs /
NK032(khi)004:3158: de'i nub kyang lto byin nas brag rtsa gcig tu nyal nas bsdad /
NK032(khi)004:3159: nangs par 'gro dogs sems tsa na yang lto byin
NK032(khi)004:3160: nas nga la nye gnas btsun chung gcig yod pa
NK032(khi)004:3161: la zwa thang du gser lan du song ba la
NK032(khi)004:3163: shing gcig bsgrub tu bcol dang gsungs nas nags khrod
NK032(khi)004:3164: nas shing skam khur che ba gcig bsgrubs nas phyin
NK032(khi)004:3165: pas shin tu mnyes nas phyag rgya chen po brda'i
NK032(khi)004:3167: rdzogs pa chen po'i skor bdun rang chas bya ba bshad /
NK032(khi)004:3168: de nas nye gnas btsun chung de byung nas mdang
NK032(khi)004:3169: sum slob dpon 'o brgyal snyam tsa na bla mas
NK032(khi)004:3170: go bcad nas 'dug pas da dung yang zhag kha
NK032(khi)004:3171: shas shig bzhugs par zhu zer nas yang yar lung
NK032(khi)004:3172: du lan gcig bskor nas byung ngo //
NK032(khi)004:3173: de nas slob dpon rba sgom de grub thob ngo
NK032(khi)004:3174: mtshar can du shes nas yul du ma phyin par
NK032(khi)004:3175: 'on dang zangs ri yan chad du ston snga ba
NK032(khi)004:3176: kun la bslang / sgye gcig nyos te nas sgye
NK032(khi)004:3177: gang dang bcas pa slob dpon rba sgom la 'bul
NK032(khi)004:3178: kun la bslang / du phyin pas / slob dpon
NK032(khi)004:3179: rba sgom gyi zhal nas nga'i g.yogs khyod kyis byas
NK032(khi)004:3180: pa yin na nga la 'di 'dra ba 'bul mi
NK032(khi)004:3181: kun la bslang / du phyin pas / dgos / 'di la khyod rang gis rgyags gyis /
NK032(khi)004:3182: nga la gdams ngag rdo rje zam pa bya ba
NK032(khi)004:3183: skad cig mas don rtogs nas tshe gcig gi sangs
NK032(khi)004:3184: rgyas pa phung po lhag med kyi brgyud pa phreng
NK032(khi)004:3185: ma chad pa rna brgyud rdo rje zam pa bya
NK032(khi)004:3186: ba gcig yod / de gong phan chad du gzhan su la'ang ma smras par gsang ba yin te /
NK032(khi)004:3187: gsang ba de mi yid du 'ong ba sems mthun pa dang 'phrad tsa na /
NK032(khi)004:3188: kha nas phis kyi shor nas smras 'gro gin 'dug pas /
NK032(khi)004:3189: gdams ngag de khyod la sbyin no gsungs nas /
NK032(khi)004:3190: slob dpon 'dzeng gis nas 'di slob dpon la bsngosa pa yin pas gsol bar zhu /
NK032(khi)004:3191: gdams ngag de thugs la gdags par zhu /
NK032(khi)004:3192: chos rgyags rnyed 'ong gis byas pas /
NK032(khi)004:3193: slob dpon gyi phyag g.yon pas spyi bo la bzung /
NK032(khi)004:3194: phyag g.yas pas ltag khung du lcab lcab byas nas /
NK032(khi)004:3195: 'or che dam tshig can du 'dug pas ngas gdams
NK032(khi)004:3196: ngag sbyin gyis phan thogs par 'ong bar 'dug gi
NK032(khi)004:3197: gsungs nas / der lo chung du sngags pa gcig
NK032(khi)004:3198: la gshin rje dmar po'i sgrub thabs gcig byin pas
NK032(khi)004:3200: lo mo 'am 'phrun du bsrung skyob zhad re byas
NK032(khi)004:3201: pas chos rgyags ldang bar byung nas nan tan du
NK032(khi)004:3202: byas pas / rdo rje zam pa'i chos tsho la byin rlabs kyi chos tsho ma gtogs pa lon /
NK032(khi)004:3203: da sgom tshul bla ma'i byin rlabs byed pa la
NK032(khi)004:3204: 'dzin ci yang med pas phyi nas zhu dgos sems
NK032(khi)004:3205: tsa na / slob dpon gyi zhal nas byin rlabs da lta bya /
NK032(khi)004:3206: phyi nas bar chad 'ong ba la tshegs med gsungs nas /
NK032(khi)004:3207: gang bar du grogs po gcig la sing mo gcig
NK032(khi)004:3208: bcol nas yod pa de la rin gcig slong du
NK032(khi)004:3209: phyin pas jo mo ba bcom pa'i sham thabs gcig
NK032(khi)004:3210: byin pas / de'i rnam pa tsho phral nas btsong
NK032(khi)004:3211: bas chang phud dang gtor ma dang nas bre lnga
NK032(khi)004:3212: dang sha gzugs gcig dang de tsho la brten nas
NK032(khi)004:3213: byin pas / / mar me ma 'dzom pa la slob dpon gyi zhal nas /
NK032(khi)004:3214: mar me'i dod po nyin par la bya'o gsungs nas /
NK032(khi)004:3215: nyin mo sgom tshul bla ma'i byin rlabs grol lam dbang bzhi rdzogs par bskur /
NK032(khi)004:3216: brda sems kyi yul du bstan /
NK032(khi)004:3217: ngag rna ba'i dbang por blugs /
NK032(khi)004:3219: byin gyis brlabs pa yang mdzad do //
NK032(khi)004:3220: de nas gdams ngag rnams ma lus par gnang /
NK032(khi)004:3221: byin rlabs phyi nas kyang lan bzhi tsam zhus /
NK032(khi)004:3222: zhabs tog kyang nas dang gser la sogs pa lan lnga tsam bskyal gsungs /
NK032(khi)004:3223: de'i rting ma slob dpon rba sgom la zhabs tog
NK032(khi)004:3224: ma jo mo gang mo bya ba gcig yod pa
NK032(khi)004:3225: la / de tsa na slob dpon gyi zhal nas /
NK032(khi)004:3226: snang ba 'di kun bden snyam pa mi 'dug gsungs
NK032(khi)004:3227: nas chu rdo ma gcig la phyag char gyis rgyab
NK032(khi)004:3228: pas gru mo man chad chu rdo ma la bstim
NK032(khi)004:3229: gyis song / sku lus phyir shigs kyis mdzad pas
NK032(khi)004:3230: brag la sku lus bstim gyis song bas rjes wal
NK032(khi)004:3231: gyi byung ba'i shul yod pa dge bshes gshen pa'i
NK032(khi)004:3232: khang pa brtsigs pas subs pa yin skad /
NK032(khi)004:3233: phug chung rong nas ting nge 'dzin gyis shug pa'i
NK032(khi)004:3234: gdung ma mang po drangs byung ba da lta jo
NK032(khi)004:3235: mo'i mchod khang phub pa yin gsungs so //
NK032(khi)004:3236: de nas slob dpon rba sgom de dgung lo dgu
NK032(khi)004:3237: bcu rtsa brgyad la grongs pa'i tshul bstan pa yin
NK032(khi)004:3238: te bsnyung ba'i na tsha med par gshegs 'dug skad
NK032(khi)004:3239: / de nas bran 'khor kun gyis chang khur nas
NK032(khi)004:3240: jo mo gang mo la mya ngan sangs du lo
NK032(khi)004:3241: mo nas 'ongs ba la mo thu bas slob dpon
NK032(khi)004:3242: bzhugs tsa na mi 'ong bar nga la chang gi
NK032(khi)004:3243: dgos pa med khyod rang tsho 'thung zer nas mos
NK032(khi)004:3244: sgo nang nas bcad nas mjal du ma btub skad
NK032(khi)004:3245: / / der khong tsho ma dgyes pa la jo
NK032(khi)004:3246: mos pur mchod khang du bzhus pas me lce la
NK032(khi)004:3247: 'od bum pa tsam pa gcig tu byas nas mig
NK032(khi)004:3248: gi mngon ngang gi nam mkha' la gshegs nas song
NK032(khi)004:3249: ba g.yul thang ga'i mya ngan bsangs pa'i chang 'thungs
NK032(khi)004:3251: phug po che na yod pa rnams kyis kyang mthong
NK032(khi)004:3252: ste shul tu pur sbyangs pa'i gdung thal yang ma
NK032(khi)004:3253: byung bar rjes med du 'od du gshegs pa lags
NK032(khi)004:3254: skad do // bla ma rin po che 'dzeng chen po'i zhal nas /
NK032(khi)004:3255: nga dang po bla ma dam pa rgya gar dang
NK032(khi)004:3256: mjal ba la byin rlabs kyis mgo thugs gcig byas
NK032(khi)004:3257: rdo rje zam pa dang mjal ba'i lung bstan pa
NK032(khi)004:3258: yin 'dug pa la da gzod las ma go /
NK032(khi)004:3259: ngas shud pu lo ts+aa ba la 'grel chung mnyan /
NK032(khi)004:3260: dge bshes grol sgom pa la n+aa ro pa'i thabs lam zhus /
NK032(khi)004:3261: lha rje snyi sgom la chos drug dang skyes sbyor zhus /
NK032(khi)004:3262: rtogs pa bsdur bas shin tu mnyes so //
NK032(khi)004:3263: so bsnyun gdangs pa la sgron sprul dang rgyab sha zhus /
NK032(khi)004:3264: rdza phor ba la bdud rtsi tshig gsum zhus /
NK032(khi)004:3265: ri khrod rlung chung pa la rna brgyud tshig gsum dang tshig don lnga pa zhus /
NK032(khi)004:3266: bla ma rlung dam pa chen po la do ha'i gdams ngag zhus /
NK032(khi)004:3267: sgom ma lab sgron la gcod yul gyi gleng bslang zhus /
NK032(khi)004:3268: rgyal ba sba ston la lhun grub sde skor bdun pa zhus /
NK032(khi)004:3269: gnubs shangs po che la bla ma ba ri lo
NK032(khi)004:3270: ts+aa ba'i kri ya'i chos lnga gsum bco lnga zhus
NK032(khi)004:3271: / dge bshes khams pa lung pa la bka' gdams kyi thun brgyad ma zhus /
NK032(khi)004:3272: dge bshes sne'u zur pa'i bu chen gcig la dmigs pa skor gsum zhus /
NK032(khi)004:3273: spyan snga rnal 'byor pa'i gra sa ru spyod pa byas pas shin tu mnyes nas byung /
NK032(khi)004:3274: lar ngas chos mang po thos te rdo rje zam
NK032(khi)004:3275: pa 'di kho na gnad che la kha rub par
NK032(khi)004:3276: 'dug pas 'di la nan tan du byas pa yin
NK032(khi)004:3277: / dwags po zhu ru'i lha zur dgon par brda bzhis bskyangs pas chos thams cad la byan tshud /
NK032(khi)004:3278: dgongs pa nam mkha' bzhin du 'dres /
NK032(khi)004:3279: don thams cad spros bral rnam dag la song /
NK032(khi)004:3280: gyur cig dang shog cig la ltos ma dgos /
NK032(khi)004:3281: rig pa dwangs pas he ru ka'i zhal mthong /
NK032(khi)004:3282: ched du bsgrub mi dgos par mngon shes zhar la 'char bar 'dug /
NK032(khi)004:3283: chos nyid la sgom rgyu mi 'dug kyang gang zag
NK032(khi)004:3284: lha dang 'grogs nas don ma bying bar byed pa
NK032(khi)004:3285: 'di gal che bar 'dug go gsungs so //
NK032(khi)004:3286: ngas a tsa ra stag sham can dang /
NK032(khi)004:3289: bla ma drod 'byor ram bla ma zhang gro smyon dang /
NK032(khi)004:3290: de tsa na'i rnal 'byor pa bzang po sha stag dang 'grogs te /
NK032(khi)004:3291: gtsang du gcer bu lo lnga byas /
NK032(khi)004:3292: 'khyag pa'i nang du bzhugs pa dang /
NK032(khi)004:3293: chu lteng nang du mchong pa dang byas pas chu s+aa rings kyis 'gro ba'i drod 'bar ba dang /
NK032(khi)004:3296: mtshon brdeg pa la sogs pa ci yang byas te spyod pa'i tshan che shos kyang yin /
NK032(khi)004:3297: dpa' bo 'dzeng chung ba zer ba yin gsung /
NK032(khi)004:3298: ri khrod rlung chung pa dang /
NK032(khi)004:3299: dngul mo rgyal le lcam dang /
NK032(khi)004:3300: mon kha zer mo'i mtsho la sogs pa'i ma jo
NK032(khi)004:3301: gcig dang kong po mtsho rdzong la sogs pa'i khams
NK032(khi)004:3302: pa dang kun phung po lhag med du song ba
NK032(khi)004:3303: yang byung gsungs / ras pa sgom stag /
NK032(khi)004:3306: rlung ras pa dang ngo mtshar che ba drod 'bar ba yang byung gsung /
NK032(khi)004:3307: bstan pa tsam gyis rtogs grol la song ba yang byung gsungs /
NK032(khi)004:3308: nga'i gam du sgra bsgyur shes pa'i lo ts+aa ba bzhi byung /
NK032(khi)004:3313: yus po che yus mo che rang mthong can mang zhig byung nas /
NK032(khi)004:3314: gdams ngag 'di ci 'dra ba zhig 'dug bltas pa yin du song ste /
NK032(khi)004:3315: gdams ngag zab kha rub zer nas nges shes skyes pa mang ba byung ste /
NK032(khi)004:3316: shes par slob khom pa tsam ma byung gsungs /
NK032(khi)004:3317: tshul bzhin du nyams su len pa dang a cang ches te /
NK032(khi)004:3318: dwags por nyams len en re byed pa'i nya ma
NK032(khi)004:3319: bcu gcig tsam la yang dang por 'chi dus thebs
NK032(khi)004:3320: pa / 'chi khar gnad gcod kyi na tsha med pa /
NK032(khi)004:3321: shul du ro la 'ja' zug pa byung ba yin gsungs /
NK032(khi)004:3322: nga'i gdams ngag 'di la bal ma bal byed pa'am /
NK032(khi)004:3323: pha ma sri'u gso ba kho na 'dra ba'i nyams
NK032(khi)004:3324: len gcig byas na lo lnga'am drug na lhag med
NK032(khi)004:3325: du 'gro stee shul du lus pa mi yong nges
NK032(khi)004:3326: gsungs so // slob dpon rin po che des res 'ga' sku lus 'ja' ru 'khyil nas 'dug pa /
NK032(khi)004:3327: res zhabs sa la mi reg par byon pa dang /
NK032(khi)004:3328: res thag ring po yud tsam re res bskor nas byung yang mthong skad /
NK032(khi)004:3329: sbur po dar re dang sbur sgom dang dpal lcam
NK032(khi)004:3330: chos 'bar dang ril ba 'chi ba shes pa la
NK032(khi)004:3331: sogs pa gzhan gyi sems shes pa dang /
NK032(khi)004:3332: 'chi 'pho ba dang skye ba dran pa'i mngon par shes pa yang byung skad /
NK032(khi)004:3333: jo sras ma rdo rje skyid kyi bu nam phyed
NK032(khi)004:3334: na gnyid rmis nas rgya mthong na mar la rbab
NK032(khi)004:3335: tu shor la khad pa mthong ba dang /
NK032(khi)004:3336: cod pan skyu ba'i khab nub mo sbur ma'i khrod
NK032(khi)004:3337: du brul ba gzigs pa la sogs pa nyin mtshan
NK032(khi)004:3338: med par gsal ba yang yod pa yin skad do
NK032(khi)004:3339: // slob dpon gyi zhal nas ngas lo mang po
NK032(khi)004:3340: lon zer ba de nga rang gis tig pa kha
NK032(khi)004:3342: kyi khung gi dge bshes hab jo sras 'jam dpal bya ba na re /
NK032(khi)004:3343: 'dzeng sgom gsas thog de da dung du dwags po na 'dug zer ba /
NK032(khi)004:3344: nga dang gnyis gzhon tsa na grogs po yin te /
NK032(khi)004:3345: de yang lo bco lnga kho nas khong rgan pa yin te /
NK032(khi)004:3346: da ngas kyang lo dgu bcu rtsa bdun song 'dug gsungs /
NK032(khi)004:3347: de nas lo gcig lon nas khong grongs /
NK032(khi)004:3348: slob dpon 'dzeng gis de'i rting la yang lo gsum chod lon 'dug pas /
NK032(khi)004:3349: dgung lo brgya dang bcu bdun kho na lon 'dug go //
NK032(khi)004:3350: slob dpon gyi zhal nas dge bshes hab kyi khungs pa'i de kha na bden pa yin gsung ngo //
NK032(khi)004:3351: dam pa rgya gar dang mjal ba yin bya ba
NK032(khi)004:3352: de lha bzo klu rgyal dam pa'i sku 'bag gcig
NK032(khi)004:3354: de bla ma rgya gar mi 'dra byas pas /
NK032(khi)004:3355: 'o na ci 'dra ba gcig yod zer bas /
NK032(khi)004:3356: ngas 'di 'dra ba gcig 'dug byas nas bshad pas /
NK032(khi)004:3357: de nas de skad gleng ba gcig byung /
NK032(khi)004:3358: de gong du bshad pa med gsung /
NK032(khi)004:3359: nga la gdams ngag 'dug zer ba de byar lkog
NK032(khi)004:3360: tu lha rje snyi sgom dang gnyis rtogs pa bsdur
NK032(khi)004:3361: bas khong mnyes nas nga'i lag pa kho rang gi
NK032(khi)004:3363: de nas sangs rgyas ga na yang cha mi 'dug pa gsungs nas /
NK032(khi)004:3364: sgom chen pa rnams nga shing khur nas phyin pa la phyag 'tshal du bcug go //
NK032(khi)004:3365: de nas gsang dbang med par gdams ngag can du
NK032(khi)004:3366: 'dug zer nas chos zhu ba mang ba la zhad
NK032(khi)004:3367: re byin / nang ma gcig rkang pa'i ngar gdong la 'bras byung bas shi la khad byung /
NK032(khi)004:3368: da res shi na gdams ngag 'di nub 'gro ba 'dug /
NK032(khi)004:3369: gdams ngag 'di lhag par byin dgos bsam pa dang sangs kyis sos pa yin pas /
NK032(khi)004:3370: da ngas gdams ngag 'di mi sri ba yin no //
NK032(khi)004:3371: dad pa can gdams ngag 'dod nges pa 'dug na nga'i gam du khrid la shog cig /
NK032(khi)004:3372: dus kyi tha ma la gdams ngag 'di dar nas 'ong ba yang bshad nas kyang 'dug /
NK032(khi)004:3374: nga la bu srad ma can med pa /
NK032(khi)004:3375: srad ma can gcig gis dar nas 'ong ba yin pa la /
NK032(khi)004:3376: nga la yang srad ma gsas thog zer ba yin /
NK032(khi)004:3377: lar du chos byed pa la mi srad ma can
NK032(khi)004:3378: rang dbang thob pa gcig min na zhe zhim gron
NK032(khi)004:3379: bcug tshod len pa gcig gis mi yong bar ngan
NK032(khi)004:3381: slob dpon rin po che 'dzeng chen po dang slob
NK032(khi)004:3382: dpon 'dzeng jo sras gnyis mjal ba'i lo rgyus la
NK032(khi)004:3383: / slob dpon jo sras de yang yab sngags pa'i
NK032(khi)004:3384: rigs rgyud du song bas chung ngu nas yig rtsis
NK032(khi)004:3385: / bslab / bcu bzhi bco lnga nas nus pa thon /
NK032(khi)004:3386: de'i rjes la 'ol kha'i slob dpon lha ris pa
NK032(khi)004:3387: la sgyu 'phrul la sogs pa'i rnying ma'i chos skor
NK032(khi)004:3388: gsan / dgyes rdor mtshan brjod zhus te shes par ma bslab gsung /
NK032(khi)004:3389: slob dpon lha ris pa 'da' khar gzhung chen po
NK032(khi)004:3390: 'di tsam pa'i chos gcig shes pa la 'chi khar
NK032(khi)004:3391: phan pa a ro'i thun bdun 'di kun las gzhan
NK032(khi)004:3392: lam du khyer du btub pa tsam dka' bar byung
NK032(khi)004:3393: bas / jo sras khyod rang yang gzhung ma bslab par gdams ngag la nan tan gyis shig gsungs /
NK032(khi)004:3394: dwags po na khyed rang gi bla ma 'dzeng bya
NK032(khi)004:3395: ba'i gdams ngag can grub thob gcig bzhugs nas yod
NK032(khi)004:3396: 'dug pas der song la nan tan gdams ngag la
NK032(khi)004:3398: gang bar du slob dpon zem bya ba rdzogs chen
NK032(khi)004:3399: lhun grub mkhan gcig gi drung du phyin nas dbyar
NK032(khi)004:3400: dgun thog drug bsdad pa la /
NK032(khi)004:3401: thugs la 'dogs pa kha na ma byung ste /
NK032(khi)004:3402: gdams ngag gi spros pa mchod nas dwags por slob dpon 'dzeng la zhus pas /
NK032(khi)004:3403: dpal lung du rdo rje zam pa tshar gsum gnang /
NK032(khi)004:3404: sgom tshul bla ma'i byin rlabs kyang mdzad nas /
NK032(khi)004:3405: da khyod rang gtsang na yar la song la gzhung 'dra bslab /
NK032(khi)004:3406: nged kyi rigs la sngags pa rtsa can zhi rtse las chos byung ba tsam med /
NK032(khi)004:3407: gtsang nas log tsa na a mis dgon pa gcig bdog cig gsungs skad /
NK032(khi)004:3408: slob dpon gyis mi gnang bar go nas gdams ngag 'di sangs kyi shes pa su yod dris pas /
NK032(khi)004:3409: gra phyi'i skyil jo sras zhang la skyabs bya bas shes pa yin te gsungs /
NK032(khi)004:3410: g.ye'i gur por khong dang gnyis mjal nas zhu bar
NK032(khi)004:3411: byas nas khong gi yig cha ngas kung lung du
NK032(khi)004:3412: tshags byas nas khong gra ru grongs nas ma byung
NK032(khi)004:3413: / de nas yang dwags por phyin pas slob dpon
NK032(khi)004:3414: gyi zhal nas a jo dkon mchog kyang chos 'dod
NK032(khi)004:3415: pa skad zer nas nor 'dod pa yin 'dug /
NK032(khi)004:3416: khyod la yang ka ca 'dra ba sbyin ran na nga la da lta 'dzom pa med gsungs pas /
NK032(khi)004:3417: 'o na nye rigs su song bas chos 'dod pa yin yang bza' 'dod pa yin snyam 'dug pas /
NK032(khi)004:3418: chos 'dir zhus pas mi gnang bar gron bcug 'dug sems nas /
NK032(khi)004:3419: btsan thang gi lha rje myang ngam 'ol ka'i dwags chung ba kun gyis shes su rung ba yin /
NK032(khi)004:3420: du gcer bu la yang yod pa yin te ci
NK032(khi)004:3421: tshugs su yod cha med khyod rang gzhan du slob
NK032(khi)004:3422: gnyer gyis la shog dang chos 'ong bar 'dug na
NK032(khi)004:3424: de nas yar sho skyam ru slob dpon ngu la
NK032(khi)004:3425: zhus pas ma gnang nas 'di sus kyang mi 'ong
NK032(khi)004:3426: da dung dwags por song la rtsad chod cig gsungs
NK032(khi)004:3427: nas / yang dwags lung 'dzin du byon nas zhus pas /
NK032(khi)004:3428: da khyod cis kyang 'dod na nga'i gdams ngag 'di la nan tan byed dgos pa yin /
NK032(khi)004:3429: mtshan nyid pa bzhin rig pa brtag dpyad byas pas grol du re ba yang 'di min /
NK032(khi)004:3430: lha rje snyi sgom pa'i chos drug bzhin du thabs
NK032(khi)004:3431: lam gyi rtsol ba dang bsam pa dang dmigs pa
NK032(khi)004:3432: la brten nas grol du re ba yang 'di min
NK032(khi)004:3433: / lto zhal 'thams nga bzhin du shi grol du 'dod pa'i gdams ngag kyang 'di min /
NK032(khi)004:3434: nga'i 'di gnas lugs rjen pa'i don de blo'i yul
NK032(khi)004:3435: du byar ma btub pas sgom du med pas shes
NK032(khi)004:3437: 'khrul du med pas brdas yengs su med /
NK032(khi)004:3438: ma bsam mi dmigs par brdal ngang gis bzhag pas
NK032(khi)004:3439: ma sgom ma 'khrul pa'i shes pa gcig rang byung
NK032(khi)004:3441: chos nyid ngo bo nyid gnas lugs de la zhal
NK032(khi)004:3442: rgyun chad med par bltas nas goms 'dris byas na
NK032(khi)004:3443: don mngon du gyur nas tshe gcig lus gcig la
NK032(khi)004:3444: 'tshang rgyar yod pa yin gsungs nas /
NK032(khi)004:3445: de nas gdams ngag rnams rim gyis ma lus par gnang /
NK032(khi)004:3446: dgun thog gcig nan tan che bar gnang /
NK032(khi)004:3447: byin rlabs kyang mdzad nas 'byung ba dar rgud kyi stabs kyis brjed du yang 'gro ba yin pas /
NK032(khi)004:3448: da yi ge'am brjed tho 'dra ba yang byas pas chog gsungs nas /
NK032(khi)004:3449: gnubs ston sangs rgyas skyabs la gnang nas brjed thor
NK032(khi)004:3450: bris pa'i khro bo'i dpe tsho gcig kyang gnas nas
NK032(khi)004:3451: / der dbyar dgun thog 'gar slob dpon gyi thad
NK032(khi)004:3452: du bsdad pas lo drug tsam du song tsa na
NK032(khi)004:3453: gdams ngag gi phran tsho yang ma lus par gnang
NK032(khi)004:3454: / / byin rlabs gzhan la mdzad pa'i las kyi
NK032(khi)004:3455: slob dpon byas pas lag len kyang byang bar byas
NK032(khi)004:3456: / / / byin rlabs kyi chos la zin bris byed par zhu ba phul bas /
NK032(khi)004:3457: da dung du zin bris dgos na shes pa'i dus
NK032(khi)004:3458: mi 'ong gsungs nas bkyon du'ang byung ba yin gsung
NK032(khi)004:3459: / sang phod da khyod la sbyin no gsungs nas
NK032(khi)004:3460: byin rlabs kyi chos skor rnams la dpe ni mi
NK032(khi)004:3461: 'dug slob dpon gyi thugs nas bton pas bkod pa
NK032(khi)004:3462: / yin gsungs / dus tshod de tsa na dwags
NK032(khi)004:3463: lung du dge 'dun ston tsher bas bla ma sbub
NK032(khi)004:3465: slob dpon sbub thung ba'i slob ma yin zer nas rnal 'byor pa'i dmag 'tshogs nas /
NK032(khi)004:3466: de'i dus su bla ma rogs po dga' 'am ma
NK032(khi)004:3467: jo zla bo'am de kun gyis dpon byas pa'i mi
NK032(khi)004:3468: zla lnga bcu tsam pa gcig na re /
NK032(khi)004:3469: nga la jo sras 'dzeng chung ba la rdo rje zam pa'i gdams ngag zhu dgos zer ba la /
NK032(khi)004:3470: ngas gnang ba ma thob pas da dung du bshad pa mi 'ong byas pas /
NK032(khi)004:3471: slob dpon chen po'i zhal nas grwa pa gdams ngag 'dod pa mang bar 'dug pas /
NK032(khi)004:3472: deng skabs su mi khoms pa dang rgas pas nga
NK032(khi)004:3473: jo sras kyis bshad dgos pa yin no gsungs nas
NK032(khi)004:3474: rdo rje slob dpon gyi dbang yang bskur /
NK032(khi)004:3475: jo sras kyis shod cig khyed tshos nyon cig gsungs
NK032(khi)004:3476: nas slob dpon chen po'i gsungs pa'i khri kha nas
NK032(khi)004:3477: rjes la slob dpon gyis bshad pa yin /
NK032(khi)004:3478: lar slob dpon jo sras dang slob dpon chen po
NK032(khi)004:3479: gnyis lo ngo bco brgyad tsam du mjal nas gdams
NK032(khi)004:3480: ngag zhus / gdams ngag gi bka' phog nas brgyud
NK032(khi)004:3481: pa 'dzin du bcug pa yin pas da lta brgyud
NK032(khi)004:3482: pa'i rtsa ba byin rlabs zhugs nas bstan pa'i bdag
NK032(khi)004:3483: po mdzad pas sprul pa'i sku slob dpon jo sras
NK032(khi)004:3484: ngag zhus / yin no // slob dpon chen po
NK032(khi)004:3485: rje d+harma bod+hi dang de'i thugs kyi sras 'dzeng chung
NK032(khi)004:3486: du smyon pa 'dzeng dkar gnyis la /
NK032(khi)004:3487: slob dpon kun bzang gis zhus pa'i lo rgyus ni /
NK032(khi)004:3488: spyir nged kyi rigs rgyud tsho la chos pa mgo
NK032(khi)004:3489: thon re re mi chad pa yin par 'dug pa
NK032(khi)004:3490: la / nged kyi khu tshan tsho la chos sgor
NK032(khi)004:3491: zhugs pa nga'i pha jo dbus pa las mi 'dug
NK032(khi)004:3492: la / ste / de yang slob dpon khams pa
NK032(khi)004:3493: rdor rgyal gyi slob ma byas nas sgom chen pa
NK032(khi)004:3494: gang zag bzang por yod pa yin gsungs /
NK032(khi)004:3495: ma rgan zi gza' des chog bya ba yin te /
NK032(khi)004:3496: gzhi yag yang la dad pa che ba gcig yod pa yin te /
NK032(khi)004:3497: ma jo smyon ma bsam 'grub bya ba la chos 'dzugs zhabs tog byed pa 'dug pa yin gsungs /
NK032(khi)004:3498: slob dpon gyi zhal nas nga rang lo lcags khyi
NK032(khi)004:3499: lo'i zla ba nya'i skar ma rgyal la skyes pa
NK032(khi)004:3500: yin par 'dug / nga skye ba'i dus su ma'i
NK032(khi)004:3501: rmi lam na mda' tshe sgro ma gcig la made'u
NK032(khi)004:3502: rag gan khro chu lcags la byas pa gcig rnyed
NK032(khi)004:3503: yin par 'dug / pa rmis skad / ma skyes
NK032(khi)004:3504: tsa na ma'i khong pa nas skad lhang lhang ba
NK032(khi)004:3505: gcig lan gsum tsam byung nas mi rung snyam nas
NK032(khi)004:3506: rtog pa zhugs pa yin te /
NK032(khi)004:3507: khyod kyi chos 'ong ba'i rtags yin 'dug ces chos sgor zhugs nas smras so gsungs /
NK032(khi)004:3508: slob dpon kun bzang de dang po sku 'khrungs pa
NK032(khi)004:3509: dang pha jo dbus pa'i rmi lam na ngas kyang
NK032(khi)004:3510: bu chung nam mkha' la 'phur nas song ba gcig
NK032(khi)004:3511: rmis skad / 'di nged la phan mi thogs par 'chi ba yin nam /
NK032(khi)004:3512: ma shi na chos pa gcig 'ong ba yin nam
NK032(khi)004:3513: byas skad de chos byed pa gcig byung ba 'di
NK032(khi)004:3515: rmi lam de de tsa na pha ma gnyis kas mi gzhan la bshad 'dug /
NK032(khi)004:3516: nga rang la yang phyis nas bshad de /
NK032(khi)004:3517: chos byed pa'i rtags su byung ba yin gsungs so //
NK032(khi)004:3518: slob dpon gyi zhal nas ngas lo dgu lon tsa na nyi zla gnyis po sa la babs nas /
NK032(khi)004:3519: ban d+he grogs grong po'i nags khrod du song ba la /
NK032(khi)004:3520: de nas phyungs nas phyag g.yas g.yon du bcug nas /
NK032(khi)004:3522: bton nas deng byas pas mig gis mthong tshad du
NK032(khi)004:3523: nyi zla'i 'od kyis khyab nas dkar lhag la song
NK032(khi)004:3524: / res dpung rings kyi rgyal pos phrogs kyis dogs
NK032(khi)004:3525: nas sbas yin yib pa gcig rmis pa yin skad
NK032(khi)004:3526: / / de yang skabs su tshogs chos byas pas
NK032(khi)004:3527: dar re dad pa skyes nas yul dkar nub pa
NK032(khi)004:3529: res rgyal pos phrogs kyis dogs nas phyag tu bcug
NK032(khi)004:3530: yin yib pa de bar chad byung gis dogs nas
NK032(khi)004:3531: dbyar gyi rigs la mtshams thabs su byas nas ri
NK032(khi)004:3532: khrod dang dgon pa 'grim pa de la lta ba
NK032(khi)004:3533: yin 'dug gsungs / lan gcig gi rmi lam na
NK032(khi)004:3534: snyims pa zur kha'i khar mo che'i rtsa nas slob
NK032(khi)004:3536: nga'i lag pa la 'jus nas yar la 'then pas
NK032(khi)004:3537: khang pa nyis thog gi rtse mo la yengs kyis
NK032(khi)004:3539: de yang slob dpon skor ston rang byis pa lo brgyad dgu nas mjal ba yin te /
NK032(khi)004:3540: de nas slob gnyer zhad re byas te /
NK032(khi)004:3541: mi chos bya snyam pa'i bsam pa ma byung ste /
NK032(khi)004:3542: 'dren pa'i bla mar gyur pa yin 'dug gsungs /
NK032(khi)004:3543: lo bco lnga lon tsa na slob dpon skor ston
NK032(khi)004:3544: r+aa dza grongs nas slob dpon bu'i gan du lo
NK032(khi)004:3545: lnga tsam zhi byed zhu yin du bsdad de zhabs
NK032(khi)004:3547: gdams ngag le'u bdun pa ma gtogs pa gzhan gyis phan thogs pa kha nas ma byung ste /
NK032(khi)004:3548: chos la dam pa de mthong bas phyis gdams ngag la rtsis dang nan tan cher song /
NK032(khi)004:3549: gdams ngag gnang ba'i bla ma rnams la yang drin du gzo bar byung /
NK032(khi)004:3550: gzhan la yang sngar nga rang chos kyi sred pa'i
NK032(khi)004:3551: nyams myong gis chos la ser sna med par ster
NK032(khi)004:3553: slar bzlas kyang shin tu phan pa gcig byung bas
NK032(khi)004:3554: log lta ma skyes te yang drin du tshor bar
NK032(khi)004:3555: byung gsungs so // da lta'i mi la ma byin na yi chad /
NK032(khi)004:3556: byin na dga' tshor mi skye /
NK032(khi)004:3557: glan ka rko ba'am snyad 'dogs pa kho na 'dra ba mthong tsa na /
NK032(khi)004:3558: slob dpon pa kun shin tu bden par 'dug sems pa yang byung gsungs so //
NK032(khi)004:3559: de nas slob dpon jo sras 'dzeng dang gnyis slob
NK032(khi)004:3560: dpon ngu'i thad du gser lung dgon par mjal ba
NK032(khi)004:3561: yin gsungs / ngas slob dpon la gnang ba zhus
NK032(khi)004:3562: nas ma 'gag rnam dag dang zhi byed rma lugs
NK032(khi)004:3563: dang ka p+aa li rtsi nag can bzang po gcig
NK032(khi)004:3564: rnams phul nas 'dzeng gi gsang sgrub dang phag mo
NK032(khi)004:3565: yin gsungs / mngon byung zhus / rdo rje zam
NK032(khi)004:3566: pa lhag ma lus par gnang ba'i dbu snyung bzhes
NK032(khi)004:3567: pa'i nub mo slob dpon la yang bzhugs pa'i bya
NK032(khi)004:3568: khang de 'od dang me tog gis khengs pa'i rmi
NK032(khi)004:3569: lam dang gnyid log tu mi ster ba'i snang ba
NK032(khi)004:3571: khyod la ngas phan thogs pa gcig 'ong bar 'dug gsungs /
NK032(khi)004:3572: nga rang la yang snga dro gnyid zi ba gcig
NK032(khi)004:3573: la nam mkha' la me tog gis khengs pa rlung
NK032(khi)004:3574: gis khyer yin nga'i mdun du thog tu bab kyi
NK032(khi)004:3575: byung ba gcig rmis pas phan thogs par byung ba
NK032(khi)004:3576: yin no gsungs / de nas slob dpon jo sras
NK032(khi)004:3577: kyis khrid nas slob dpon 'dzeng chen po dang sprad
NK032(khi)004:3578: yin no gsungs / pa'i tshe / tshes bco lnga'i
NK032(khi)004:3579: zla ba gcig shar nas 'dug pa'i dkyil du skar
NK032(khi)004:3580: ma gnyis thim nas song ba gcig rmis pa yin
NK032(khi)004:3581: yin no gsungs / pa'i tshe / te / de
NK032(khi)004:3582: nga dang slob dpon jo sras gnyis kyi brdar byung
NK032(khi)004:3583: yin no gsungs / pa'i tshe / te / gsungs
NK032(khi)004:3584: so // de'i tshe slob dpon 'dzeng chen po la
NK032(khi)004:3585: rdo rje zam pa tshar gcig zhus /
NK032(khi)004:3586: rdo rje zam pa thob pa'i snga shos de yin gsungs /
NK032(khi)004:3587: de nas slob dpon 'dzeng jo sras dpung rings su
NK032(khi)004:3588: spyan drangs nas rdo rje zam pa tshar bdun tsam
NK032(khi)004:3589: zhus / sgom tshul bla ma'i byin rlabs zhus /
NK032(khi)004:3590: de nas yang dwags por slob dpon chen po'i thad du dgun thog bzhi phyin /
NK032(khi)004:3591: der dgun thog lngar song ba yin te /
NK032(khi)004:3592: rdo rje zam pa tshar phyed pa gcig dang bcu bzhi thob bo //
NK032(khi)004:3593: slob dpon jo sras dang lo brgyad tsam la phal cher ma bral bar 'grogs nas 'dug pa la /
NK032(khi)004:3594: rdo rje zam pa tshar bdun zhus gsungs /
NK032(khi)004:3595: na ning phyi nas sho ru tshar gnyis /
NK032(khi)004:3596: gser lung du thun gcig la tshar gcig thon pa
NK032(khi)004:3597: gcig dang nyi shu tham pa de yan gsung 'phro
NK032(khi)004:3598: la mjal ba'i tshar phyed phyed thos pa la tshar
NK032(khi)004:3599: gcig tu byas pas slob dpon rin po che 'dzeng
NK032(khi)004:3600: mes dbon gnyis la tshar sum cu rtsa lnga thos
NK032(khi)004:3601: pa lags gsungs / slob dpon chen po'i thad du
NK032(khi)004:3602: 'gro tsa na ma gi ram btol gyi bar du
NK032(khi)004:3603: 'ja' mi snye ba mi yong ma myong ste chos
NK032(khi)004:3604: pa lags gsungs / rtags su byung / slob dpon
NK032(khi)004:3605: jo sras byon 'ong tsa na lung pa me tog
NK032(khi)004:3606: gis khengs pa sha stag rmir 'ong ba yin te
NK032(khi)004:3607: shin tu bzang bar byung ngo gsungs /
NK032(khi)004:3608: phyi nas slob dpon chen po grongs 'gro tsa na
NK032(khi)004:3609: ston zla ra ba'i nyi shu gnyis kyi srod la
NK032(khi)004:3610: tshes pa bco lnga'i zla ba je chung je chung
NK032(khi)004:3611: la zad pa'i shul na skar ma gnyis 'dug pa
NK032(khi)004:3613: sngar slob dpon dang mjal tsa na skar ma gnyis thim pa rmis pa dang /
NK032(khi)004:3614: phyis zla ba'i shul na 'dug pa rmis pa des
NK032(khi)004:3615: nged slob dpon jo sras dang gnyis kyi brdar byung
NK032(khi)004:3616: gsungs / tho rangs slob dpon chen po grongs nas phur mchod rten gcig gi steng du bskyal nas /
NK032(khi)004:3617: da chos ston gcig byas nas me spar dgos sems tsa na /
NK032(khi)004:3618: sku lus la me rang 'bar du byung ba la
NK032(khi)004:3619: bud med gsum gyi pha rgyal ba 'dzeng ston zer
NK032(khi)004:3621: mchod rten gyi phyogs bzhi na mar la zhun chu
NK032(khi)004:3622: re 'bab kyin 'dug pa ngas mgo la byug khong
NK032(khi)004:3623: par 'thung byas pas lus snum du tsir gyis song
NK032(khi)004:3625: spu lung gi mchod khang du pha jo dbus pa dang /
NK032(khi)004:3631: g.yag sgom lha pho dgos dang /
NK032(khi)004:3632: de rnams la rmi lam bshad skad /
NK032(khi)004:3633: slob dpon rgyal ba 'dzeng ston la phyis dris tsa
NK032(khi)004:3634: na de'i nub mo kho nar grongs pa yin gda'
NK032(khi)004:3635: 'o gsungs / slob dpon gyi zhal nas nga la skye ba snga ma'i las 'phro yod de /
NK032(khi)004:3636: slob dpon rin po che 'dzeng mes dbon gnyis kyi byin rlabs kyi bka' babs pa lags /
NK032(khi)004:3637: snyan brgyud rdo rje zam pa'i bdag po gcig tu bsngosa pa yin no gsungs /
NK032(khi)004:3638: slob dpon rin po che dam pa kun bzang gi
NK032(khi)004:3639: sras sprul pa'i skur skye ba bzhes nas 'gro ba
NK032(khi)004:3640: sems can thams cad byang chub kyi thar pa'i lam
NK032(khi)004:3641: ston par mdzad pa'i sprul sku 'od 'bar gyi lo
NK032(khi)004:3642: rgyus ni / de yang jo sras 'od 'bar seng
NK032(khi)004:3643: ge jo mo rgya smyon ma'i lus khong na med
NK032(khi)004:3644: rgyus ni / tsa na / nga rang gi zhi
NK032(khi)004:3645: nga lag pa can gyi thog tu nam mkha' nas
NK032(khi)004:3646: skar ma chen po gcig babs nas 'od lhag lhag
NK032(khi)004:3648: pha jo la bshad pas bu 'ong ba'i rtags yin /
NK032(khi)004:3649: rgya smyon ma lus po ma bde ba yin nam zer bas /
NK032(khi)004:3651: rgya smyon ma na re nga lus po ma bde ba yod 'dug pas /
NK032(khi)004:3652: 'ong yang khye'u gsha' ma gcig 'ong ba gcig 'dug /
NK032(khi)004:3653: nam mkha' la skar ma'i mi rkang lag can gcig shar 'dug pa gcig rmis /
NK032(khi)004:3654: khyod kyis nor bu rin po che yin no zer ba gcig byung zer ro //
NK032(khi)004:3656: dbyar sham po gangs la lag bde byas pa'i mar
NK032(khi)004:3657: la 'ong tsa na lhums su zhugs pa yin 'dug
NK032(khi)004:3658: nas skar ma 'od lhag lhag pa gcig rmis pa
NK032(khi)004:3659: yin / nga rang la'ang chos rtags su skar ma
NK032(khi)004:3660: sha stag rmi ru byung bas chos pa gsha' ma
NK032(khi)004:3662: 'od 'bar seng ge bya bar btags pa yin gsungs /
NK032(khi)004:3663: slob dpon jo sras 'od 'bar de yang sku sprul
NK032(khi)004:3664: pa'i sku lta bu blo rno ba thugs shes rab
NK032(khi)004:3665: che ba / dgung lo bzhi bcu las ma lon par rdo rje zam pa gsungs pa lags so //
NK032(khi)004:3666: des brgyud 'dzin jo mgon la gnang /
NK032(khi)004:3667: des bya med tshul rin la dgongs pa gsal lo //
NK032(khi)004:3668: chos 'di lta bu'i ngo mtshar can phog pa yin pas bsam rlag tu ma sdod cig /
NK032(khi)004:3669: grub thob gcig byed dgos pa yin gsungs so //
NK032(khi)004:3670: rdo rje zam pa'i gang zag gdams ngag gis grol
NK032(khi)004:3671: ba'i lo rgyus chen mo 'di brgyud 'dzin gyi sras
NK032(khi)004:3672: 'od 'bar seng ge'i don ched du yon tan gyi
NK032(khi)004:3673: 'byung khungs kyi lung pa stag rtse sgra'i lung pa'i
NK032(khi)004:3674: bkra shis nyams dga' ba'i gnas rdzong ri dgon par
NK032(khi)004:3676: slob dpon rin po che kun bzang gis bla ma rgya ye shes seng ge la gnang ngo //
NK032(khi)004:3677: rang don dang gzhan don 'grub par smon no //
NK032(khi)004:3678: des gang thal zhe na slob dpon rin po che
NK032(khi)004:3679: kun bzang gis bla ma rin po che 'dzeng mes
NK032(khi)004:3680: dbon gnyis la zhus pa'i lo rgyus thal lo //
NK032(khi)004:3681: de'i gong ma des slob dpon 'dzeng jo sras kyi lo rgyus thal lo //
NK032(khi)004:3682: de'i gong ma des slob dpon 'dzeng chen po'i lo rgyus thal lo //
NK032(khi)004:3683: de'i gong ma des slob dpon rba sgom gyi lo rgyus thal lo //
NK032(khi)004:3684: de'i gong ma des slob dpon nyang shes rab 'byung gnas kyi lo rgyus thal lo //
NK032(khi)004:3685: de'i gong ma des slob dpon nyang byang chub grags pa'i lo rgyus thal lo //
NK032(khi)004:3686: des chos bod dbus gtsang du brgyud pa thal lo //
NK032(khi)004:3687: de'i gong ma des khu 'gyur gsal ba mchog dang /
NK032(khi)004:3688: za ngam rin chen dbyig dang /
NK032(khi)004:3689: ngan lam byang chub rgyal mtshan te /
NK032(khi)004:3690: khams kyi wa seng ge brag la bzhugs pa gsum gyi lo rgyus thal lo //
NK032(khi)004:3691: de'i gong ma des slob dpon bee ro tsa na'i bka' babs gsum las /
NK032(khi)004:3692: bka' babs brgyud pa tha ma mi pham mgon po la babs pa thal lo //
NK032(khi)004:3693: de'i gong ma des bka' babs bar pa rgyal mo g.yu sgra snying po la babs pa thal lo //
NK032(khi)004:3694: de'i gong ma des bka' babs dang po mnga' bdag rgyal po la babs pa thal lo //
NK032(khi)004:3695: der slob dpon bee ro tsa nas rgyal po la bshad pa dang gcig /
NK032(khi)004:3696: rgyal mo g.yu sgra snying po la bshad pa dang gnyis /
NK032(khi)004:3697: spang mi pham mgon po la bshad nas bsam yas su log nas sgra don bsgyur /
NK032(khi)004:3698: yab yum la phan btags nas sgrags kyi yang rdzong la gshegs pa dang gsum /
NK032(khi)004:3699: spang mi pham mgon po nas da lta bdag yan
NK032(khi)004:3700: chad du brgyud pa dang bzhis gang zag gdams ngag
NK032(khi)004:3701: gis grol ba'i lo rgyus thal ba lags so //
NK032(khi)004:3702: de yang chos kyi sku'i thugs dpal bde ba chen po yin /
NK032(khi)004:3703: chos kyi sku'i gsung dpal kun tu bzang po yin /
NK032(khi)004:3704: chos kyi sku'i sku dpal rdo rje sems dpa' yin /
NK032(khi)004:3705: chos kyi sku'i sku gsung thugs gsum rnam par dag
NK032(khi)004:3706: pas 'gro ba'i don du sprul pa bkye ba sems
NK032(khi)004:3708: de yan chad ni rgyal ba dgongs pa'i brgyud pa yin /
NK032(khi)004:3709: rdo rje sems dpa'i yang sprul dga' rab rdo rje
NK032(khi)004:3710: ni nub phyogs o rgyan gyi yul sprin nag po
NK032(khi)004:3711: 'dus pa'i khrod du mkha' 'gro ma ma rungs pa
NK032(khi)004:3712: 'dul ba la chos gsung gin da dung grongs pa
NK032(khi)004:3713: mi mnga' bar bzhugs nas yod skad /
NK032(khi)004:3714: de'i slob ma 'jam dpal bshes gnyen ni 'phags pa 'jam dpal gyi sprul pa yin te /
NK032(khi)004:3715: dpal yon tan 'byung ba'i grong khyer du da dung grongs pa mi mnga' bar bzhugs yod skad /
NK032(khi)004:3716: de'i slob ma sh+r+ai sing ha ni spyan ras gzigs kyi sprul pa yin skad /
NK032(khi)004:3717: de yang nam mkha' la mkha' spyod du gshegs pa yin skad de /
NK032(khi)004:3718: rgya nag bkra shis khri sgo na 'gro ba'i don mdzad nas yod par ke'u tshang nas bshad gda' /
NK032(khi)004:3719: de'i slob ma bee ro tsa na ni dpal rnam par snang mdzad kyi sprul pa yin te /
NK032(khi)004:3720: sgrags kyi yang rdzong la phung po lhag med du gshegs pa'o //
NK032(khi)004:3721: spang mi pham mgon po dgung lo lnga brgya thub pa yin /
NK032(khi)004:3722: da dung du'ang bzhugs nas yod gsungs skad /
NK032(khi)004:3723: ngan lam byang chub rgyal mtshan khams kyi wa seng
NK032(khi)004:3724: ge brag la dgung lo brgya dang bdun cu rtsa
NK032(khi)004:3725: gnyis lon nas lhag med du bzhud skad /
NK032(khi)004:3726: de'i slob ma za ngam rin chen dbyig brgya dang
NK032(khi)004:3727: bzhi bcu rtsa bzhi lon nas lhag med du gshegs
NK032(khi)004:3728: skad / de'i slob ma khu 'gyur gsal ba'i mchog
NK032(khi)004:3729: gi dgung lo brgya dang bcu bdun lon nas lhag
NK032(khi)004:3731: pha spad de gsum ka khams kyi wa seng ge
NK032(khi)004:3732: brag la sbrul gyi lo la gcig rting la gcig
NK032(khi)004:3733: gshegs te sku na bun dengs pa'am 'ja' yal ba
NK032(khi)004:3734: bzhin du dngos su gshegs pa lags skad /
NK032(khi)004:3735: nyang byang chub grags pa gtsang gi rgyam nye kha'i
NK032(khi)004:3736: phung po ri bo che la deng sang 'dug pa'i
NK032(khi)004:3737: 'phro la ri zur na yar la sku sprin chad
NK032(khi)004:3738: pa bzhin du lhag med du gshegs skad /
NK032(khi)004:3739: nyang shes rab 'byung gnas phug po che'i lha ri'i
NK032(khi)004:3740: rtse mo la shug pa rkang gcig lan bza' dang
NK032(khi)004:3741: / phreng ba ka p+aa li kun gzar nas phung po lhag med du gshegs nas gda' skad /
NK032(khi)004:3742: de'i slob ma slob dpon rba sgom gyis dgung lo
NK032(khi)004:3743: dgu bcu rtsa brgyad lon nas bsnyung ba med par
NK032(khi)004:3744: grongs nas pur mchod khang du sbyangs nas me lce
NK032(khi)004:3745: la 'od bum pa tsam gcig 'dug nas /
NK032(khi)004:3746: mig gi mngon ngang gi nam mkha'i dbyings su gshegs nas shul du gdung thal yang ma byung skad /
NK032(khi)004:3747: de'i slob ma slob dpon 'dzeng chen po'i dwags lung
NK032(khi)004:3748: 'dzi stod dgon par dge bshes kyi khung pas gsung
NK032(khi)004:3749: ba'i dbang du byas na brgya dang bcu bdun bzhes
NK032(khi)004:3750: nas 'dug pas / ma grongs pa nas dgon pa'i mtha' ma 'ja' 'khor byung bar gda' 'o //
NK032(khi)004:3751: de nas ston zla ra ba'i nyi shu gnyis kyi
NK032(khi)004:3752: tho rangs sku gshegs pa la pur sbyangs pas nam
NK032(khi)004:3753: mkha' la 'ja' mig mngas ris su byung ba phar
NK032(khi)004:3754: kha'i rkyang phu ba'i mis mthong ba dang /
NK032(khi)004:3755: ring bsrel dang man+dala pad+ma'i ris can dang /
NK032(khi)004:3756: srin lag thab nas yar nas mchod rten du byung ba yon bdag rdo rjes thob pa dang /
NK032(khi)004:3759: sa g.yos chen po la sogs pa byung bar yin par gda' 'o //
NK032(khi)004:3760: de'i gdung brgyud 'dzin pa slob dpon smyon pa 'dzeng dkar gyis yon tan thams cad kyi mgo thon /
NK032(khi)004:3761: grub thob brgyud pa'i byin rlabs zhugs nas sprul pa'i skur gyur /
NK032(khi)004:3762: da lta bstan pa'i bdag po mdzad /
NK032(khi)004:3763: 'gro ba la phan thogs shin tu che /
NK032(khi)004:3764: ngo mtshar shin tu che bar bzhugs pa lags so //
NK032(khi)004:3765: bla ma rin po che 'dzeng mes dbon gnyis kyi slob ma slob dpon kun bzang gis /
NK032(khi)004:3766: gdams ngag 'di la nan tan du byas nas 'gro ba gzhan rnams nges shes bskyed pa'i phyir /
NK032(khi)004:3767: lo rgyus rgyas par bkod pa 'di brgyud 'dzin gyi
NK032(khi)004:3768: jo sras 'od 'bar seng ge'i don du mdzad pa
NK032(khi)004:3769: lags so // nyung bar 'dod na tshigs bcad dang lo rgyus 'gyang po tsho zhog la shod cig /
NK032(khi)004:3770: de yan chad kyis gang thal na /
NK032(khi)004:3771: rig 'dzin brdas grol ba'i brgyud pa dang /
NK032(khi)004:3772: gang zag gdams ngag gis grol ba'i brgyud pa gnyis pa thal lo //
NK032(khi)004:3773: de gnyis hril gyi dril bas nges shes bskyed pa brgyud pa'i lo rgyus skabs thal ba lags so //
NK032(khi)004:3774: sgom med don gyi gzer chen gdab pa la /
NK032(khi)004:3776: tshig don bstan pa gnyis te /
NK032(khi)004:3779: tshig don ni sgom byed kyi don de brdas ngo sprad pa dang /
NK032(khi)004:3780: don de'i gol sa gcod pa gnyis kyis nan tan du rgyas par bstan pa'o //
NK032(khi)004:3781: dang po sgom du med pa'i go ba mdor bstan pa la /
NK032(khi)004:3782: sgom du med ces pa ni /
NK032(khi)004:3783: gang la sgom du med na /
NK032(khi)004:3784: sems nyid dngos po'i gnas lugs de la bsgom du med de /
NK032(khi)004:3785: de yang ji ltar du bsgom du med na /
NK032(khi)004:3786: sems nyid dngos po'i gnas lugs de ni dus gsum du 'du 'bral med pa /
NK032(khi)004:3789: skye 'gags med pa'i chos bzhi dang ldan pa'i don de ni yid kyi yul lam /
NK032(khi)004:3792: blo'i yul du mi gnas pas /
NK032(khi)004:3793: bsgom par bya ba'i rgyu'am byed pa'i mkhan po gcig
NK032(khi)004:3794: mi 'dug pas don blo'i yul du byas pa'i sgom
NK032(khi)004:3795: rgyu gcig med pas na sgom med do //
NK032(khi)004:3796: de yang ye shes gsang ba 'khor lo'i rgyud las /
NK032(khi)004:3797: bsgom med don la blo bzhag med //
NK032(khi)004:3799: sgom du med pa de nyid blo'i spyod yul du ma gyur pas na don no //
NK032(khi)004:3801: don dam blo yi spyod yul min //
NK032(khi)004:3802: blo ni kun rdzob yin par nges //
NK032(khi)004:3804: sgom du med pa'i don de nyid la bla ma'i
NK032(khi)004:3805: brda dang ngag gis ngo sprad pas don blo bral
NK032(khi)004:3806: 'dus ma byas pa de nyid la rkyen gang gis
NK032(khi)004:3807: kyang phan gnod mi nus te /
NK032(khi)004:3808: bya blo'i 'bad rtsol mi dgos par don de nyid
NK032(khi)004:3809: mi 'chug par 'gyur bar rig cing rtogs pas na
NK032(khi)004:3810: don gyi gzer chen thebs pa'o //
NK032(khi)004:3811: de yang zam pa chenapo dbang gi man ngag las /
NK032(khi)004:3812: sgom med don la bya blo med //
NK032(khi)004:3813: yid la ma byas rang bzhin gnas //
NK032(khi)004:3814: rig pa'i gzer gyis 'da' ba med //
NK032(khi)004:3816: dper na sgo'i 'ba' span la rgyab pas rnam pa 'khrol mi 'gro ste /
NK032(khi)004:3817: mi 'chug mi 'gyur ba lta bur don ma nor
NK032(khi)004:3818: ba la rig cing rtogs pas gzer thebs pas sems
NK032(khi)004:3820: 'khor ba rang rgyud par mi 'chug cing chos nyid kyi ngang las mi 'gyur ba'o //
NK032(khi)004:3821: rna brgyud rdo rje zam pa 'phrul gyi me long brtsegs pa las /
NK032(khi)004:3822: 'phrul gyi me long sgo dgu bzhin //
NK032(khi)004:3823: rtog med mthong ba'i lam sprad de //
NK032(khi)004:3824: sgom med don gyi gzer chen gdab //
NK032(khi)004:3825: bgrod med rtog pa'i 'dam las bsgral //
NK032(khi)004:3827: de ni sgom med don gyi gzer chen gdab pa'i go ba mdor bstan pa'o //
NK032(khi)004:3828: de las kyang go ba rgyas par bshad na /
NK032(khi)004:3829: sgom du med pa'i don de la ming du btags nas stong pa nyid ces bya ste /
NK032(khi)004:3831: sangs rgyas pa'i stong pa dang gcig /
NK032(khi)004:3832: sems can blo'i stong pa dang gnyis /
NK032(khi)004:3833: rnal 'byor pa lam gyi stong pa dang gsum mo //
NK032(khi)004:3834: sangs rgyas pa'i stong pa ni don dam blo'i spyod yul du ma gyur pas sgom du med pa'o //
NK032(khi)004:3835: sems can blo'i stong pa ni ji ltar cha phra
NK032(khi)004:3836: mor gzhig cing gtan la phab kyang blo'i spyod yul
NK032(khi)004:3837: yin pas don sems nyid dngos po'i gnas lugs mtshan
NK032(khi)004:3838: nyid bzhi ldan gyi thog tu mi phebs so //
NK032(khi)004:3839: rnal 'byor pa lam gyi stong pa ni bla ma'i
NK032(khi)004:3840: brda dang ngag gis rgyud la sbyar bas sems can
NK032(khi)004:3841: gyi blo de ma spangs par de nyid du zad
NK032(khi)004:3842: nas blo bral don dam pa dngos po gnas lugs
NK032(khi)004:3843: ci yang ma yin pa de byas pa dang bcos
NK032(khi)004:3844: pa med par gtan med rang gsal du rgyud la
NK032(khi)004:3845: 'char ro // de yang rtsa ba'i rgyud ye shes gsang ba las /
NK032(khi)004:3846: cir yang ma yin gtan med pa'i //
NK032(khi)004:3847: rang gsal ye shes nyi ma'i 'od //
NK032(khi)004:3848: kun bzang rgyal ba'i thugs dam yin //
NK032(khi)004:3850: rnal 'byor lam gyi stong pa des sems can blo'i
NK032(khi)004:3851: stong pa bsam mno dmigs su med par blo zad
NK032(khi)004:3852: nas sangs rgyas pa'i stong pa don dngos po'i gnas
NK032(khi)004:3853: lugs kun tu bzang po'i thugs dgongs de rgyud la
NK032(khi)004:3854: shar ba'o // gsang sngags don gyi tshad ma las /
NK032(khi)004:3855: blo dngos zad cing sems dang chos nyid 'dres //
NK032(khi)004:3856: blo nyid dngos por 'gyur zhes rdo rje sems dpas gsungs //
NK032(khi)004:3858: don dngos po'i gnas lugs mtshan nyid chos bzhi ldan
NK032(khi)004:3859: du rtogs pa de la sgom pa dang mi bsgom
NK032(khi)004:3860: pa'i blo'i mtha' gang yang mi gnas pa'o //
NK032(khi)004:3861: de yang sgom du yod na rtag pa'i mthar lhung /
NK032(khi)004:3862: med na chad pa'i mthar lhung /
NK032(khi)004:3863: yod med du 'dzin pa'i mtha' dang bral ba'i dbu ma /
NK032(khi)004:3864: gol sar 'khyog pa med pa'i drang po /
NK032(khi)004:3865: rgya chad phyogs lhung gi lam la mi 'jug ste /
NK032(khi)004:3866: gnyis med zung 'jug gcig tu 'char bar ston pa'o //
NK032(khi)004:3867: spyir rdzogs pa chen po la sgom yod dang bsgom med gnyis su 'dod pa mang pa las /
NK032(khi)004:3868: rdo rje zam pa 'di'i lugs kyis sgom du yod
NK032(khi)004:3869: byas nas don blo'i mtha' zab cing phra ba tsam
NK032(khi)004:3870: yang mi gnas pas sgom rgyu rdul tsam yang med
NK032(khi)004:3871: do // bsgom du med byas na tha mal rang rgyud pa'i phyal bar yang ma song ste /
NK032(khi)004:3872: brda bzhi'i ngang las skad cig ma gcig kyang yengs su med /
NK032(khi)004:3873: dmigs su med pa shes rab kyi mthar thug /
NK032(khi)004:3874: yengs su med pa thabs kyi mthar thug /
NK032(khi)004:3875: mi dmigs pa dang ma yengs pa gnyis dus gcig
NK032(khi)004:3876: la rgyud la sbyor ba yin pas thabs shes rab
NK032(khi)004:3877: gnyis su med par zung 'jug gi dgongs pa rang
NK032(khi)004:3878: byung gi ye shes chos bzhi dang ldan pa rgya
NK032(khi)004:3879: chad phyogs lhung med pa'i don de mi 'chug mi
NK032(khi)004:3880: 'gyur bar rtogs pa de ni sgom med don gyi
NK032(khi)004:3881: gzer chen gdab pa'i go ba rgyas pa mthar thug
NK032(khi)004:3882: par bstan pa'o // de yang phyogs su ma lhung
NK032(khi)004:3883: ba'i lung ni rtsa ba'i rgyud ye shes gsang ba
NK032(khi)004:3884: par bstan pa'o // las / bsgom du yod med mtha' yi chos //
NK032(khi)004:3885: mtha' bral dbu ma drang po'i lam //
NK032(khi)004:3886: phyogs kyi lam la 'jug pa med //
NK032(khi)004:3888: de yang rdo rje zam pa'i rgyud ye shes rdzogs pa las /
NK032(khi)004:3889: mtha' bral ye shes rdzogs pa 'di //
NK032(khi)004:3890: rtags pa ma yin mi rtag min //
NK032(khi)004:3892: dbu ma chen po drang po'i sems //
NK032(khi)004:3893: phyogs kyi lam la 'jug pa med //
NK032(khi)004:3895: ma yengs pa dang mi dmigs pa /
NK032(khi)004:3896: sgom pa dang mi sgom pa gnyis su med par zung 'jug gol sa med pa'i lung ni /
NK032(khi)004:3897: byang chub sems sgom pa don drug pa las /
NK032(khi)004:3898: sems dang chos gnyis ci yang ma yin pas //
