NK032(khi)004:6844: rtogs nas / / pa min no // de'ang rdzogs pa chen po nam mkha' che las /
NK032(khi)004:6845: byang ba chen po bcom ldan 'das //
NK032(khi)004:6846: chub par gnas pa'i bcom ldan 'das //
NK032(khi)004:6847: 'gro ba kun la rang bzhin gnas //
NK032(khi)004:6848: phyin ci log tu rnam brtags kyang //
NK032(khi)004:6849: grol ba rang byung gzhan las min //
NK032(khi)004:6851: de'ang rang gi sems nyid dngos po'i gnas lugs blo'i
NK032(khi)004:6852: mtha' zab cing phra ba tsam yang mi gnas pa'i
NK032(khi)004:6854: de ltar ma rtogs pa'i sems can rnams 'khor ba'i
NK032(khi)004:6855: sdug bsngal las grol bar bya ba'i don du bdag
NK032(khi)004:6856: chos kyi dbyings rnam par dag par sangs rgyas nas
NK032(khi)004:6857: kyang gzugs sku rnam gnyis sems can gyi snang ba
NK032(khi)004:6858: la byon nas 'gro ba 'dren pa'i don byas nas
NK032(khi)004:6859: / chos kyi dbyings spros pa dang bral ba rnam
NK032(khi)004:6860: par dag pa'i don mngon du gyur nas rtog pa
NK032(khi)004:6861: med kyang don byed nus pa bya khyung gi mchod
NK032(khi)004:6862: sdong la klu'i gnyen por rab gnas byas pas bya
NK032(khi)004:6863: khyung gi 'bag de la rtog pa med kyang rab
NK032(khi)004:6864: gnas byas pa'i byin rlabs kyi stobs kyis klu'i gnyen
NK032(khi)004:6865: por gyur nas gnod mi nus pa bzhin du /
NK032(khi)004:6866: chos sku la rtog pa med kyang gzhan don du
NK032(khi)004:6867: sems bskyed dang smon lam btab pa'i byin rlabs kyis
NK032(khi)004:6868: gzhan snang la gzugs sku gnyis su byon nas 'gro
NK032(khi)004:6869: ba 'dren pa'i gtso bor gyur nas 'khor ba'i sdug
NK032(khi)004:6870: bsngal zhi zhing thar pa mya ngan las 'da' bar
NK032(khi)004:6871: 'gyur nus pa'o // de tsa na ngo bo gcig
NK032(khi)004:6872: las ma 'das kyang don du mi rtog pa chos
NK032(khi)004:6873: 'gyur nus pa'o // sku / gzhan don du gsal ba sprul sku /
NK032(khi)004:6874: gnyis ka'i don du bde ba longs sku /
NK032(khi)004:6875: sku gsum ngo bo dbyer mi phyed pa la dbyer
NK032(khi)004:6876: phyed ces bya ba'am mi phyed ces bya ba'i blo'i
NK032(khi)004:6877: mtha' 'am tshig gi mtha' zab cing phra ba tsam
NK032(khi)004:6878: yang mi gnas pa gcig gi ngang du rdzogs par
NK032(khi)004:6879: thob pa'o // de'ang rtsa ba'i rgyud ye shes gsang ba las /
NK032(khi)004:6880: nga yi ngo bo chos sku ni //
NK032(khi)004:6881: spros pa'i mtha' rnams kun bral te //
NK032(khi)004:6882: spros pa'i mtha' dang yang dag ldan //
NK032(khi)004:6883: ye shes 'gyu ba yang dag chad //
NK032(khi)004:6884: smon lam mthu stobs gdul bya'i las //
NK032(khi)004:6885: sku gnyis 'byung bas yang dag rdzogs //
NK032(khi)004:6888: smon lam mthu stobs gdul bya'i las //
NK032(khi)004:6889: byin rlabs yon tan ngo bos 'phags //
NK032(khi)004:6890: 'dir ni sku gsum gcig gi ngang //
NK032(khi)004:6892: de'ang chos nyid kyi rdo rje zam pa rtogs pa'i
NK032(khi)004:6893: rnal 'byor pa de skye ba gzhan du mi len
NK032(khi)004:6894: par tshe gcig lus gcig gis sangs rgyas nas rtog
NK032(khi)004:6895: pa med par dgos 'dod 'byung ba'i sangs rgyas yid
NK032(khi)004:6896: bzhin gyi nor bu rin po che lta bur 'gyur
NK032(khi)004:6897: te / rang don du chos sku /
NK032(khi)004:6899: gnyis ka'i don du longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku /
NK032(khi)004:6900: 'bad rtsol bya mi dgos par sku gsum rang chas su thob pa'o //
NK032(khi)004:6901: de'ang ye shes gsang ba sku'i rgyud /
NK032(khi)004:6905: phrin las kyi rgyud dang lngar yod pa las /
NK032(khi)004:6906: de yang ye shes gsang ba phrin las kyi rgyud las /
NK032(khi)004:6907: ma bcos chos nyid rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor pa //
NK032(khi)004:6908: skye ba gzhan du mi len par //
NK032(khi)004:6910: bya rtsol mi dgos sku gsum rang la 'char //
NK032(khi)004:6912: de yan chad kyis don nyams su shar ba'i dus su sgom pa'i nyams bstan pa'o //
NK032(khi)004:6914: don gtan la phebs pa'i dus /
NK032(khi)004:6915: don nyams su shar ba'i dus dang gsum gyis rna brgyud rdo rje zam pa'i gdams ngag bstan pa'o //
NK032(khi)004:6916: snyan brgyud rdo rje zam pa 'di yang brgyud pa bzhi dang ldan pa yin te /
NK032(khi)004:6921: byin rlabs kyi brgyud pa dang bzhi'o //
NK032(khi)004:6922: bka'i brgyud pa chad na pha mang gi bu rus stor ba dang 'dra ste /
NK032(khi)004:6923: phyogs gar gtogs ngo mi shes te ci yin cha med pa'o //
NK032(khi)004:6924: tshig gi brgyud pa chad na rgyal po gdung rgyud chad pa dang 'dra ste /
NK032(khi)004:6925: tshig gi rtsa ba ma zin pas gnad med 'chal
NK032(khi)004:6926: bar shor bas don gyi bsgril so mi shes pa'o
NK032(khi)004:6927: // brda'i brgyud pa med na long ba 'khar ba bral ba dang 'dra ste /
NK032(khi)004:6928: 'khar ba med na thang bde mo la'ang som nyi zar 'ong ba dang 'dra bar /
NK032(khi)004:6929: rig pa'i don thog tu 'jog mi shes par gnas lugs kyi don la the tshom zar 'ong ba'o //
NK032(khi)004:6930: byin rlabs kyi brgyud pa med na mdzod dang tshang
NK032(khi)004:6931: mang gi bar gyi sgron me shi ba dang 'dra
NK032(khi)004:6932: ste / mdzod kyi ka ca'ang mi lon /
NK032(khi)004:6933: tshang mang du bskyal du 'gro bas chud 'dza' ba bzhin du /
NK032(khi)004:6934: bla ma'i dgongs pa mi lon te rang gi rgyud
NK032(khi)004:6935: la nyams myong skyer ma btub pas bar chad du
NK032(khi)004:6936: gyur nas phan mi thogs pa'o //
NK032(khi)004:6937: bka'i brgyud pa ma chad na bka' brgyud kyi dgongs pa lon /
NK032(khi)004:6938: tshig gi brgyud pa ma chad na yang dag pa'i don rtogs /
NK032(khi)004:6939: brda'i brgyud pa ma chad na sems nyid mngon du mthong /
NK032(khi)004:6940: byin rlabs kyi brgyud pa ma chad na mkha' 'gro ma'i ko long du mi 'gro ste /
NK032(khi)004:6941: mchog dang thun mong gi dngos grub da lta nyid du thob ste /
NK032(khi)004:6942: tshe gcig lus gcig la rang dang gzhan gnyis ka'i don 'grub ste rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas thob pa'o //
NK032(khi)004:6943: bka'i brgyud pa ni rna brgyud lung gi gter chen dgrol ba'o //
NK032(khi)004:6944: tshig gi brgyud pa ni rdo rje'i tshig lam sems kyi lde mig bstan pa'o //
NK032(khi)004:6945: brda'i brgyud pa ni brda don dgrol ba'i man ngag go //
NK032(khi)004:6946: byin rlabs kyi brgyud pa ni 'jug pa bstan pa
NK032(khi)004:6947: sgom tshul bla ma'i byin rlabs a ha ho'i 'o
NK032(khi)004:6948: // de yang bka' sa man+ta nam mkha' dang mnyam pa bde ba kun tu spyod pa'i rgyud las /
NK032(khi)004:6949: klong dgu bam po nyi khri le'u khri drug stong yod pa las /
NK032(khi)004:6950: de las phye ba'i rdo rje'i snying po don gtan la 'bebs pa'i rgyud sde bcu gsum dang /
NK032(khi)004:6951: pad+ma'i snying po'i don nyams su len pa'i sgrub sde bcu gsum las /
NK032(khi)004:6952: pha rgyud g.yo ba rlung 'dzin pa'i gdams ngag gi brgyud pa dang /
NK032(khi)004:6953: ma rgyud bde ba'i nyams 'char ba byin rlabs kyi brgyud pa /
NK032(khi)004:6954: de la pha rgyud kyi don bsdus pa g.yo ba rlung gi man ngag /
NK032(khi)004:6955: ma rgyud kyi don bsdus pa bde ba thig le'i man ngag /
NK032(khi)004:6956: de gnyis gcig tu med pa sgom med don gyi gzer chen gdab pa /
NK032(khi)004:6957: rgyud sde bcu gsum gyi don /
NK032(khi)004:6958: sgrub sde bcu gsum gyi snying po /
NK032(khi)004:6959: rna brgyud rin po che rdo rje zam pa'i gdams ngag /
NK032(khi)004:6960: lus kyi dbang po'i nang nas mig lta bu /
NK032(khi)004:6961: byang khog gi nang nas snying lta bu /
NK032(khi)004:6962: rgya mtsho'i nang nas bdud rtsi /
NK032(khi)004:6963: skad cig ma'i don rtogs nas tshe gcig gis sangs rgya ba'i gdams ngag rdzogs so //
NK032(khi)004:6964: rgya mtsho'i nang gi bsdus pa lta bu'i lung ni /
NK032(khi)004:6965: rna brgyud dbang gi man ngag las /
NK032(khi)004:6966: rna brgyud 'phrul gyi rdo rje zam pa 'di //
NK032(khi)004:6967: bka' yi thugs kyi nying khu ste //
NK032(khi)004:6968: ngang pas chu las 'o ma bsdus pa'am //
NK032(khi)004:6969: n+aa ga 'jog pos rin chen sgrom phyung ste //
NK032(khi)004:6970: rgya mtsho'i kha byabs bdud rtsi bsdus pa bzhin //
NK032(khi)004:6971: b+ha ga'i thugs bcud bdud rtsi bsdus pa bzhin //
NK032(khi)004:6973: snyan brgyud rdo rje zam pa'i gdams ngag 'di snod
NK032(khi)004:6974: dang mi ldan pa la bstan du mi rung ste
NK032(khi)004:6976: gsang med dam tshig mi ldan snod med rnams la ni /
NK032(khi)004:6977: snyan brgyud rin po che 'di bstan 'gyur na //
NK032(khi)004:6978: 'dam shod gling gi dur khrod du //
NK032(khi)004:6980: sha khrag dngos su za bar 'gyur //
NK032(khi)004:6982: gnas lugs kyi don dbyer mi phyed pa blo'i mtha'
NK032(khi)004:6983: zab cing phra ba tsam yang mi gnas pa'i don
NK032(khi)004:6984: las mi 'da' ba ni dam tshig bsrung ba yin
NK032(khi)004:6985: no // de yang ye shes gsang ba las /
NK032(khi)004:6986: brjod med rig pa'i don mthong na //
NK032(khi)004:6987: rang byung gsal ba'i dam tshig thob //
NK032(khi)004:6989: bang mdzod 'phrul gyi lde mig las //
NK032(khi)004:6990: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad la //
NK032(khi)004:6991: rang bzhin dam tshig gcig las med //
NK032(khi)004:6992: rang snang mi 'gyur chos nyid la //
NK032(khi)004:6993: rang bzhag rig pa mi 'da' na //
NK032(khi)004:6994: sems nyid gcis pu'i dam tshig ste //
NK032(khi)004:6995: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad la //
NK032(khi)004:6996: dam tshig de las yong mi mnga' //
NK032(khi)004:6998: rna brgyud rdo rje zam pa'i gdams pa zab mo 'di //
NK032(khi)004:6999: bla ma dam pa rin po chen kun bzang gis //
NK032(khi)004:7000: bla ma rgya ye shes seng ge zhes bya ba la //
NK032(khi)004:7001: thugs la btags nas gnang ba yin //
NK032(khi)004:7002: de las bsod nams ci byung ba'i dge ba yis //
NK032(khi)004:7003: nyon mongs 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal gyis mnar ba'i sems can rnams //
NK032(khi)004:7004: 'khor ba dag las rab tu grol nas kyang //
NK032(khi)004:7005: bla med byang chub myur du thob par shog /
NK032(khi)004:7008: chos sku kun tu bzang po dag pa'i gzhi //
NK032(khi)004:7009: longs sku rdo rje sems dpa' 'gag med rtsal //
NK032(khi)004:7010: sprul sku sems dag lha'i bu mtshon pa'i brda //
NK032(khi)004:7011: sku gsum 'du 'bral med par dgos pa'i klong //
NK032(khi)004:7012: rgyal ba dgongs pa'i brgyud pa ngo mtshar can //
NK032(khi)004:7013: bde gshegs sangs rgyas rnams kyi bkra shis shog /
NK032(khi)004:7014: dga' rab rdo rje sprul sku theg chen rigs //
NK032(khi)004:7015: 'jam dpal bshes gnyen grub thob dpa' bo'i thugs //
NK032(khi)004:7016: sh+r+ai sing ha mkhas pa pan+di ta //
NK032(khi)004:7017: bee ro tsa na rgya bod lo ts+aa ba //
NK032(khi)004:7018: rig 'dzin brda yi brgyud pa ngo mtshar can //
NK032(khi)004:7019: rig 'dzin brgyud pa rnams kyi bkra shis shog /
NK032(khi)004:7020: mi pham mgon po skal ldan las 'phro can //
NK032(khi)004:7021: byang chub rgyal mtshan za ngam rin chen dbyig /
NK032(khi)004:7022: khu 'gyur gsal ba'i mchog dang ni //
NK032(khi)004:7023: brgyud 'dzin chen po rig 'dzin khyed kyi bkra shis shog /
NK032(khi)004:7024: byang chub grags pa shes rab 'byung gnas dang //
NK032(khi)004:7025: rba sgom ye shes rgyal ba 'dzeng ston dang //
NK032(khi)004:7026: brgyud 'dzin grags pa bzhi yi bkra shis shog /
NK032(khi)004:7027: dam pa jo sras rin chen kun bzang dang //
NK032(khi)004:7028: sprul sku 'od 'bar skal ldan ye shes seng ge dang //
NK032(khi)004:7029: brgyud 'dzin sras po bzhi yi bkra shis shog /
NK032(khi)004:7030: dang po byin gyis brlabs dang bar du zhal nas gsungs shing tha ma rjes su gnang //
NK032(khi)004:7031: snyan brgyud kyi bde gshegs dam pa dang //
NK032(khi)004:7032: grub thob kyi bka' brgyud rim pa rnams //
NK032(khi)004:7033: gang zag gdams ngag gi brgyud pa ngo mtshar can //
NK032(khi)004:7034: bde gshegs gong ma rnams kyi sras //
NK032(khi)004:7035: dka' pa dpag med spyad gyur pas //
NK032(khi)004:7036: bde gshegs byin rlabs sangs rgyas dgongs pa mthong //
NK032(khi)004:7037: dbang gi don rtogs sems nyid mngon du gyur //
NK032(khi)004:7038: grub thob rtags tshang phung po lhag med gshegs //
NK032(khi)004:7039: bkra shis tshe ring 'gro ba'i don la brtson //
NK032(khi)004:7040: rdo rje zam pa'i brgyud pa ngo mtshar can //
NK032(khi)004:7041: grub thob byin rlabs can gyi bkra shis shog /
NK032(khi)004:7042: mngon rdzogs byin che yang dag thugs kyi lha //
NK032(khi)004:7043: zhi khro'i lha tshogs nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam //
NK032(khi)004:7044: dngos grub char ltar 'bebs pa'i lha tshogs ngo mtshar can //
NK032(khi)004:7045: zhi khro'i lha tshogs kun gyi bkra shis shog /
NK032(khi)004:7046: dpal chen he ru ka yab yum thugs kyi sras //
NK032(khi)004:7047: zhing skyes la sogs mkha' 'gro sde gsum po //
NK032(khi)004:7048: zab mo'i bka' skyong byed par rang dam rang gis bcas /
NK032(khi)004:7049: dad ldan lam sna 'dren zhing dam nyams sgrol //
NK032(khi)004:7050: zhi khro'i sprul pa 'gyed cing rten 'brel sgrigs //
NK032(khi)004:7051: thun mong mchog gi dngos grub ster ba'i ngo mtshar can //
NK032(khi)004:7052: zhing skyong mkha' 'gro gsum gyi bkra shis shog /
NK032(khi)004:7053: sku gsung thugs kyi mkha' 'gro'i sras //
NK032(khi)004:7054: ma nor ma bcos sems nyis don ston pa //
NK032(khi)004:7055: gdod nas dag pa rang la gsal bar ston //
NK032(khi)004:7056: rna brgyud lung gi brgyud pa nges shes bskyed //
NK032(khi)004:7057: sgom med don gyi sems nyid ngo bo sprod //
NK032(khi)004:7058: re dogs med par chos nyid dbyings dang 'phrad //
NK032(khi)004:7059: don nyid gtan la phebs pa'i bkra shis shog /
NK032(khi)004:7060: dbang rnams ngang gis rdzogs pas ltos med rang la tshang //
NK032(khi)004:7061: sku lnga rang chas su gyur pas bdag gzhan 'dzin pa med //
NK032(khi)004:7062: don rnams gcig tu rtogs pas blo yi rtog dpyod 'das //
NK032(khi)004:7063: yang dag don de gtan la phebs pa'i bkra shis shog /
NK032(khi)004:7064: rtse gcig sgyu ma'i nyams shar bden par 'dzin pa med //
NK032(khi)004:7065: don rnams nyams su shar ba'i sras //
NK032(khi)004:7066: rdo rje'i lam mchog 'di la 'grub thob bsam mi khyab //
NK032(khi)004:7067: skal ldan 'bad rtsol ma byas don de lhun gyis grub //
NK032(khi)004:7068: rang don gzhan la smin pas 'gro don rgyun mi chad //
NK032(khi)004:7069: snyan brgyud rdo rje zam pa'i lam gyi sras //
NK032(khi)004:7070: phyogs su ma lhung ye shes snying po can //
NK032(khi)004:7071: blo bral rang gsal lta ba'i bkra shis shog /
NK032(khi)004:7072: bying rgod kyi dbang du ma song bar //
NK032(khi)004:7074: ma gtad ma yengs sgom pa'i bkra shis shog /
NK032(khi)004:7075: spong len ma shor ma 'gags zhen med spyod //
NK032(khi)004:7076: snang yang 'dzin med spyod pa'i bkra shis shog /
NK032(khi)004:7077: re dogs ma shor gzhi shes 'dzin pa grol //
NK032(khi)004:7078: ka dag dbyings grol 'bras bu'i bkra shis shog /
NK032(khi)004:7079: khyab brdal ma chags rtog med 'gro don mdzad //
NK032(khi)004:7080: gzhan don sun med nam mkha' lta bur khyab pa'i bkra shis shog /
NK032(khi)004:7081: tshe zad skal med ma gtogs par //
NK032(khi)004:7082: glo bur ye 'drogs dbang du ma song bar //
NK032(khi)004:7083: slob dpon rtag tu 'dzin pa dang //
NK032(khi)004:7084: rigs rgyud mi chad chu bo chen po bzhi lta bu'i bkra shis shog /
NK032(khi)004:7085: chos sku bde chen kun bzang man chad nas //
NK032(khi)004:7086: da lta brgyud 'dzin grub thob gang zag bcas //
NK032(khi)004:7087: tha ma dus mtha'i bskal pa tshun chad du //
NK032(khi)004:7088: dam pa chos kyi bstan pa dar rgyas shing //
NK032(khi)004:7089: brgyud 'dzin gyi bstan pa 'phel ba'i bkra shis shog /
NK032(khi)004:7090: dus da lta 'dir tshogs kyi skal ldan pho mo rnams //
NK032(khi)004:7091: bde gshegs ltung bar mi 'gyur zhing khams su //
NK032(khi)004:7092: dgongs pa nam mkha' bzhin du 'dres nas kyang //
NK032(khi)004:7093: 'gro ba ma lus bde gnas 'dren pa'i smon lam 'debs //
NK032(khi)004:7094: bkra shis dam pa des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK032(khi)004:7095: smon lam mthu btsan par gyur cig //
NK032(khi)004:7096: de kho na bzhin du 'grub par gyur cig /
